kathaamukham |

AUM namaH shriishaaradaagaNapatigurubhyaH |
mahaakavibhyo namaH |

brahmaa rudraH kumaaro harivaruNayamaa vahnirindraH kubera\-
shcandraadityau sarasvatyudadhiyuganagaa vaayururvii bhuja~NgaaH |
siddhaa nadyo.ashvinau shriirditiraditisutaa maatarashcaNDikaadyaaH |
vedaastiirthaani yakShaa gaNavasumunayaH paantu nitya.n grahaashca ||
manave vaacaspataye shukraaya paraasharaaya sa sutaaya |
caaNakyaaya ca viduShe namo.astu nayashaastrakartR^ibhyaH || 1||
sakalaarthashaastrasaara.n jagati samaalokya viShNusharmedam |
tantraiH pa~ncabhiretaishcakaara sumanohara.n shaastram || 2||

tadyathaanushruuyate | asti daakShiNaatye janapade mahilaaropya.n naama
nagaram | tatra sakalaarthisaarthakalpadrumaH pravaranR^ipamukuTamaNi\-
mariicicayacarcitacaraNayugalaH sakalakalaapaara.ngato.amarashakti\-
rnaama raajaa babhuuva | tasya trayaH putraaH paramadurmedhaso
vasushaktirugrashaktiranekashaktishceti naamaano babhuuvuH | atha raajaa
taan shaastravimukhaanaalokya sacivaanaahuuya provaaca \- bhoH
dnyaatametadbhavadbhiryanmamaite trayo.api putraaH shaastravimukhaa
vivekahiinaashca | tadetaanpashyato me mahadapi raajya.n na
saukhyamaavahati | athavaa saadhvidamucyate \-

ajaatamR^itamuurkhebhyo mR^itaajaatau sutau varam |
yatastau svalpaduHkhaaya yaavajjiiva.n jaDo dahet || 3||
vara.n garbhasraavo varamR^ituShu naivaabhigamanam |
vara.n jaataH preto varamapi ca kanyaiva janitaa |
vara.n vandhyaa bhaaryaa varamapi ca garbheShu vasati\-
rna caavidagdhaan ruupadraviNaguNayukto.api tanayaH || 4||
ki.n tayaa kriyate dhenvaa yaa na suute na dugdhadaa |
ko.arthaH putreNa jaatena yo na vidvaanna bhaktimaan || 5||

tadeteShaa.n yathaa buddhiprabodhana.n bhavati tathaa ko.apyupaa\-
yo.anuShThiiyataam | atra ca maddattaa.n vR^itti.n bhu~njaanaanaa.n
paNDitaanaa.n pa~ncashatii tiShThati | tato yathaa mama manorathaaH
siddhi.n yaanti tathaanuShThiiyataamiti | tatraikaH provaaca \- deva
dvaadashabhirvarShairvyaakaraNa.n shruuyate | tato dharmashaastraaNi
manvaadiinyarthashaastraaNi caaNakyaadiini kaamashaastraaNi
vaatsyaayanaadiini | eva.n ca tato dharmaarthakaamashaastraaNi
dnyaayante | tataH pratibodhana.n bhavati | atha tanmadhyataH
sumatirnaama sacivaH praaha \- ashaashvato.aya.n jiivaviShayaH |
prabhuutakaaladnyeyaani shabdashaastraaNi | tatsa~NkShepamaatra.n
shaastra.n ki~ncideteShaa.n prabodhanaartha.n cintyataamiti |
ukta~nca yataH \-

anantapaara.n kila shabda shaastra.n
           svalpa.n tathaayurbahavashca vighnaaH |
saara.n tato graahyamapaasya phalgu
           ha.nsairyathaa kShiiramivaambumadhyaat || 6||

tadatraasti viShNusharmaa naama braahmaNaH sakalashaastrapaara.n\-
gamashcaatra sa.nsadi labdhakiirtiH | tasmai samarpayatvetaan | sa
nuuna.n draak prabuddhaan kariShyatiiti |sa raajaa tadaakarNya
viShNusharmaaNamaahuuya provaaca\- bho bhagavan madanugra\-
haarthametaanarthashaastra.n prati draagyathaananyasadR^ishaan
vidadhaasi tathaa kuru | tadaha.n tvaa.n shaasanashatena yojayiShyaami |
atha viShNusharmaa ta.n raajaanamaaha \- deva shruuyataa.n me
tathyavacanam | naaha.n vidyaavikraya.n shaasanashatenaapi karomi |
punaretaa{\m+}stava putraanmaasaShaTkena yadi niitishaastradnyaanna
karomi tataH svanaamatyaaga.n karomi |athaasau raajaa taa.n braahmaNa\-
syaasa.nbhaavyaa.n pratidnyaa.n shrutvaa sasacivaH prahR^iShTo
vismayaanvitastasmai saadara.n taan kumaaraan samarpya paraa.n
nirvR^itimaajagaama | viShNusharmaNaapi taanaadaaya tadartha.n
mitrabhedamitrapraaptikaakoluukiiyalabdhapraNaashaapariikShitakaarakaaNi
ceti pa~nca tantraaNi racayitvaa paaThitaaste raajaputraaH | te.api 
taanyadhiitya
maasaShaTkena yathoktaaH sa.nvR^ittaaH | tataH prabhR^ityetat
pa~ncatantraka.n naama niitishaastra.n baalaavabodhanaartha.n
bhuutale pravR^ittam | ki.n bahunaa \-

adhiite ya ida.n nitya.n niitishaastra.n shR^iNoti ca |
na paraabhavamaapnoti shakraadapi kadaacana || 7||

iti kathaamukham |
\medskip\hrule\medskip

mitrabhedaH |

vardhamaanavR^ittaantaH |

athaataH praarabhyate mitrabhedo naama prathama.n tantram |
yasyaayamaadimaH shlokaH \-

vardhamaano mahaan snehaH si.nhagovR^iShayorvane |
pishunenaatilubdhena jambukena vinaashitaH || 1||

tadyathaanushruuyate | asti dakShiNaatye janapade mahilaaropya.n naama
nagaram | tatra dharmopaarjitabhuurivibhavo vardhamaanako naama
vaNikputro babhuuva | tasya kadaacidraatrau shayyaaruuDhasya
cintaa samutpannaa | yatprabhuute.api vitte.arthopaayaashcintaniiyaaH
kartavyaashceti | yata ukta~nca \-

na hi tadvidyate ki.ncidyadarthena na sidhyati |
yatnena matimaa.nstasmaadarthameka.n prasaadhayet || 2||
yasyaarthaastasya mitraaNi yasyaarthaastasya baandhavaaH |
yasyaarthaaH sa pumaa{\m+}lloke yasyaarthaaH sa ca paNDitaH || 3||
na saa vidyaa na taddaana.n na tacChilpa.n na saa kalaa |
na tatsthairya.n hi dhaninaa.n yaacakairyanna giiyate || 4||
iha loke hi dhaninaa.n paro.api svajanaayate |
svajano.api daridraaNaa.n sarvadaa durjanaayate || 5||
arthebhyo.api hi vR^iddhebhyaH sa.nvR^ittebhyastastataH |
pravartante kriyaaH sarvaaH parvatebhya ivaapagaaH || 6||
puujyate yadapuujyo.api yadagamyo.api gamyate |
vandyate yadavandyo.api sa prabhaavo dhanasya ca || 7||
ashanaadindriyaaNiiva syuH kaaryaaNyakhilaanyapi |
etasmaatkaaraNaadvitta.n sarvasaadhanamucyate || 8||
arthaarthii jiivaloko.aya.n shmashaanamapi sevate |
tyaktvaa janayitaara.n sva.n niHsva.n gacChati duurataH || 9||
gatavayasaamapi pu.nsaa.n yeShaamarthaa bhavanti te taruNaaH |
arthena tu ye vihiinaa vR^iddhaaste yauvane.api syuH || 10||

sa caarthaH puruShaaNaa.n ShaDbhirupaayairbhavati bhikShayaa
nR^ipasevayaa kR^iShikarmaNaa vidyopaarjanena vyavahaareNa
vaNikkarmaNaa vaa | sarveShaamapi teShaa.n vaaNijyenaatiraskR^ito\-
.arthalaabhaH syaat | ukta~nca yataH \-

kR^itaa bhikShaanekairvitarati nR^ipo nocitamaho
kR^iShiH kliShTaa vidyaa guruvinayavR^ittyaativiShamaa |
kusiidaaddaaridrya.n parakaragatagranthishamanaa\-
nna manye vaaNijyaatkimapi parama.n vartanamiha || 11||
upaayaanaa.n ca sarveShaamupaayaH paNyasa.ngrahaH |
dhanaartha.n shasyate hyekastadanyaaH sa.nshayaatmakaaH || 12||

tacca vaaNijya.n saptavidhamarthaagamaaya syaat | tadyathaa gaandhika\-
vyavahaaro nikShepapravesho goShThikakarma paricitagraahakaagamo
mithyaakrayakathana.n, kuuTatulaamaana.n deshaantaraadbhaaNDaa\-
nayana.n ceti | ukta~nca \-

paNyaanaa.n gaandhika.n paNya.n kimanyaiH kaa~ncanaadibhiH |
yatraikena ca yatkriita.n tacChatena pradiiyate || 13||
nikShepe patite harmye shreShThii stauti svadevataam |
nikShepii mriyate tubhya.n pradaasyaamyupayaacitam || 14||
goShThikakarmaniyuktaH shreShThii cintayati cetasaa hR^iShTaH |
vasudhaa vasusa.npuurNaa mayaadya labdhaa kimanyena || 15||
paricitamaagacChanta.n graahakamutkaNThayaa vilokyaasau |
hR^iShyati taddhanalabdho yadvatputreNa jaatena || 16||

anyacca \-

puurNaapuurNe maane paricitajanava~ncana.n tathaa nityam |
mithyaakrayasya kathana.n prakR^itiriya.n syaatkiraataanaam || 17||
dviguNa.n triguNa.n vitta.n bhaaNDakrayavicakShaNaaH |
praapnuvantyudyamaallokaa duuradeshaantara.n gataaH || 18||

ityeva.n sa.npradhaarya mathuraagaamiini bhaaNDaanyaadaaya shubhaayaa.n
tithau gurujanaanuj~naataH surathaadhiruuDhaH prasthitaH | tasya ca
ma~NgalavR^iShabhau sa.njiivakanandakanaamaanau gR^ihotpannau
dhuurvoDhaarau sthitau | tayorekaH sa.njiivakaabhidhaano yamunaakacCha\-
mavatiirNaH san pa~Nkapuuramaasaadya kalitacaraNo yugabha~Nga.n
vidhaaya niShasaada | atha ta.n tadavasthamaalokya vardhamaanaH
para.n viShaadamagamat | tadartha.n ca snehaardrahR^idayastriraatra.n
prayaaNabha~Ngamakarot | atha ta.n viShaNNamaalokya saarthikairabhihitam
\- bhoH shreShThin ! kimeva.n vR^iShabhasya kR^ite si.nhavyaaghrasamaakule
bahvapaaye.asmin vane samastasaarthastvayaa sandehe niyojitaH |
ukta~nca \-

na svalpasya kR^ite bhuuri naashayenmatimaannaraH |
etadevaatra paaNDitya.n yatsvalpaadbhuuri rakShaNam || 19||

athaasau tadavadhaarya sa.njiivakasya rakShaapuruShaanniruupyaa\-
sheShasaartha.n niitvaa prasthitaH | atha rakShaapuruShaa api bahvapaaya.n
tadvana.n viditvaa sa.njiivaka.n parityajya pR^iShThato gatvaa.anyedyusta.n
saarthavaaha.n mithyaa.ahuH \- svaamin mR^ito.asau sa.njiivakaH |
asmaabhistu saarthavaahasyaabhiiShTa iti matvaa vahninaa sa.nskR^ita iti |
tacChrutvaa saarthavaahaH kR^itaj~natayaa snehaardrahR^idayastasyaurdhva\-
dehikakriyaa vR^iShotsargaadikaaH sarvaashcakaara | sa.njiivako.apyaayuH\-
sheShatayaa yamunaasalilamishraiH shishirataravaatairaapyaayitashariiraH
katha.ncidapyutthaaya yamunaataTamupapede | tatra marakatasadR^ishaani
baalatR^iNaagraaNi bhakShayankatipayairahobhirharavR^iShabha iva piinaH
kakudmaanbalavaa.nshca sa.nvR^ittaH | pratyaha.n valmiikashikharaagraaNi
shR^i~Ngaabhyaa.n vidaarayangarjamaana aaste | saadhu cedamucyate \-

arakShita.n tiShThati devarakShita.n surakShita.n devahata.n vinashyati |
jiivatyanaatho.api vane visarjitaH kR^itaprayatno.api gR^ihe vinashyati || 20||

atha kadaacitpi~Ngalako naama si.nhaH sarvamR^igaparivR^itaH
pipaasaakula udakapaanaartha.n yamunaataTamavatiirNaH sa.njiivakasya
gambhiiratararaava.n duuraadevaashR^iNot | tacChrutvaa.atiiva vyaakula\-
hR^idayaH sasaadhvasamaakaara.n pracChaadya vaTatale
caturmaNDalaavasthaanenaavasthitaH | caturmaNDalaavasthaana.n
tvida.n si.nhaH si.nhaanuyaayinaH kaakakaravaaH ki.nvR^ittaa iti | 
atha tasya karaTakadamanakanaamaanau dvau shR^igaalau mantriputrau
bhraShTaadhikaarau sadaanuyaayinaavaastaam | tau ca paraspara.n
mantrayataH | tatra damanako.abraviit \- bhadra karaTaka aya.n
taavadasmatsvaamii pi~Ngalaka udakagrahaNaartha.n yamunaakacCha\-
mavatiirya sthitaH | sa ki.nnimitta.n pipaasaakulo.api nivR^ittya
vyuuharacanaa.n vidhaaya daurmanasyenaabhibhuuto.atra vaTatale
sthitaH | karaTaka aaha \- bhadra kimaavayoranena vyaapaareNa |
ukta~nca yataH \-

avyaapaareShu vyaapaara.n yo naraH kartumicChati |
sa eva nidhana.n yaati kiilotpaaTiiva vaanaraH || 21||

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 1
kiilotpaaTivaanarakathaa |

kasmi.nshcinnagaraabhyaase kenaapi vaNikputreNa tarukhaNDamadhye
devataayatana.n kartumaarabdham | tatra ca ye karmakaraaH
sthaapanaadayaste madhyaahnavelaayaamaahaaraartha.n nagaramadhye
gacChanti | atha kadaacit tatraanuSha~Ngika.n vaanarayuuthamitashce\-
tashca paribhramadaagatam | tatraikasya kasyacicChilpino.ardhasphaaTito\-
.a~njanavR^ikShadaarumayaH stambhaH khadirakiilakena madhyanihitena
tiShThati | etasminnantare te vaanaraastarushikharapraasaadashR^i~Nga\-
daaruparyanteShu yathecChayaa kriiDitumaarabdhaaH | ekashca teShaa.n
pratyaasannamR^ityushcaapalyaattasminnardhasphoTitastambha upavishya
paaNibhyaa.n kiilaka.n sa.ngR^ihya yaavadutpaadayitumaarebhe taavattasya
stambhamadhyagatavR^iShaNasya svasthaanaaccalitakiilakena yadvR^itta.n
tatpraageva niveditam | ato.aha.n braviimi \- avyaapaareShu iti |
aavayorbhakShitasheSha aahaaro.astyeva | tat kimanena vyaapaareNa |
damanaka aaha tat ki.n bhavaanaahaaraarthii kevalameva | tanna yuktam |
ukta~nca \-

suhR^idaamupakaarakaaraNaaddviShataamapyapakaarakaaraNaat |
nR^ipasa.nshraya iShyate budhairjaThara.n ko na bibharti kevalam || 22||

ki~nca \-

yasmin jiivanti jiivanti bahavaH so.atra jiivati |
vayaa.nsi ki.n na kurvanti ca~ncvaa svodarapuuraNam || 23||

tathaa ca \-

yajjiivyate kShaNamapi prathita.n manuShyai\-
           rvij~naanashauryavibhavaaryaguNaiH sametam |
tannaama jiivitamiha pravadanti tajdnyaaH
           kaako.api jiivati ciraaya bali.n ca bhu~Nkte || 24||
yo naatmanaa na ca pareNa ca bandhuvarge
diine dayaa.n na kurute na ca martyavarge |
ki.n tasya jiivitaphala.n hi manuShyaloke
kaako.api jiivati ciraaya bali.n ca bhu~Nkte || 25||
supuuraa syaatkunadikaa supuuro muuShikaa~njaliH |
susa.ntuShTaH kaapuruShaH svalpakenaapi tuShyati || 26||

ki~nca \-

ki.n tena jaatu jaatena maaturyauvanahaariNaa |
aarohati na yaH svasya va.nshasyaagre dhvajo yathaa || 27||
parivartini sa.nsaare mR^itaH ko vaa na jaayate |
jaatastu gaNyate so.atra yaH sphurecca shriyaadhikaH || 28||

ki~nca \-

jaatasya nadiitiire tasyaapi tR^iNasya janmasaaphalyam |
yatsalilamajjanaakulajanahastaalambana.n bhavati || 29||

tathaa ca \-

stimitonnatasa~ncaaraa janasantaapahaariNaH |
jaayante viralaa loke jaladaa iva sajjanaaH || 30||
niratishaya.n garimaaNa.n tena jananyaaH smaranti vidvaa.nsaH |
yatkamapi vahati garbha.n mahataamapi yo gururbhavati || 31||
aprakaTiikR^itashaktiH shakto.api janastiraskriyaa.n labhate |
nivasannantardaaruNi la~Nghyo vahnirna tu jvalitaH || 32||

karaTaka aaha \- aavaa.n taavadapradhaanau tatkimaavayoranena
vyaapareNa | ukta~nca \-

apR^iShTo.atraapradhaano yo bruute raadnyaH puraH kudhiiH |
na kevalamasa.nmaana.n labhate ca viDambanam || 33||

tathaa ca \-

vacastatra prayoktavya.n yatrokta.n labhate phalam |
sthaayii bhavati caatyanta.n raagaH shuklapaTe yathaa || 34||

damanaka aaha \- maa maiva.n vada |

apradhaanaH pradhaanaH syaatsevate yadi paarthivam |
pradhaano.apyapradhaanaH syaadyadi sevaavivarjitaH || 35||

yata ukta~nca \-

aasannameva nR^ipatirbhajate manuShya.n
           vidyaavihiinamakuliinamasa.nskR^ita.n vaa |
praayeNa bhuumipatayaH pramadaa lataashca
           yatpaarshvato bhavati tatpariveShTayanti || 36||

tathaa ca \-

kopaprasaadavastuuni ye vicinvanti sevakaaH |
aarohanti shanaiH pashcaaddhunvantamapi paarthivam || 37||
vidyaavataa.n mahecChaanaa.n shilpavikramashaalinaam |
sevaavR^ittividaa.n caiva naashrayaH paarthiva.n vinaa || 38||
ye jaatyaadimahotsaahaannarendraannopayaanti ca |
teShaamaamaraNa.n bhikShaa praayashcitta.n vinirmitam || 39||
ye ca praahurduraatmaano duraaraadhyaa mahiibhujaH |
pramaadaalasyajaaDyaani khyaapitaani nijaani taiH || 40||
sarpaanvyaaghraangajaansi.nhaan dR^iShTopaayairvashiikR^itaan |
raajeti kiyatii maatraa dhiimataamapramaadinaam || 41||
raajaanameva sa.nshritya vidvaanyaati paraa.n gatim |
vinaa malayamanyatra candana.n na prarohati || 42||
dhavalaanyaatapatraaNi vaajinashca manoramaaH |
sadaa mattaashca maata~NgaaH prasanne sati bhuupatau || 43||

karaTaka aaha \- atha bhavaanki.n kartumanaaH | so.abraviit \-
adyaasmatsvaamii pi~Ngalako bhiito bhiitaparivaarashca vartate | tadena.n
gatvaa bhayakaaraNa.n vij~naaya 
sandhivigrahayaanaaasanasa.nshrayadvaidhiibhaavaa\-
naamekatamena sa.nvidhaasye | karaTaka aaha \- katha.n vetti
bhavaanyadbhayaaviShTo.aya.n svaamii | so.abraviit \- dnyeya.n kimatra |
yata ukta~nca \-

udiirito.arthaH pashunaapi gR^ihyate
           hayaashca naagaashca vahanti coditaaH |
anuktamapyuuhati paNDito janaH
           pare~Ngitadnyaanaphalaa hi buddhayaH || 44||

tathaa ca manuH (8.26) \-

aakaarairi~Ngitairgatyaa ceShTayaa bhaaShaNena ca |
netravaktravikaaraishca lakShyate.antargata.n manaH || 45||

tadadyaina.n bhayaakula.n praapya svabuddhiprabhaavena nirbhaya.n
kR^itvaa vashiikR^itya ca nijaa.n saacivyapadavii.n
samaasaadayiShyaami | karaTaka aaha \- anabhij~no bhavaan
sevaadharmasya | tatkathamena.n vashiikariShyasi | so.abraviit \-
kathamaha.n sevaanabhidnyaH | mayaa hi taatotsa~Nge kriiDataa\-
.abhyaagatasaadhuunaa.n niitishaastra.n paThataa.n yacChruta.n
sevaadharmasya saara.n tad hR^idi sthaapitam | shruuyataa.n
taccedam \-

suvarNapuShpitaa.n pR^ithvii.n vicinvanti naraastrayaH |
shuurashca kR^itavidyashca yashca jaanaati sevitum || 46||
saa sevaa yaa prabhuhitaa graahyaa vaakyavisheShataH |
aashrayetpaarthiva.n vidvaa.nstaddvaareNaiva naanyathaa || 47||
yo na vetti guNaanyasya na ta.n seveta paNDitaH |
na hi tasmaatphala.n ki~ncitsukR^iShTaaduuSharaadiva || 48||
dravyaprakR^itihiino.api sevyaH sevyaguNaanvitaH |
bhavatyaajiivana.n tasmaatphala.n kaalaantaraadapi || 49||
api sthaaNuvadaasiinaH shuShyanparigataH kShudhaa |
na tvevaanaatmasampannaadvR^ittimiiheta paNDitaH || 50||
sevakaH svaamina.n dveShTi kR^ipaNa.n paruShaakSharam |
aatmaana.n ki.n sa na dveShTi sevyaasevya.n na vetti yaH || 51||
yamaashritya na vishraama.n kShudhaartaa yaanti sevakaaH |
so.arkavannR^ipatistyaajyaH sadaa puShpaphalo.api san || 52||
raajamaatari devyaa.n ca kumaare mukhyamantriNi |
purohite pratiihaare sadaa varteta raajavat || 53||
jiiveti prabruvanproktaH kR^ityaakR^ityavicakShaNaH |
karoti nirvikalpa.n yaH sa bhavedraajavallabhaH || 54||
prabhuprasaadaja.n vitta.n supraapta.n yo nivedayet |
vastraadya.n ca dadhatya~Nge sa bhavedraajavallabhaH || 55||
antaHpuracaraiH saardha.n yo na mantra.n samaacaret |
na kalatrairnarendrasya sa bhavedraajavallabhaH || 56||
dyuuta.n yo yamaduutaabha.n haalaa.n haalaahalopamaam |
pashyeddaaraanvR^ithaakaaraansa bhavedraajavallabhaH || 57||
yuddhakaale.agraNiiryaH syaatsadaa pR^iShThaanugaH pure |
prabhordvaaraashrito harmye sa bhavedraajavallabhaH || 58||
sammato.aha.n vibhornityamiti matvaa vyatikramet |
kR^icChreShvapi na maryaadaa.n sa bhavedraajavallabhaH || 59||
dveShidveShaparo nityamiShTaanaamiShTakarmakR^it |
yo naro naranaathasya sa bhavedraajavallabhaH || 60||
proktaH pratyuttara.n naaha viruddha.n prabhuNaa ca yaH |
na samiipe hasatyuccaiH sa bhavedraajavallabhaH || 61||
yo raNa.n sharaNa.n tadvanmanyate bhayavarjitaH |
pravaasa.n svapuraavaasa.n sa bhavedraajavallabhaH || 62||
na kuryaannaranaathasya yoShidbhiH saha sa.ngatim |
na nindaa.n na vivaada.n ca sa bhavedraajavallabhaH || 63||

karaTaka aaha \- atha bhavaa.nstatra gatvaa ki.n taavatprathama.n
vakShyati tattaavaducyataam | damanaka aaha \-

uttaraaduttara.n vaakya.n vadataa.n sa.nprajaayate |
suvR^iShTiguNasampannaadbiijaadbiijamivaaparam || 64||
apaayasa.ndarshanajaa.n vipattimupaayasa.ndarshanajaa.n ca siddhim |
medhaavino niitiguNaprayuktaa.n puraH sphurantiimiva varNayanti || 65||
ekeShaa.n vaaci shukavadanyeShaa.n hR^idi muukavat |
hR^idi vaaci tathaanyeShaa.n valgu valganti suuktayaH || 66||

na caahamapraaptakaala.n vakShye | aakarNita.n mayaa niitisaara.n pituH
puurvamutsa~Nga.n hi niShevataa |

apraaptakaala.n vacana.n bR^ihaspatirapi bruvan |
labhate bahvavadnyaanamapamaana.n ca puShkalam || 67||

karaTaka aaha \-

duraaraadhyaa hi raajaanaH parvataa iva sarvadaa |
vyaalaakiirNaaH suviShamaaH kaThinaa duShTasevitaaH || 68||

tathaa ca \-

bhoginaH ka~ncukaaviShTaaH kuTilaaH kruuraceShTitaaH |
suduShTaa mantrasaadhyaashca raajaanaH pannagaa iva || 69||
dvijihvaaH kruurakarmaaNo.aniShTaashChidraanusaariNaH |
duurato.api hi pashyanti raajaano bhujagaa iva || 70||
svalpamapyapakurvanti ye.abhiiShTaa hi mahiipateH |
te vahnaaviva dahyante pata~NgaaH paapacetasaH || 71||
duraaroha.n pada.n raadnyaa.n sarvalokanamaskR^itam |
svalpenaapyapakaareNa braahmaNyamiva duShyati || 72||
duraaraadhyaaH shriyo raaj~naa.n duraapaa duShparigrahaaH |
tiShThantyaapa ivaadhaare ciramaatmani sa.nsthitaaH || 73||

damanaka aaha \- satyametatparam | ki.n tu \-

yasya yasya hi yo bhaavastena tena samaacaret |
anupravishya medhaavii kShipramaatmavasha.n nayet || 74||
bhartushcittaanuvartitva.n suvR^itta.n caanujiivinaam |
raakShasaashcaapi gR^ihyante nitya.n ChandaanuvartibhiH || 75||
saruShi nR^ipe stutivacana.n tadabhimate prema taddviShi dveShaH |
taddaanasya ca sha.nsaa amantratantra.n vashiikaraNam || 76||

karaTaka aaha \- yadyevamabhimata.n tarhi shivaaste panthaanaH
santu | yathaabhilaShitamanuShThiiyataam | so.api praNamya
pi~Ngalakaabhimukha.n pratasthe | athaagacChanta.n damanaka\-
maalokya pi~Ngalako dvaaHsthamabraviit \- apasaaryataa.n
vetralataa | ayamasmaaka.n cirantano mantriputro damanako.avyaa\-
hatapraveshaH | tatpraveshyataa.n dvitiiyamaNDalabhaagii | iti | sa
aaha \- yathaavaadiidbhagavaaniti | athopasR^itya damanako
nirdiShTaasane pi~Ngalaka.n praNamya praaptaanudnya upaviShTaH |
sa tu tasya nakhakulishaala~NkR^ita.n dakShiNapaaNimupari dattvaa
maanapuraHsaramuvaaca \- api shiva.n bhavataH | kasmaacciraad
dR^iShTo.asi |damanaka aaha\- na ki.ncid devapaadaanaamasmaabhiH
prayojanam | para.n bhavataa.n praaptakaala.n vaktavya.n yata
uttamamadhyamaadhamaiH sarvairapi raadnyaa.n prayojanam |
ukta~nca \-

dantasya niShkoShaNakena nitya.n
           karNasya kaNDuuyanakena vaapi |
tR^iNena kaarya.n bhavatiishvaraaNaa.n
           kima~Ngavaagghastavataa nareNa || 77||

tathaa vaya.n devapaadaanaamanvayaagataa bhR^ityaa aapatsvapi
pR^iShThagaamino yadyapi svamadhikaara.n na labhaamahe tathaapi
devapaadaanaametadyukta.n na bhavati | ukta~nca \-

sthaaneShveva niyoktavyaa bhR^ityaa aabharaNaani ca |
na hi cuuDaamaNiH paade prabhavaamiiti badhyate || 78||

yataH \-

anabhij~no guNaanaa.n yo na bhR^ityairanugamyate |
dhanaaDhyo.api kuliino.api kramaayaato.api bhuupatiH || 79||

ukta~nca \-

asamaiH samiiyamaanaH samaishca parihiiyamaaNasatkaaraH |
dhuri yo na yujyamaanastribhirarthapati.n tyajati bhR^ityaH || 80||

yaccaavivekitayaa raajaa bhR^ityaanuttamapadayogyaanhiinaadhamasthaane
niyojayati na te tatraiva tiShThanti sa bhuupaterdoSho na teShaam |
ukta~nca \-

kanakabhuuShaNasa~NgrahaNocito
           yadi maNistrapuNi pratibadhyate |
na sa virauti na caapi sa shobhate
           bhavati yojayiturvacaniiyataa || 81||

yacca svaamyeva.n vadati ciraaddR^ishyate | tadapi shruuyataam \-

savyadakShiNayoryatra visheSho naasti hastayoH |
kastatra kShaNamapyaaryo vidyamaanagatirbhavet || 82||
kaace maNirmaNau kaaco yeShaa.n buddhirvikalpate |
na teShaa.n sannidhau bhR^ityo naamamaatro.api tiShThati || 83||
pariikShakaa yatra na santi deshe
           naarghanti ratnaani samudrajaani |
aabhiiradeshe kila candrakaanta.n
           tribhirvaraaTairvipaNanti gopaaH || 84||
lohitaakhyasya ca maNeH padmaraagasya caantaram |
yatra naasti katha.n tatra kriyate ratnavikrayaH || 85||
nirvisheSha.n yadaa svaamii sama.n bhR^ityeShu vartate |
tatrodyamasamarthaanaamutsaahaH parihiiyate || 86||
na vinaa paarthivo bhR^ityairna bhR^ityaaH paarthiva.n vinaa |
teShaa.n ca vyavahaaro.aya.n parasparanibandhanaH || 87||
bhR^ityairvinaa svaya.n raajaa lokaanugrahakaaribhiH |
mayuukhairiva diiptaa.nshustejasvyapi na shobhate || 88||
araiH sandhaaryate naabhirnaabhau caaraaH pratiShThitaaH |
svaamisevakayoreva.n vR^itticakra.n pravartate || 89||
shirasaa vidhR^itaa nitya.n snehena paripaalitaaH |
keshaa api virajyante niHsnehaaH ki.n na sevakaaH || 90||
raajaa tuShTo hi bhR^ityaanaamarthamaatra.n prayacChati |
te tu sa.nmaanamaatreNa praaNairapyupakurvate || 91||
eva.n dnyaatvaa narendreNa bhR^ityaaH kaaryaa vicakShaNaaH |
kuliinaaH shauryasa.nyuktaaH shaktaa bhaktaaH kramaagataaH || 92||
yaH kR^itvaa sukR^ita.n raadnyo duShkara.n hitamuttamam |
lajjayaa vakti no ki~ncittena raajaa sahaayavaan || 93||
yasminkR^itya.n samaaveshya nirvisha~Nkena cetasaa |
aasyate sevakaH sa syaatkalatramiva caaparam || 94||
yo.anaahuutaH samabhyeti dvaari tiShThati sarvadaa |
pR^iShTaH satya.n mita.n bruute sa bhR^ityo.arho mahiibhujaam || 95||
anaadiShTo.api bhuupasya dR^iShTvaa haanikara.n ca yaH |
yatate tasya naashaaya sa bhR^ityo.arho mahiibhujaam || 96||
taaDito.api durukto.api daNDito.api mahiibhujaa |
yo na cintayate paapa.n sa bhR^ityo.arho mahiibhujaam || 97||
na garva.n kurute maane naapamaane ca tapyate |
svaakaara.n rakShayedyastu sa bhR^ityo.arho mahiibhujaam || 98||
na kShudhaa piiDyate yastu nidrayaa na kadaacana |
na ca shiitaatapaadyaishca sa bhR^ityo.arho mahiibhujaam || 99||
shrutvaa saa.ngraamikii.n vaartaa.n bhaviShyaa.n svaamina.n prati |
prasannaasyo bhavedyastu sa bhR^ityo.arho mahiibhujaam || 100||
siimaa vR^iddhi.n samaayaati shuklapakSha ivoDuraaT |
niyogasa.nsthite yasminsa bhR^ityo.arho mahiibhujaam || 101||
siimaa sa.nkocamaayaati vahnau carma ivaahitam |
sthite yasminsa tu tyaajyo bhR^ityo raajya.n samiihataa || 102||

tathaa shR^igaalo.ayamiti manyamaanena mamopari svaaminaa
yadyavadnyaa kriyate tadapyayuktam | ukta~nca yataH \-

kausheya.n kR^imija.n suvarNamupalaadduurvaapi goromataH
pa~Nkaattaamarasa.n shashaa~Nka udadherindiivara.n gomayaat |
kaaShThaadagniraheH phaNaadapi maNirgopittato rocanaa
praakaashya.n svaguNodayena guNino gacChanti ki.n janmanaa || 103||
muuShikaa gR^ihajaataapi hantavyaa svaapakaariNii |
bhakShyapradaanairmaarjaaro hitakR^itpraapyate janaiH || 104||
eraNDabhiNDaarkanalaiH prabhuutairapi sa~ncitaiH |
daarukR^itya.n yathaa naasti tathaivaadnyaiH prayojanam || 105||
ki.n bhaktenaasamarthena ki.n shaktenaapakaariNaa |
bhakta.n shakta.n ca maa.n raajannaavadnyaatu.n tvamarhasi || 106||

pi~Ngalaka aaha \- bhavatveva.n taavat | asamarthaH samartho vaa
cirantanastvamasmaaka.n mantriputraH | tadvishrabdha.n bruuhi
yatki~ncidvaktukaamaH | damanaka aaha \- deva vidnyaapya.n ki~ncidasti |
pi~Ngalaka aaha \- tannivedayaabhipretam | so.abraviit \-

api svalpatara.n kaarya.n yadbhavetpR^ithiviipateH |
tanna vaacya.n sabhaamadhye provaaceda.n bR^ihaspatiH || 107||

tadaikaantike madvidnyaapyamaakarNayantu devapaadaaH | yataH \-

ShaTkarNo bhidyate mantrashcatuShkarNaH sthiro bhavet |
tasmaat sarvaprayatnena ShaTkarNa.n varjayetsudhiiH || 108||

atha pi~Ngalakaabhipraayadnyaa vyaaghradviipivR^ikapuraHsaraa sarve.api
tadvacaH samaakarNya sa.nsadi tatkShaNaadeva duuriibhuutaaH | tatashca
damanaka aaha \- udakagrahaNaartha.n pravR^ittasya svaaminaH kimiha
nivR^ittyaavasthaanam | pi~Ngalaka aaha savilakShasmitam\- na ki~ncidapi |
so.abraviit \- deva yadyanaakhyeya.n tattiShThatu | ukta~nca \-

daareShu ki~ncitsvajaneShu ki~ncidgopya.n vayasyeShu suteShu ki~ncit |
yukta.n na vaa yuktamida.n vicintya vadedvipashcinmahato.anurodhaat || 109 ||

tacChrutvaa pi~Ngalakashcintayaamaasa\- yogyo.aya.n dR^ishyate |
tatkathayaamyetasyaagra aatmano.abhipraayam | ukta~nca \-

svaamini guNaantaradnye guNavati bhR^itye.anuvartini kalatre |
suhR^idi nirantaracitte nivedya duHkha.n sukhii bhavati || 110 ||

bho damanaka shR^iNoShi shabda.n duuraanmahaantam | so.abraviit\-
svaamin shR^iNomi | tatkim | pi~Ngalaka aaha \- bhadra
ahamasmaadvanaadgantumicChaami | damanaka aaha \- kasmaat |pi~Ngalaka
aaha \- yato.adyaasmadvane kimapyapuurva.n sattva.n praviShTa.n yasyaaya.n
mahaashabdaH shruuyate | tasya ca shabdaanuruupeNa paraakrameNa
bhavitavyamiti | damanaka aaha \- yacChabdamaatraadapi bhayamupagataH
svaamii tadapyayuktam | ukta~nca \-

ambhasaa bhidyate setustathaa mantro.apyarakShitaH |
paishunyaadbhidyate sneho bhidyate vaagbhiraaturaH || 111||

tanna yukta.n svaaminaH puurvopaarjita.n vana.n tyaktu.n yato bheriiveNu\-
viinaamR^ida~NgataalapaTahasha~Nkhakaahalaadibhedena shabdaa
anekavidhaa bhavanti | tanna kevalaacChabdamaatraadapi bhetavyam |
ukta~nca \-

atyutkaTe ca raudre ca shatrau praapte na hiiyate |
dhairya.n yasya mahiinaatho na sa yaati paraabhavam || 112||
darshitabhaye.api dhaatari dhairyadhva.nso bhavenna dhiiraaNaam |
shoShitasarasi nidaaghe nitaraamevoddhataH sindhuH || 113||

tathaa ca \-
yasya na vipadi viShaadaH sa.npadi harSho raNe na bhiirutvam |
ta.n bhuvanatrayatilaka.n janayati jananii suta.n viralam || 114||

tathaa ca \-

shaktivaikalyanamrasya niHsaaratvaallaghiiyasaH |
janmino maanahiinasya tR^iNasya ca samaa gatiH || 115||

api ca \-

anyaprataapamaasaadya yo dR^iDhatva.n na gacChati |
jatujaabharaNasyeva ruupeNaapi hi tasya kim || 116||

tadeva.n dnyaatvaa svaaminaa dhairyaavaShTambhaH kaaryaH | na shabda\-
maatraadbhetavyam | api ca \-

puurvameva mayaa dnyaata.n puurNametaddhi medasaa |
anupravishya vidnyaata.n yaavaccarma ca daaru ca || 117||

pi~Ngalaka aaha \- kathametat | so.abraviit \-

