kathaa 2
shR^igaaladundubhikathaa |

kashcidgomaayurnaama shR^igaalaH kShutkShaamakaNTha itastataH
paribhramanvane sainyadvayasa.ngraamabhuumimapashyat | tasyaa.n ca
dundubheH patitasya vaayuvashaadvalliishaakhaagrairhanyamaanasya
shabdamashR^iNot | atha kShubhitahR^idayashcintayaamaasa aho
vinaShTo.asmi | tadyaavannaasya proccaaritashabdasya dR^iShTigocare
gacChaami taavadanyato vrajaami | athavaa naitadyujyate sahasaiva |

bhaye vaa yadi vaa harShe sa.npraapte yo vimarshayet |
kR^itya.n na kurute vegaanna sa santaapamaapnuyaat || 118||

tattaavajjaanaami kasyaaya.n shabdaH | dhairyamaalambya vimarshayan\-
yaavanmanda.n manda.n gacChati taavaddundubhimapashyat | sa ca ta.n
paridnyaaya samiipa.n gatvaa svayameva kautukaadataaDayat | bhuuyashca
harShaadacintayat \- aho ciraadetadasmaaka.n mahadbhojanamaapatitam |
tannuuna.n maa.nsamedo.asR^igbhiH paripuurita.n bhaviShyati | tataH
paruShacarmaavaguNThita.n tatkathamapi vidaaryaikadeshe Chidra.n kR^itvaa
sa.nhR^iShTamanaa madhye praviShTaH | para.n carmavidaaraNato
da.nShTraabha~NgaH samajani | atha niraashiibhuutastaddaarusheSha\-
mavalokya shlokamenamapaThat puurvameva mayaa dnyaatam iti | ato na
shabdamaatraadbhetavyam | pi~Ngalaka aaha\- bhoH pashyaaya.n mama
sarvo.api parigraho bhayavyaakulitamanaaH palaayitumicChati | tatkathamaha.n
dhairyaadavaShTambha.n karomi | so.abraviit\- svaaminnaiShaameSha doShaH |
yataH svaamisadR^ishaa eva bhavanti bhR^ityaaH | ukta~nca \-

ashvaH shastra.n shaastra.n viiNaa vaaNii narashca naarii ca |
puruShavisheSha.n praaptaa bhavantyayogyaashca yogyaashca || 119 ||

tatpauruShaavaShTambha.n kR^itvaa tva.n taavadatraiva pratipaalaya
yaavadahametacChabdasvaruupa.n dnyaatvaa aagacChaami | tataHpashcaad
yathocita.n kaaryamiti | pi~Ngalaka aaha \- ki.n tatra bhavaan
gantumutsahate | sa aaha\- ki.n svaamyaadeshaatsadbhR^ityasya
kR^ityaakR^ityamasti | ukta~nca \-

svaamyaadeshaatsubhR^ityasya na bhiiH sa~njaayate kvacit |
pravishenmukhamaaheya.n dustara.n vaa mahaarNavam || 120||

tathaa ca \-

svaamyaadiShTastu yo bhR^ityaH sama.n viShamameva ca |
manyate na sa sandhaaryo bhuubhujaa bhuutimicChataa || 121||

pi~Ngalaka aaha \- bhadra.n yadyeva.n tadgacCha | shivaaste panthaanaH
santviti | damanako.api ta.n praNamya sa.njiivakashabdaanusaarii
pratasthe | atha damanake gate bhayavyaakulamanaaH
pi~Ngalakashcintayaamaasa \- aho na shobhana.n kR^ita.n mayaa |
yattasya vishvaasa.n gatvaatmaabhipraayo niveditaH | kadaacid
damanako.ayamubhayavetano bhuutvaa mamopari duShTabuddhiH
syaadbhraShTaadhikaaratvaat | ukta~nca \-

ye bhavanti mahiipasya sammaanitavimaanitaaH |
yatante tasya naashaaya kuliinaa api sarvadaa || 122||

tattaavadasya cikiirShita.n vettumanyatsthaanaantara.n gatvaa
pratipaalayaami | kadaaciddamanakastamaadaaya maa.n
vyaapaadayitumicChati | ukta~nca \-

na badhyante hyavishvastaa balibhirdurbalaa api |
vishvastaastveva badhyante balavanto.api durbalaiH || 123||
bR^ihaspaterapi praadnyo na vishvaasa.n vrajennaraH |
ya icChedaatmano vR^iddhimaayuShya.n ca sukhaani ca || 124||
shapathaiH sandhitasyaapi na vishvaase vrajedripoH |
raajyalobhaadyato vR^itraH shakreNa shapathairhataH || 125||
na vishvaasa.n vinaa shatrurdevaanaamapi sidhyati |
vishvaasaattridashendreNa ditergarbho vidaaritaH || 126||

eva.n sa.npradhaarya sthaanaantara.n gatvaa damanakamaargamavaloka\-
yannekaakii tasthau | damanako.api sa.njiivakasakaasha.n gatvaa
vR^iShabho.ayamiti paridnyaaya hR^iShTamanaa vyacintayat \- aho
shobhanamaapatitam | anenaitasya sandhivigrahadvaareNa mama pi~Ngalako
vashyo bhaviShyatiiti | ukta~nca \-

na kauliinaanna sauhaardaannR^ipo vaakye pravartate |
mantriNaa.n yaavadabhyeti vyasana.n shokameva ca || 127||
sadaivaapadgato raajaa bhogyo bhavati mantriNaam |
ata eva hi vaa~nChanti mantriNaH saapada.n nR^ipam || 128||
yathaa necChati niirogaH kadaacitsucikitsakam |
tathaapadrahito raajaa saciva.n naabhivaa~nChati || 129||

eva.n vicintayanpi~NgalakaabhimukhaH pratasthe | pi~Ngalako.api
tamaayaanta.n prekShya svaakaara.n rakShanyathaapuurvasthitaH |
damanako.api pi~Ngalakasakaasha.n gatvaa praNamyopaviShTaH |
pi~Ngalaka aaha\- ki.n dR^iShTa.n bhavataa tatsattvam |damanaka aaha\-
dR^iShTa.n svaamiprasaadaat | pi~Ngalaka aaha\- api satyam | damanaka
aaha\- ki.n svaamipaadaanaamagre.asatya.n vidnyaapyate | ukta~nca \-

api svalpamasatya.n yaH puro vadati bhuubhujaam |
devaanaa.n ca vinashyeta sa druta.n sumahaanapi || 130||

tathaa ca \-

sarvadevamayo raajaa manunaa sa.nprakiirtitaH |
tasmaatta.n devavatpashyenna vyaliikena karhicit || 131||
sarvadevamayasyaapi visheSho nR^ipaterayam |
shubhaashubhaphala.n sadyo nR^ipaaddevaadbhavaantare || 132||

pi~Ngalaka aaha \- satya.n dR^iShTa.n bhaviShyati bhavataa | na diinopari
mahaantaH kupyantiiti na tva.n tena nipaatitaH | yataH \-

tR^iNaani nonmuulayati prabha~njano
           mR^iduuni niicaiH praNataani sarvataH |
svabhaava evonnatacetasaamaya.n
           mahaanmahatsveva karoti vikramam || 133||

api ca \-

gaNDasthaleShu madavaariShu baddharaaga\-
           mattabhramadbhramarapaadatalaahato.api |
kopa.n na gacChati nitaantabalo.api naaga\-
           stulye bale tu balavaanparikopameti || 134||

damanaka aaha \- astveva.n sa mahaatmaa vaya.n kR^ipaNaaH | tathaapi
svaamii yadi kathayati tato bhR^ityatve niyojayaami | pi~Ngalaka aaha
socChvaasam \- ki.n bhavaa~nChaknotyeva.n kartum | damanaka aaha \-
kimasaadhya.n buddherasti | ukta~nca \-

na tacChastrairna naagendrairna hayairna padaatibhiH |
kaarya.n sa.nsiddhimabhyeti yathaa buddhyaa prasaadhitam || 135||

pi~Ngalaka aaha \- yadyeva.n tarhyamaatyapade.adhyaaropitastvam |
adyaprabhR^iti prasaadanigrahaadika.n tvayaiva kaaryamiti nishcayaH |atha
damanakaH satvara.n gatvaa saakShepa.n tamidamaaha \- ehyehiito
duShTavR^iShabha | svaamii pi~Ngalakastvaamaakaarayati | ki.n niHsha~Nko
bhuutvaa muhurmuhurnadasi vR^ithaa iti| tacChrutvaa sa.njiivako.abraviit \-
bhadra ko.aya.n pi~NgalakaH | damanaka aaha \- ki.n svaamina.n
pi~Ngalakamapi na jaanaasi | tatkShaNa.n pratipaalaya | phalenaiva
dnyaasyasi | nanvaya.n sarvamR^igaparivR^ito vaTatale svaamii
pi~Ngalakanaamaa si.nhastiShThati | tacChrutvaa gataayuShamivaatmaana.n
manyamaanaH sa.njiivakaH para.n viShaadamagamat | aaha ca \-
bhadra bhavaansaadhusamaacaaro vacanapaTushca dR^ishyate | tadyadi
maamavashya.n tatra nayasi tadabhayapradaanena svaaminaH sakaashaat
prasaadaH kaarayitavyaH | damanaka aaha \- bhoH satyamabhihita.n
bhavataa | niitireShaa yataH \-

paryanto labhyate bhuumeH samudrasya girerapi |
na katha~ncinmahiipasya cittaantaH kenacitkvacit || 136||

tattvamatraiva tiShTha yaavadaha.n ta.n samaye dR^iShTvaa tataH
pashcaattvaamanayaami iti | tathaanuShThite damanakaH pi~Ngalaka\-
sakaasha.n gatvedamaaha \- svaamin na tatpraakR^ita.n sattvam| sa hi
bhagavato maheshvarasya vaahanabhuuto vR^iShabha iti | mayaa pR^iShTa
idamuuce | maheshvareNa parituShTena kaalindiiparisare shaShpaagraaNi
bhakShayitu.n samaadiShTaH | ki.n bahunaa mama pradatta.n bhagavataa
kriiDaartha.n vanamidam | pi~Ngalaka aaha sabhayam \- satya.n dnyaata.n
mayaadhunaa | na devataaprasaada.n vinaa shaShpabhojino vyaalaakiirNa
eva.nvidhe vane niHsha~Nka.n nandanto bhramanti | tatastvayaa
kimabhihitam | damanaka aaha\-svaamin etadabhihita.n mayaa yadetadvana.n
caNDikaavaahanabhuutasya pi~Ngalakasya viShayiibhuutam | tadbhavaan
abhyaagataH priyo.atithiH | tattasya sakaasha.n gatvaa bhraatR^isnehenaikatra
bhakShaNapaanaviharaNakriyaabhirekasthaanaashrayeNa kaalo neyaH iti |
tatastenaapi sarvametatpratipannam | ukta~nca saharSha.n svaaminaH
sakaashaadabhayadakShiNaa daapayitavyaa iti | tadatra svaamii pramaaNam|
tacChrutvaa pi~Ngalaka aaha \- saadhu sumate saadhu | mantrishrotriya
saadhu | mama hR^idayena saha sa.nmantrya bhavatedamabhihitam |
taddattaa mayaa tasyaabhayadakShiNaa | para.n so.api madarthe\-
.abhayadakShiNaa.n yaacayitvaa drutataramaaniiyataamiti | atha saadhu
cedamucyate \-

antaHsaarairakuTilairacChidraiH supariikShitaiH |
mantribhirdhaaryate raajya.n sustambhairiva mandiram || 137||

tathaa ca \-

mantriNaa.n bhinnasandhaane bhiShajaa.n saannipaatike |
karmaNi vyajyate pradnyaa svasthe ko vaa na paNDitaH || 138||

damanako.api ta.n praNamya sa.njiivakasakaasha prasthitaH saharSha\-
macintayat \-  aho prasaadasa.nmukho naH svaamii vacanavashagashca
sa.nvR^ittaH | tannaasti dhanyataro mama | ukta~nca \-

amR^ita.n shishire vahniramR^ita.n priyadarshanam |
amR^ita.n raajasa.nmaanamamR^ita.n kShiirabhojanam || 139||

atha sa.njiivakasakaashamaasaadya saprashrayamuvaaca \- bho mitra
praarthito.asau mayaa bhavadarthe svaamyabhayapradaanam |
tadvishrabdha.n gamyataam iti | para.n tvayaa raajaprasaadamaasaadya
mayaa saha samayadharmeNa vartitavyam | na garvamaasaadya
svaprabhutayaa vicaraNiiyam | ahamapi tava sa~Nketena sarvaa.n
raajyadhuramamaatyapadaviimaashrityoddhariShyaami | eva.n kR^ite
dvayorapyaavayo raajalakShmiirbhogyaa bhaviShyati | yataH \-

aakheTakasya dharmeNa vibhavaaH syurvashe nR^iNaam |
nR^iprajaaH prerayatyeko hantyanyo.atra mR^igaaniva || 140 ||

tathaa ca \-

yo na puujayate garvaaduttamaadhamamadhyamaan |
nR^ipaasannaatsa maanyo.api bhrashyate dantilo yathaa || 141 ||

sa.njiivaka aaha \- katham etat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 3
dantilagorambhakathaa  |

astyatra dharaatale vardhamaana.n naama nagaram | tatra dantilo naama
naanaabhaaNDapatiH sakalapuranaayakaH prativasati sma | tena purakaarya.n
nR^ipakaarya.n ca kurvataa tuShTi.n niitaastatpuravaasino lokaa nR^ipatishca |
ki.n bahunaa na ko.api taadR^ikkenaapi caturo dR^iShTo shruto vaa | athavaa
satyametaduktam \-

narapatihitakartaa dveShyataa.n yaati loke
           janapadahitakartaa tyajyate paarthivendraiH |
iti mahati virodhe vartamaane samaane
           nR^ipatijanapadaanaa.n durlabhaH kaaryakartaa || 142||

athaiva.n gacChati kaale dantilasya kadaacidvivaahaH sa.npravR^ittaH |
tatra tena sarve puranivaasino raajasa.nnidhilokaashca sammaanapuraH\-
saramaamantrya bhojitaa vastraadibhiH satkR^itaashca | tato vivaahaanantara.n
raajaa saantaHpuraH svagR^ihamaaniiyaabhyarcitaH | atha tasya
nR^ipatergR^ihasammaarjanakartaa gorambho naama raajasevako
gR^ihaayaato.api tenaanucitasthaana upaviShTo.avadnyayaardhacandra.n
dattvaa niHsaaritaH | so.api tataH prabhR^iti nishvasannapamaanaanna
raatraavapyadhishete | katha.n mayaa tasya bhaaNDapate raajaprasaadahaaniH
kartavyaa iti cintayannaaste | athavaa kimanena vR^ithaa shariirashoShaNena |
na ki.ncinmayaa tasyaapakartu.n shakyamiti | athavaa saadhvidamucyate \-

yo hyapakartumashaktaH kupyati kimasau naro.atra nirlajjaH |
utpatito.api hi caNakaH shaktaH ki.n bhraaShTraka.n bha~Nktum || 143||

atha kadaacitpratyuuShe yoganidraa.n gatasya raadnyaH shayyaante
maarjana.n kurvannidamaaha \- aho dantilasya mahaddR^iptatva.n
yadraajamahiShiimaali~Ngati | tacChrutvaa raajaa sasambhramamutthaaya
tamuvaaca \- bho bho gorambha | satyametadyattvayaa jalpitam | ki.n
dantilena samaali~Ngitaa iti | gorambhaH praaha \- deva raatrijaagaraNena
dyuutaasaktasya me balaannidraa samaayaataa | tanna vedmi ki.n
mayaabhihitam | raajaa serShya.n svagatameSha taavadasmadgR^ihe\-
.apratihatagatistathaa dantilo.api | tatkadaacidanena devii
samaali~Ngyamaanaa dR^iShTaa bhaviShyati | tenedamabhihitam |
ukta~nca \-

yadvaa~nChati divaa martyo viikShate vaa karoti vaa |
tat svapne.api tadabhyaasaadbruute vaatha karoti vaa || 144||

tathaa ca \-

shubha.n vaa yadi va paapa.n yannR^iNaa.n hR^idi sa.nsthitam |
suguuDhamapi tajdnyeya.n svapnavaakyaattathaa madaat || 145||

athavaa striiNaa.n viShaye ko.atra sandehaH |

jalpanti saardhamanyena pashyantyanya.n savibhramaaH |
hR^idgata.n cintayantyanya.n priyaH ko naama yoShitaam || 146||

anyacca \-

ekena smitapaaTalaadhararuco jalpantyanalpaakSharam |
viikShante.anyamitaH sphuTatkumudiniiphullollasallocanaaH |
duurodaaracaritracitravibhava.n dhyaayanti caanya.n dhiyaa |
kenettha.n paramaarthato.arthavadiva premaasti vaamabhruvaam || 147||

tathaa ca \-

naagnistR^ipyati kaaShThaanaa.n naapagaanaa.n mahodadhiH |
naantakaH sarvabhuutaanaa.n na pu.nsaa.n vaamalocanaa || 148||
raho naasti kShaNo naasti naasti praarthayitaa naraH |
tena naarada naariiNaa.n satiitvamupajaayate || 149||
yo mohaanmanyate muuDho rakteya.n mama kaaminii |
sa tasyaa vashago nitya.n bhavetkriiDaashakuntavat || 150||
taasaa.n vaakyaani kR^ityaani svalpaani suguruuNyapi |
karoti sa kR^itairloke laghutva.n yaati sarvataH || 151||
striya.n ca yaH praarthayate sannikarSha.n ca gacChati |
iiShacca kurute sevaa.n tamevecChanti yoShitaH || 152||
anarthitvaanmanuShyaaNaa.n bhayaatparijanasya ca |
maryaadaayaamamaryaadaaH striyastiShThanti sarvadaa || 153||
naasaa.n kashcidagamyo.asti naasaa.n ca vayasi sthitiH |
viruupa.n ruupavanta.n vaa pumaanityeva bhujyate || 154||
rakto hi jaayate bhogyo naariiNaa.n shaaTikaa yathaa |
ghR^iShyante yo dashaalambii nitambe viniveshitaH || 155||
alaktako yathaa rakto niShpiiDya puruShastathaa |
abalaabhirbalaadraktaH paadamuule nipaatyate || 156||

eva.n sa raajaa bahuvidha.n vilapya tataH prabhR^iti dantilasya prasaada\-
paraa~NmukhaH sa.njaataH | ki.n bahunaa raajadvaarapravesho.api tasya
nivaaritaH | dantilo.apyakasmaadeva prasaadaparaa~Nmukhamavanipati\-
mavalokya cintayaamaasa \- aho saadhu cedamucyate \-

ko.arthaanpraapya na garvito viShayiNaH kasyaapado.asta.n gataaH |
striibhiH kasya na khaNDita.n bhuvi manaH ko naamaa raadnyaa.n priyaH |
kaH kaalasya na gocaraantaragataH ko.arthii gato gauravam |
ko vaa durjanavaaguraasu patitaH kShemeNa yaataH pumaan || 157||

tathaa ca \-

kaake shauca.n dyuutakaareShu satya.n
           sarpe kShaantiH striiShu kaamopashaantiH |
kliibe dhairya.n madyape tattvacintaa
           raajaa mitra.n kena dR^iShTa.n shruta.n vaa || 158||

apara.n mayaasya bhuupaterathavaanyasyaapi kasyacidraajasambandhinaH
svapne.api naaniShTa.n kR^itam | tatkimetatparaa~Nmukho maa.n prati
bhuupatiriti | eva.n ta.n dantila.n kadaacidraajadvaare viShkambhita.n vilokya
sa.nmaarjanakartaa gorambho vihasya dvaarapaalaanidamuuce \- bho bho
dvaarapaalaaH  raajaprasaadaadhiShThito.aya.n dantilaH svaya.n
nigrahaanugrahakartaa ca | tadanena nivaaritena yathaaha.n tathaa
yuuyamapyardhacandrabhaajino bhaviShyatha | tacChrutvaa
dantilashcintayaamaasa \- nuunamidamasya gorambhasya ceShTitam |
athavaa saadhvidamucyate \-

akuliino.api muurkho.api bhuupaala.n yo.atra sevate |
api sa.nmaanahiino.api sa sarvatra prapuujyate || 159||
api kaapuruSho bhiiruH syaaccennR^ipatisevakaH |
tathaapi na paraabhuuti.n janaadaapnoti maanavaH || 160||

eva.n sa bahuvidha.n vilapya vilakShamanaaH sodvego gataprabhaavaH
svagR^iha.n nishaamukhe gorambhamaahuuya vastrayugalena
sa.nmaanyedamuvaaca \- bhadra  mayaa na tadaa tva.n raagavashaanniH\-
saaritaH | yatastva.n braahmaNaanaamagrato.anucitasthaane samupaviShTo
dR^iShTa ityapamaanitaH | tatkShamyataam | so.api svargaraajyopama.n
tadvastrayugalamaasaadya para.n paritoSha.n gatvaa tamuvaaca \- bhoH
shreShThin  kShaanta.n mayaa te tat | tadasya sa.nmaanasya kR^ite pashya
me buddhiprabhaava.n raajaprasaada.n ca | evamuktvaa saparitoSha.n
niShkraantaH | saadhu cedamucyate \-

stokenonnatimaayaati stokenaayaatyadhogatim |
aho sasadR^ishaa ceShTaa tulaayaShTeH khalasya ca || 161||

tatashcaanyedyuH sa gorambho raajakula.n gatvaa yoganidraa.n gatasya
bhuupateH sa.nmaarjanakriyaa.n kurvannidamaaha \- aho aviveko.asmad\-
bhuupateH | yat puriiShotsargamaacara.nshcarbhaTiibhakShaNa.n karoti |
tacChrutvaa raajaa savismaya.n tamuvaaca \- re re gorambha  kimaprastuta.n
lapasi | gR^ihakarmakara.n matvaa tvaa.n na vyaapaadayaami | ki.n tvayaa
kadaacidahameva.nvidha.n karma samaacarandR^iShTaH | so.abraviit \-
dyuutaasaktasya raatrijaagaraNena sa.nmaarjana.n kurvaaNasya mama
balaannidraa samaayaataa | tayaadhiShThitena mayaa ki.ncijjalpitam |
tanna vedmi | tatprasaada.n karotu svaamii nidraaparavashasya iti | eva.n
shrutvaa raajaa cintitavaan \- yanmayaa janmaantare puriiShotsarga.n kurvataa
kadaapi cirbhaTikaa na bhakShitaa | tadyathaaya.n vyatikaro.asambhaavyo
mamaanena muuDhena vyaahR^itaHstathaa dantilasyaapiiti nishcayaH |
tanmayaa na yukta.n kR^ita.n yatsa varaakaH sa.nmaanena viyojitaH | na
taadR^ikpuruShaaNaameva.nvidha.n ceShTita.n sambhaavyate | tadabhaavena
raajakR^ityaani paurakR^ityaani  sarvaaNi shithilataa.n vrajanti | 
evamanekadhaa
  vimR^ishya dantila.n samaahuuya nijaa~NgavastraabharaNaadibhiH sa.nyojya
svaadhikaare niyojayaamaasa | ato.aha.n braviimi yo na puujayate garvaaditi |
sa.njiivaka aaha \- bhadra evamevaitat | yadbhavataabhihita.n tadeva mayaa
kartavyamiti | evamabhihite damanakastamaadaaya pi~Ngalakasakaasha\-
magamat | aaha ca \- deva eSha mayaaniitaH sa sa.njiivakaH | adhunaa devaH
pramaaNam | sa.njiivako.api ta.n saadara.n praNamyaagrataH savinaya.n
sthitaH | pi~Ngalako.api tasya piinaayatakakudmato nakhakulishaala.nkR^ita.n
dakShiNapaaNimupari dattvaa maanapuraHsaramuvaaca api shiva.n bhavataH |
kutastvamasminvane vijane samaayaato.asi |tenaapyaatmavR^ittaantaH kathitaH |
yathaa vardhamaanena  saha viyogaH sa.njaatastathaa sarva.n niveditam |
tacChrutvaa pi~NgalakaH saadaratara.n tamuvaaca \- vayasya na bhetavyam |
madbhujapa~njaraparirakShitena yathecCha.n tvayaadhunaa vartitavyam |
anyacca nitya.n matsamiipavartinaa bhaavyam | yataH kaaraNaadbahvapaaya.n
raudrasattvaniShevita.n vana.n guruuNaamapi sattvaanaamasevya.n kutaH
shaShpabhojinaam | evamuktvaa sakalamR^igaparivR^ito yamunaakacCha\-
mavatiiryodakagrahaNa.n kR^itvaa svecChayaa tadeva vana.n praviShTaH |
tatashca karakaTadamanakanikShiptaraajyabhaaraH sa.njiivikena saha
subhaaShitagoShThiimanubhavannaaste | athavaa saadhvidamucyate \-

yadR^icChayaapyupanata.n sakR^itsajjanasa~Ngatam |
bhavatyajaramatyanta.n naabhyaasakramamiikShate || 162||

sa.njiivakenaapyanekashaastraavagaahanaadutpannabuddhipraagalbhyena
stokairevaahobhirmuuDhamatiH pi~Ngalako dhiimaa.nstathaa kR^ito yathaa\-
.araNyadharmaadviyojya graamyadharmeShu niyojitaH | ki.n bahunaa pratyaha.n
pi~Ngalakasa.njiivakaaveva kevala.n rahasi mantrayataH | sheShaH sarvo.api
mR^igajano duuriibhuutastiShThati | karaTakadamanakaavapi pravesha.n na
labhete | anyacca si.nhaparaakramaabhaavaatsarvo.api mR^igajanastau ca
shR^igaalau kShudhaavyaadhibaadhitaa ekaa.n dishamaashritya sthitaaH |
ukta~nca \-

phalahiina.n nR^ipa.n bhR^ityaaH kuliinamapi connatam |
santyajyaanyatra gacChanti shuShka.n vR^ikShamivaaNDajaaH || 163||

tathaa ca \-

api sa.nmaanasa.nyuktaaH kuliinaa bhaktitatparaaH |
vR^ittibha~Ngaanmahiipaala.n tyajantyeva hi sevakaaH || 164||

anyacca \-

kaalaatikramaNa.n vR^itteryo na kurviita bhuupatiH |
kadaacitta.n na mu~ncanti bhartsitaa api sevakaaH || 165||

tathaa ca kevala.n sevakaa ittha.nbhuutaa yaavatsamastamapyetajjagat\-
paraspara.n bhakShaNaartha.n saamaadibhirupaayaistiShThati | tadyathaa \-

deshaanaamupari kShmaabhR^idaaturaaNaa.n cikitsakaaH |
vaNijo graahakaaNaa.n ca muurkhaaNaamapi paNDitaaH || 166||
pramaadinaa.n tathaa cauraa bhikShukaa gR^ihamedhinaam |
gaNikaaH kaaminaa.n caiva sarvalokasya shilpinaH || 167||
saamaadisajjitaiH paashaiH pratiikShante divaanisham |
upajiivanti shaktyaa hi jalajaa jaladaaniva || 168||

athavaa saadhvidamucyate \-

sarpaaNaa.n ca khalaanaa.n ca paradravyaapahaariNaam |
abhipraayaa na sidhyanti teneda.n vartate jagat || 169||
attu.n vaa~nChati shaambhavo gaNapateraakhu.n kShudhaartaH phaNii |
ta.n ca krau~ncaripoH shikhii girisutaasi.nho.api naagaashanam |
ittha.n yatra parigrahasya ghaTanaa shambhorapi syaadgR^ihe |
tatraanyasya katha.n na bhaavi jagato yasmaatsvaruupa.n hi tat || 170||

tataH svaamiprasaadarahitau kShutkShaamakaNThau paraspara.n karaTaka\-
damanakau mantrayete | tatra damanako bruute \- aarya karaTaka |
aavaa.n taavadapradhaanataa.n gatau | eSha pi~NgalakaH sa.njiivakaa\-
nuraktaH svavyaapaaraparaa~NmukhaH sa.njaataH | sarvo.api parijano gataH |
tatki.n kriyate | karaTaka aaha \- yadyapi tvadiiyavacana.n na karoti
tathaapi svaamii svadoShanaashaaya vaacyaH | ukta~nca \-

ashR^iNvannapi boddhavyo mantribhiH pR^ithiviipatiH |
yathaa svadoShanaashaaya vidureNaambikaasutaH || 171||

tathaa ca \-

madonmattasya bhuupasya ku~njarasya ca gacChataH |
unmaarga.n vaacyataa.n yaanti mahaamaatraaH samiipagaaH || 172||

tat tvayaiSha shaShpabhojii svaaminaH sakaashamaaniitaH |
tatsvahastenaa~NgaaraaH karShitaaH | damanaka aaha \- satyametat |
mamaaya.n doSho na svaaminaH | ukta~nca \-

jambuuko huDuyuddhena vaya.n caaShaaDhabhuutinaa |
duutikaa parakaaryeNa trayo doShaaH svaya.n kR^itaaH || 173||

karaTaka aaha \- kathametat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 4
devasharmaparivraajakakathaa |

asti kasmi.nshcidviviktapradeshe maThaayatanam | tatra devasharmaa naama
parivraajakaH prativasati sma | tasyaanekasaadhujanadattasuukShmavastra\-
vikrayavashaatkaalena mahatii vittamaatraa sa~njaataa | tataH sa na
kasyacidvishvasiti | nakta.n dina.n kakShaantaraattaa.n maatraa.n na
mu~ncati | athavaa saadhu cedamucyate \-

arthaanaamarjane duHkhamarjitaanaa.n ca rakShaNe |
naashe duHkha.n vyaye duHkha.n dhigarthaaH kaShTasa.nshrayaaH || 174||

athaa.aShaaDhabhuutirnaama paravittaapahaarii dhuurtastaamarthamaatraa.n
tasya kakShaantaragataa.n lakShayitvaa vyacintayat \- katha.n
mayaasyeyamarthamaatraa hartavyaa iti | tadatra maThe taavaddR^iDhashilaa\-
sa~ncayavashaadbhittibhedo na bhavati | uccaistaratvaacca dvaare pravesho
na syaat | tadena.n maayaavacanairvishvaasyaaha.n Chaatrataa.n vrajaami
yena sa vishvastaH kadaacidvishvaasameti | ukta~nca \-

nispR^iho naadhikaarii syaannaakaamii maNDanapriyaH |
naavidagdhaH priya.n bruuyaatsphuTavaktaa na va~ncakaH || 175||

eva.n nishcitya tasyaantikamupagamya AUM namaH shivaayeti proccaarya
saaShTaa~Nga.n praNamya ca saprashrayamuvaaca \- bhagavannasaaraH

sa.nsaaro.ayam | girinadiivegopama.n yauvanam | tR^iNaagnisama.n jiivitam |
sharadabhracChaayaasadR^ishaa bhogaaH | svapnasadR^isho mitraputra\-
kalatrabhR^ityavargasambandhaH | eva.n mayaa samyakparidnyaatam | tatki.n
kurvato me sa.nsaarasamudrottaraNa.n bhaviShyati | tacChrutvaa devasharmaa
saadaramaaha \- vatsa dhanyo.asi yatprathame vayasyeva.n viraktiibhaavaH |
ukta~nca \-

puurve vayasi yaH shaantaH sa shaanta iti me matiH |
dhaatuShu kShiiyamaaNeShu shamaH kasya na jaayate || 176||
aadau citte tataH kaaye sataa.n sa.njaayate jaraa |
asataa.n ca punaH kaaye naiva citte kadaacana || 177||

yacca maa.n sa.nsaarasaagarottaraNopaaya.n pR^icChasi |
tacChruuyataam \-

shuudro vaa yadi vaanyo.api caNDaalo.api jaTaadharaH |
diikShitaH shivamantreNa sa bhasmaa~Ngii shivo bhavet || 178||
ShaDakShareNa mantreNa puShpamekamapi svayam |
li~Ngasya muurdhni yo dadyaanna sa bhuuyo.abhijaayate || 179||

tacChrutvaa.aShaaDhabhuutistatpaadau gR^ihiitvaa saprashrayamidamaaha\-
bhagavan tarhi diikShayaa me.anugraha.n kuru | devasharmaa aaha \- vatsa
anugraha.n te kariShyaami | parantu raatrau tvayaa maThamadhye na
praveShTavyam | yatkaaraNa.n niHsa~Ngataa yatiinaa.n prashasyate
tava ca mamaapi ca | ukta~nca \-

durmantraannR^ipatirvinashyati yatiH sa~Ngaatsuto laalanaat |
vipro.anadhyayanaatkula.n kutanayaacChiila.n khalopaasanaat |
maitrii caapraNayaatsamR^iddhiranayaatsnehaH pravaasaashrayaat |
strii garvaadanavekShaNaadapi kR^iShistyaagaatpramaadaaddhanam || 180||

tattvayaa vratagrahaNaanantara.n maThadvaare tR^iNakuTiirake shayitavyamiti |
sa aaha \- bhagavan  bhavadaadeshaH pramaaNam | paratra hi tena me
prayojanam | atha kR^itashayanasamaya.n devasharmanigraha.n kR^itvaa
shaastroktavidhinaa shiShyataamanayat | so.api hastapaadaavamardanaadi\-
paricaryayaa ta.n paritoShamanayat | punastathaapi muniH
kakShaantaraanmaatraa.n na mu~ncati | athaiva.n gacChati kaala
aaShaaDhabhuutishcintayaamaasa \- aho na katha.ncideSha me
vishvaasamaagacChati | tatki.n divaapi shastreNa maarayaami ki.n vaa
viSha.n prayacChaami | ki.n vaa pashudharmeNa vyaapaadayaamiiti | eva.n
cintayatastasya devasharmaNo.api shiShyaputraH kashcidgraamaad\-
aamantraNaartha.n samaayaataH| praaha ca \- bhagavan pavitraaropaNa\-
kR^ite mama gR^ihamaagamyataamiti | tacChrutvaa devasharmaa.
aShaaDhabhuutinaa saha prahR^iShTamanaaH prasthitaH | athaiva.n
tasya gacChato.agre kaacinnadii samaayaataa | taa.n dR^iShTvaa maatraa.n
kakShaantaraadavataarya kanthaamadhye suguptaa.n nidhaaya snaatvaa
devaarcana.n vidhaaya tadanantaramaaShaaDhabhuutimidamaaha \- bho
aaShaaDhabhuute yaavadaha.n puriiShotsarga.n kR^itvaa samaagacChaami
taavadeShaa kanthaa yogeshvarasya saavadhaanatayaa rakShaNiiyaa |
ityuktvaa gataH | aaShaaDhabhuutirapi tasminnadarshaniibhuute
maatraamaadaaya satvara.n prasthitaH | devasharmaa.api ChaatraguNaanu\-
ra~njitamanaaH suvishvasto yaavadupaviShTastiShThati taavatsuvarNaroma\-
dehayuuthamadhye huDuyuddhamapashyat | atha roShavashaaddhuDu\-
yugalasya duuramapasaraNa.n kR^itvaa bhuuyo.api samupetya
lalaaTapaTTaabhyaa.n praharato bhuuri rudhira.n patati | tacca jambuuko
jihvaalaulyena ra~Ngabhuumi.n praveshyaasvaadayati | devasharmaa.api
tadaalokya vyacintayat \- aho mandamatiraya.n jambuukaH | yadi
kathamapyanayoH sa~NghaTTe patiShyati tannuuna.n mR^ityumavaapsyatiiti
vitarkayaami | kShaNaantare ca tathaiva raktaasvaadanalaulyaanmadhye
pravisha.nstayoH shiraHsampaate patito mR^itashca shR^igaalaH |
devasharmaa.api ta.n shocamaano maatraamuddishya shanaiH shanaiH
prasthito yaavadaaShaaDhabhuuti.n na pashyati tatashcautsukyena
shauca.n vidhaaya yaavatkanthaamaalokayati taavanmaatraa.n na
pashyati | tatashca haa haa muShito.asmiiti jalpanpR^ithiviitale muurcChayaa
nipapaata | tataH kShaNaaccetanaa.n labdhvaa bhuuyo.api samutthaaya
phuutkartumaarabdhaH \- bho aaShaaDhabhuute kva maa.n va~ncayitvaa
gato.asi | taddehi me prativacanam | eva.n bahu vilapya tasya padapaddhati\-
manveShayanshanaiH shanaiH prasthitaH | athaiva gacChansaayantanasamaye
ka~ncidgraamamaasasaada | atha tasmaadgraamaatkashcitkaulikaH sabhaaryo
madyapaanakR^ite samiipavartini nagare prasthitaH | devasharmaa.api tamaalokya
provaaca \- bho bhadra vaya.n suuryoDhaa atithayastavaantika.n praaptaaH | na
kamapyatra graame jaaniimaH | tadgR^ihyataamatithidharmaH | ukta~nca \-

sampraapto yo.atithiH saaya.n suuryoDhe gR^ihamedhinaam |
puujayaa tasya devatva.n prayaanti gR^ihamedhinaH || 181||

tathaa ca \-

tR^iNaani bhuumirudaka.n vaakcaturthii ca suunR^itaa |
sataametaani harmyeShu nocChidyante kadaacana || 182||
svaagatenaagnayastR^iptaa aasanena shatakratuH |
paadashaucena pitaro.arghaacChambhustathaatitheH || 183||

kauliko.api tacChrutvaa bhaaryaamaaha \- priye gacCha tvamatithimaadaaya
gR^iha.n prati paadashaucabhojanashayanaadibhiH satkR^itya tva.n tatraiva
tiShTha | aha.n tava kR^ite prabhuutamadyamaaneShyaami | evamuktvaa
prasthitaH | saa.api bhaaryaa pu.nshcalii tamaadaaya prahasitavadanaa
devadatta.n manasi  dhyaayantii gR^iha.n prati pratasthe | athavaa saadhu
cedamucyate \-

durdivase ghanatimire duHsa.ncaaraasu nagaraviithiiShu |
patyurvideshagamane paramasukha.n jaghanacapalaayaaH || 184||

tathaa ca \-

parya~NkeShvaastaraNa.n patimanukuula.n manohara.n shayanam |
tR^iNamiva laghu manyante kaaminyashcauryaratalubdhaaH || 185||

tathaa ca \-

keli.n pradahati lajjaa shR^i~Ngaaro.asthiini caaTavaH kaTavaH |
vandhatrayaaH paritoSho na ki.ncidiShTa.n bhavetpatyau || 186||
kulapatana.n janagarhaa.n bandhanamapi jiivitavyasandeham |
a~Ngiikaroti kulaTaa satata.n parapuruShasa.nsaktaa || 187||

atha kaulikabhaaryaa gR^iha.n gatvaa devasharmaNe gataastaraNa.n
bhagnaa.n ca khaTvaa.n samarpyedamaaha \- bho bhagavan yaavadaha.n
svasakhii.n graamaadabhyaagataa.n  sambhaavya drutamaagacChaami
taavattvayaa madgR^ihe.apramattena bhaavyam | evamabhidhaaya
shR^i~Ngaaravidhi.n vidhaaya yaavaddevadattamuddishya vrajati
taavattadbhartaa sa.nmukho madavihvalaa~Ngo muktakeshaH pade
pade praskhalangR^ihiitamadyabhaaNDaH samabhyeti | ta.n ca
dR^iShTvaa saa drutatara.n vyaaghuTya svagR^iha.n pravishya
muktashR^i~Ngaaraveshaa yathaapuurvamabhavat | kauliko.api taa.n
palaayamaanaa.n kR^itaadbhutashR^i~Ngaaraa.n vilokya praageva
karNaparamparayaa tasyaaH shrutaavapavaadakShubhitahR^idayaH
svaakaara.n niguuhamaanaH sadaivaaste | tatashca tathaavidha.n
ceShTitamavalokya dR^iShTapratyayaH krodhavashago gR^iha.n pravishya
taamuvaaca \- aaH paape pu.nshcali kva prasthitaasi |saa provaaca \- aha.n
tvatsakaashaadaagataa na kutracidapi nirgataa | tatkatha.n madyapaana\-
vashaadaprastuta.n vadasi | athavaa saadhvidamucyate \-

vaikalya.n dharaNiipaatamayathocitajalpanam |
sa.nnipaatasya cihnaani madya.n sarvaaNi darshayet || 188||
karaspando.ambaratyaagastejohaaniH saraagataa |
vaaruNiisa~Ngajaavasthaa bhaanunaapyanubhuuyate || 189||

so.api tacChrutvaa pratikuulavacana.n veshaviparyaya.n caavalokya tamaaha \-
pu.nshcali cirakaala.n shruto mayaa tavaapavaadaH | tadadya svaya.n
sa~njaatapratyayastava yathocita.n nigraha.n karomi | ityabhidhaaya
laguDaprahaaraistaa.n jarjaritadehaa.n vidhaaya sthuuNayaa saha
dR^iDhabandhanena baddhvaa so.api madavihvalo nidraavashamagamat |
etasminnantare tasyaaH sakhii naapitii kaulika.n nidraavasha.n vidnyaaya
taa.n gatvedamaaha \- sakhi sa devadattastasminsthaane tvaa.n pratiikShate |
tacChiighramaagamyataamiti | saa caaha \- pashya mamaavasthaam |
tatkatha.n gacChaami | tadgatvaa bruuhi ta.n kaamina.n yadasyaa.n raatrau
na tvayaa saha samaagamaH | naapitii praaha \- sakhi, maa maiva.n vada |
naaya.n kulaTaadharmaH | ukta~nca \-

viShamasthasvaaduphalagrahaNavyavasaayanishcayo yeShaam |
uShTraaNaamiva teShaa.n manye.aha.n sha.nsita.n janma || 190||

tathaa ca \-

sandigdhe paraloke janaapavaade ca jagati bahucitre |
svaadhiine pararamaNe dhanyaastaaruNyaphalabhaajaH || 191||

anyacca \-

yadi bhavati daivayogaatpumaanviruupo.api bandhako rahasi |
na tu kR^icChraadapi bhadra.n nijakaanta.n saa bhajatyeva || 192||

saa.abraviit \- yadyeva.n tarhi kathaya katha.n dR^iDhabandhanabaddhaa satii
tatra gacChaami | sannihitashcaaya.n paapaatmaa matpatiH | naapityaaha \-
sakhi madavihvalo.aya.n suuryakaraspR^iShTaH prabodha.n yaasyati | tadaha.n
  tvamunmocayaami | maamaatmasthaane baddhvaa drutatara.n devadatta.n
sambhaavyaagacCha | saa.abraviidevamastviti | tadanu saa naapitii taa.n
svasakhii.n bandhanaadvimocya tasyaaH sthaane yathaapuurvamaatmaana.n
baddhvaa taa.n devadattasakaashe  sa~Nketasthaana.n preShitavatii |
tathaanuShThite kaulikaH kasmi.nshcitkShaNe samutthaaya ki.ncidgatakopo
vimadastaamaaha \- he paruShavaadini yadadyaprabhR^iti gR^ihaanni\-
ShkramaNa.n na karoShi na ca paruSha.n vadasi tatastvaamunmocayaami |
naapityapi svarabhedabhayaadyaavanna ki.nciduuce taavatso.api bhuuyo
bhuuyastaa.n tadevaaha | atha saa yaavatpratyuttara.n kimapi na dadau
  taavatsa prakupitastiikShNashastramaadaaya naasikaamacChinat | aaha ca \-
re pu.nshcali tiShThedaaniim | tvaa.n bhuuyastoShayiShyaami | iti jalpan
punarapi nidraavashamagaat | devasharmaa.api vittanaashaatkShutkShaama\-
kaNTho naShTanidrastatsarva.n striicaritramapashyat | saa.api kaulikabhaaryaa
yathecChayaa devadattena saha suratasukhamanubhuuya kasmi.nshcitkShaNe
svagR^ihamaagataya taa.n naapitiimidamaaha \- ayi shiva.n bhavatyaaH | naaya.n
paapaatmaa mama gataayaa utthitaH | naapityaaha \- shiva.n naasikayaa vinaa
sheShasya shariirasya | taddruta.n  mocaya bandhanaadyaavannaaya.n maa.n
pashyati yena svagR^iha.n gacChaami | tathaanuShThite  bhuuyo.api kaulika
utthaaya taamaaha \- pu.nshcali kimadyaapi na vadasi ? ki.n bhuuyo.apyato
duShTatara.n nigraha.n karNacChedena karomi | atha saa sakopa.n saadhikShepa\-
midamaaha \- dhi~NmahaamuuDha ko maa.n mahaasatii.n dharShayitu.n
vya~Ngayitu.n vaa samarthaH | tacChR^iNvantu sarve.api lokapaalaaH |

aadityacandraharisha.nkaravaasavaadyaaH
           shaktaa na jetumatiduHkhakaraaNi yaani |
taaniindriyaaNi balavanti sudurjayaani
           ye nirjayanti bhuvane balinasta eke || 193||

tadyadi mama satiitvamasti manasaa.api parapuruSho naabhilaShitaH tato
devaa bhuuyo.api me naasikaa.n taadR^igruupaakShataa.n kurvantu | athavaa
yadi mama citte parapuruShasya bhraantirapi bhavati, maa.n
bhasmasaannayantu | evamuktvaa bhuuyo.api tamaaha \- bho duraatman
pashya me satiitvaprabhaaveNa taadR^ishyeva naasikaa sa.nvR^ittaa |
athaasaavulmukamaadaaya yaavatpashyati taavattadruupaa.n naasikaa.n
ca bhuutale raktapravaaha.n ca mahaantamapashyat | atha sa vismita\-
manaastaa.n bandhanaadvimucya shayyaayaamaaropya ca caaTushataiH
paryatoShayat | devasharmaa.a  pi ta.n sarvavR^ittaantamaalokya
vismitamanaa idamaaha \-

shambarasya ca yaa maayaa yaa maayaa namucerapi |
baleH kumbhiinasashcaiva sarvaastaa yoShito viduH || 194||
hasanta.n prahasantyetaa rudanta.n prarudantyapi |
apriya.n priyavaakyaishca gR^ihNanti kaalayogataH || 195||
ushanaa veda yacChaastra.n yacca veda bR^ihaspatiH |
striibuddhyaa na vishiShyete taaH sma rakShyaaH katha.n naraiH || 196||
anR^ita.n satyamityaahuH satya.n caapi tathaanR^itam |
iti yaastaaH katha.n viira sa.nrakShyaaH puruShairiha || 197||

anyatraapyuktam \-

naatiprasa~NgaH pramadaasu kaaryo
           necChedbala.n striiShu vivardhamaanam |
atiprasaktaiH puruShairyatastaaH
           kriiDanti kaakairiva luunapakShaiH || 198||
sumukhena vadanti valgunaa
           praharantyeva shitena cetasaa |
madhu tiShThati vaaci yoShitaa.n
           hR^idi haalahala.n mahadviSham || 199||
ata eva nipiiyate.adharo
           hR^idaya.n muShTibhireva taaDyate |
puruShaiH sukhaleshava~ncitai\-
           rmadhulubdhaiH kamala.n yathaa.alibhiH || 200||

api ca \-

aavartaH sa.nshayaanaamavinayabhavana.n pattana.n saahasaanaam |
doShaaNaa.n sa.nnidhaana.n kapaTashatamaya.n kShetramapratyayaanaam |
svargadvaarasya vighna.n narakapuramukha.n sarvamaayaakaraNDam |
striiyantra.n kena sR^iShTa.n viShamamR^itamaya.n praaNilokasya 
paashaH || 201||
kaarkashya.n stanayordR^ishostaralataa.aliika.n mukhe shlaaghyate |
kauTilya.n kacasa.ncaye ca vacane maandya.n trike sthuulataa |
bhiirutva.n hR^idaye sadaiva kathita.n maayaaprayogaH priye |
yaasaa.n doShagaNo guNo mR^igadR^ishaa.n taaH syurnaraaNaa.n priyaaH || 202||
etaa hasanti ca rudanti ca kaaryaheto\-
           rvishvaasayanti ca para.n na ca vishvasanti |
tasmaannareNa kulashiilasamanvitena
           naaryaH shmashaanaghaTikaa iva varjaniiyaaH || 203||
vyaakiirNakesarakaraalamukhaa mR^igendraa
           naagaashca bhuurimadaraajiviraajamaanaaH |
medhaavinashca puruShaaH samareShu shuuraaH
           striisannidhau paramakaapuruShaa bhavanti || 204 ||
kurvanti taavatprathama.n priyaaNi
           yaavanna jaananti nara.n prasaktam |
dnyaatvaa ca ta.n manmathapaashabaddha.n
           grastaamiSha.n miinamivoddharanti || 205||
samudraviiciiva calasvabhaavaaH
           sandhyaabhrarekheva muhuurtaraagaaH |
striyaH kR^itaarthaaH puruSha.n nirartha.n
           niShpiiDitaalaktakavattyajanti || 206||
anR^ita.n saahasa.n maayaa muurkhatvamatilubdhataa |
ashauca.n nirdayatva.n ca striiNaa.n doShaaH svabhaavajaaH || 207||
sammohayanti madayanti viDambayanti
           nirbhartsayanti ramayanti viShaadayanti |
etaaH pravishya sarala.n hR^idaya.n naraaNaa.n
           ki.n vaa na vaamanayanaa na samaacaranti || 208||
antarviShamayaa hyetaa bahishcaiva manoramaaH |
gu~njaaphalasamaakaaraa yoShitaH kena nirmitaaH || 209||

eva.n cintayatastasya parivraajakasya saa nishaa mahataa
kR^icChreNaaticakraama | saa ca duutikaa Chinnanaasikaa svagR^iha.n
gatvaa cintayaamaasa \- kimidaanii.n kartavyam | kathameta\-
nmahacChidra.n sthagayitavyam | atha tasyaa eva.n vicintayantyaa
bhartaa kaaryavashaadraajakule paryuShitaH pratyuuShe ca svagR^iha\-
mabhyupetya dvaaradeshastho vividhapaurakR^ityotsukatayaa taamaaha \-
bhadre shiighramaaniiyataa.n kShurabhaaNDa.n yena kShaurakarmakaraNaaya
gacChaami | saapi Chinnanaasikaa gR^ihamadhyasthitaiva kaaryakaraNaa\-
pekShayaa kShurabhaaNDaatkShurameka.n samaakR^iShya tasyaabhimukha.n
preShayaamaasa | naapito.apyutsukatayaa tameka.n kShuramavalokya
kopaaviShTaH san tadabhimukhameva ta.n kShura.n praahiNot | etasminnantare
saa duShTordhvabaahuu vidhaaya phutakartumanaa gR^ihaannishcakraama |
aho pashyata paapenaanena mama sadaacaaravartinyaaH naasikaacChedo
vihitaH | tatparitraayataa.n paritraayataam | atraantare raajapuruShaaH
samabhyetya ta.n naapita.n laguDaprahaarairjarjariikR^itya dR^iDhabandhanai\-
rbaddhvaa tayaa Chinnanaasikayaa saha dharmaadhikaraNasthaana.n
niitvaa sabhyaanuucuH \- shR^iNvantu bhavantaH sabhaasadaH | anena
naapitenaaparaadha.n vinaa striiratnametadvya~Ngitam | tadasya yadyujyate
  tatkriyataam | ityabhihite sabhyaa uucuH \- re naapita kimartha.n tvayaa
bhaaryaa vya~Ngitaa | kimanayaa parapuruSho.abhilaShitaH | utasvitpraaNa\-
drohaH kR^itaH ki.n vaa cauryakarmaacaritam | tatkathyataamasyaa\-
.aparaadhaH | naapito.api prahaarapiiDitatanurvaktu.n na shashaaka | atha ta.n
tuuShNii.nbhuuta.n dR^iShTvaa punaruucuH \- aho satyametadraaja\-
puruShaaNaa.n vacaH | paapaatmaa.ayam | aneneya.n nirdoShaa varaakii
duuShitaa | ukta~nca \-

bhinnasvaramukhavarNaH sha~NkitadR^iShTiH samutpatitatejaaH |
bhavati hi paapa.n kR^itvaa svakarmasantraasitaH puruShaH || 210||

tathaa ca \-

aayaati skhalitaiH paadairmukhavaivarNyasa.nyutaH |
lalaaTasvedabhaagbhuurigadgada.n bhaaShate vacaH || 211||
adhodR^iShTirvadetkR^itvaa paapa.n praaptaH sabhaa.n naraH |
tasmaadyatnaatparidnyeyaashcihnairetairvicakShaNaiH || 212||

anyacca \-

prasannavadano dR^iShTaH spaShTavaakyaH saroShadR^ik |
sabhaayaa.n vakti saamarSha.n saavaShTambho naraH shuciH || 213||

tadeSha duShTacaritralakShaNo dR^ishyate | striidharShaNaadvadhya iti |
tacChuuliiyaamaaropyataamiti | atha vadhyasthaane niiyamaana.n tamavalokya
devasharmaa taandharmaadhikR^itaangatvaa provaaca \- bho bho
anyaanyenaiSha varaako vadhyate naapitaH | saadhusamaacaara eShaH |
tacChruuyataa.n me vaakya.n jambuuko huDuyuddhena iti |atha te sabhyaa
uucuH \- bho bhagavankathametat |tato devasharmaa teShaa.n trayaaNaamapi
vR^ittaanta.n vistareNaakathayat | tadaakarNya suvismitamanasaste naapita.n
vimocya mithaH procuH \- aho

avadhyaa braahmaNaa gaavo striyo baalaashca dnyaatayaH |
yeShaa.n caannaani bhu~njiita ye ca syuH sharaNaagataaH || 214||

tadasyaa naasikaacChedaH svakarmaNaa hi sa.nvR^ittaH | tato raajanigrahastu
karNacChedaH kaaryaH | tathaanuShThite devasharmaa.api vittanaasha\-
samudbhuutashokarahitaH punarapi svakiiya.n maThaayatana.n jagaama |
ato.aha.n braviimi \- jambuuko huDuyuddheneti | karaTaka aaha \- eva.nvidhe
vyatikare ki.n kartavyamaavayoH | damanako.abraviit \- eva.nvidhe.api samaye
mama buddhisphuraNa.n bhaviShyati yena sa~njiivaka.n
prabhorvishleShayiShyaami | ukta~nca, yataH \-

eka.n hanyaanna vaa hanyaadiShuH kShipto dhanuShmataa |
praadnyena tu matiH kShiptaa hanyaadgarbhagataanapi || 215||

tadaha.n maayaaprapa~ncena guptamaashritya ta.n sphoTayiShyaami |
karaTaka aaha \- bhadra yadi kathamapi tava maayaapravesha.n pi~Ngalako
dnyaasyati sa~njiivako vaa tadaa nuuna.n vighaata eva | so.abraviit \- taata
maiva.n vada | guuDhabuddhibhiraapatkaale vidhure.api daive buddhiH
prayoktavyaa | nodyamastyaajyaH | kadaaci ghuNaakSharanyaayena
buddheH saamraajya.n bhavati | ukta~nca \-

tyaajya.n na dhairya.n vidhure.api daive
           dhairyaatkadaacitsthitimaapnuyaatsaH |
yaate samudre.api hi potabha~Nge
           saa.nyaatriko vaa~nChati karma eva || 216||

tathaa ca \-

udyogina.n satatamatra sameti lakShmii\-
           rdaiva.n hi daivamiti kaapuruShaa vadanti |
daiva.n nihatya kuru pauruShamaatmashaktyaa
           yatne kR^ite yadi na sidhyati ko.atra doShaH || 217||

tadeva.n dnyaatvaa suguuDhabuddhiprabhaaveNa yathaa tau dvaavapi
na dnyaasyataH tathaa mitho viyojayiShyaami | ukta~nca \-

suprayuktasya dambhasya brahmaa.apyanta.n na gacChati |
kauliko viShNuruupeNa raajakanyaa.n niShevate || 218||

karaTaka aaha \- kathametat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 5
kaulikarathakaarakathaa |

kasmi.nshcidadhiShThaane kaulikarathakaarau mitre prativasataH sma | tatra
ca baalyaatprabhR^iti sahacaariNau parasparamatiiva snehaparau sadaika\-
sthaanavihaariNau kaala.n nayataH | atha kadaacit tatraadhiShThaane
kasmi.nshcid devaayatane yaatraamahotsavaH sa.nvR^ittaH | tatra ca
  naTanartakacaaraNasa~Nkule naanaadeshaagatajanaavR^ite tau sahacarau
bhramantau kaa~ncidraajakanyaa.n kareNukaaruuDhaa.n sarvalakShaNa\-
sanaathaa.n ka~ncukivarShadharaparivaaritaa.n devataadarshanaartha.n
samaayaataa.n dR^iShTavantau | athaasau kaulikastaa.n dR^iShTvaa
viShaardita iva duShTagrahagR^ihiita iva kaamasharairhanyamaanaH sahasaa
bhuutale nipapaata | atha ta.n tadavasthamavalokya rathakaarastad\-
duHkhaduHkhita aaptapuruShaista.n samutkShipya svagR^ihamaanayat |
tatra ca vividhaiH shiitopacaaraishcikitsakopadiShTairmantravaadibhi\-
rupacaryamaaNaishciraatkatha.ncitsacetano babhuuva |tato
rathakaareNa pR^iShTaH \- bho mitra kimeva.n tvamakasmaadvicetanaH
sa~njaataH | tatkathyataamaatmasvaruupam | sa aaha \- vayasya yadyeva.n
tacChR^iNu me rahasya.n yena sarvaamaatmavedanaa.n te vadaami | yadi
tva.n maa.n suhR^ida.n manyase tataH kaaShThapradaanena prasaadaH
kriyataam | kShamyataa.n yadvaa ki~ncitpraNayaatirekaadayukta.n tava
mayaanuShThitam | so.api tadaakarNya baaShpapihitanayanaH sagadgada\-
muvaaca \- vayasya yatki.ncidduHkhakaaraNa.n tadvada yena pratiikaaraH
kriyate yadi shakyate kartum | ukta~nca \-

auShadhaarthasumantraaNaa.n buddheshcaiva mahaatmanaam |
asaadhya.n naasti loke.atra yadbrahmaaNDasya madhyagam || 219||

tadeShaa.n caturNaa.n yadi saadhya.n bhaviShyati tadaaha.n
saadhayiShyaami | kaulika aaha \- vayasya eteShaamanyeShaamapi
sahasraaNaamupaayaanaamasaadhya.n tanme duHkham | tasmaanmama
maraNe maa kaalakShepa.n kuru | rathakaara aaha \- bho mitra
yadyapyasaadhya.n tathaapi nivedaya yenaahamapi tadasaadhya.n matvaa
tvayaa sama.n vahnau pravishaami | na kShaNamapi tvadviyoga.n sahiShye |
eSha me nishcayaH|  kaulika aaha \- vayasya yaa.asau raajakanyaa
kareNumaaruuDhaa tatrotsave dR^iShTaa tasyaa darshanaanantara.n
makaradhvajena mameyamavasthaa vihitaa | tanna shaknomi
tadvedanaa.n soDhum | tathaa coktam \-

mattebhakumbhapariNaahini ku~Nkumaardre
           tasyaaH payodharayuge ratikhedakhinnaH |
vakSho nidhaaya bhujapa~njaramadhyavartii
           svapsye kadaa kShaNamavaapya tadiiyasa~Ngam || 220||

tathaa ca \-

raagii bimbaadharo.asau stanakalashayuga.n yauvanaaruuDhagarvam |
niicaa naabhiH prakR^ityaa kuTilakamalaka.n svalpaka.n caapi madhyam |
kurvantvetaani naama prasabhamiha manashcintitaanyaashu khedam |
yanmaa.n tasyaaH kapolau dahata iti muhuH svacChakau tanna yuktam || 221||

rathakaaro.apyeva.n sakaama.n tadvacanamaakarNya sasmitamidamaaha \-
vayasya yadyeva.n tarhi diShTyaa siddha.n naH prayojanam | tadadyaiva
tayaa saha samaagamaH kriyataamiti |kaulika aaha \- vayasya yatra
kanyaantaHpure vaayu.n muktvaa naanyasya pravesho.asti tatra rakShaa\-
puruShaadhiShThite katha.n mama tasyaa saha samaagamaH | tatki.n
maamasatyavacanena viDambayasi | rathakaara aaha \- mitra pashya me
buddhibalam | evamabhidhaaya tatkShaNaatkiilasa~ncaariNa.n vainateya.n
baahuyugala.n vaayujavR^ikShadaaruNaa sha~Nkhacakragadaapadmaanvita.n
sakiriiTakaustubhamaghaTayan | tatastasminkaulika.n samaaropya
viShNucihnita.n kR^itvaa kiilasa~ncaraNavidnyaana.n ca darshayitvaa
provaaca \- vayasya, anena viShNuruupeNa gatvaa kanyaantaHpure nishiithe
taa.n raajakanyaamekaakinii.n saptabhuumikapraasaadapraantagataa.n
mugdhasvabhaavaa.n tvaa.n vaasudeva.n manyamaanaa.n svakiiyamithyaa\-
vakroktibhii ra~njayitvaa vaatsyaayanoktavidhinaa bhaja | kauliko.api
tadaakarNya tathaaruupastatra gatvaa taamaaha \- raajaputri suptaa ki.n
vaa jaagarShi |  aha.n tava kR^ite samudraatsaanuraago lakShmii.n
vihaayaivaagataH | tatkriyataa.n mayaa saha samaagama iti |saa.api
garuDaaruuDha.n caturbhuja.n saayudha.n kaustubhopetamavalokya
savismayaa shayanaadutthaaya provaaca \- bhagavan aha.n maanuShii
kiiTikaashuciH | bhagavaa{\m+}strailokyapaavano vandaniiyashca |
tatkathametadyujyate | kaulika aaha \- subhage satyamabhihita.n
bhavatyaa | para.n ki.n tu raadhaa naama me bhaaryaa gopakulaprasuutaa
prathamaa.asiit | saa tvamatraavatiirNaa | tenaahamatraayaataH | ityuktaa
saa praaha \- bhagavan yadyeva.n tanme taata.n praarthaya |
so.apyavikalpa.n maa.n tubhya.n prayacChati | kaulika aaha \- subhage
naaha.n darshanapatha.n maanuShaaNaa.n gacChaami | ki.n
punaraalaapakaraNam | tva.n gaandharveNa vivaahenaatmaana.n prayacCha |
no cecChaapa.n dattvaa saanvaya.n te pitara.n bhasmasaatkariShyaamiiti |
evamabhidhaaya garuDaadavatiirya savye paaNau gR^ihiitvaa taa.n sabhayaa.n
salajjaa.n vepamaanaa.n shayyaayaamaanayat | tatashca raatrisheSha.n
yaavadvaatsyaayanoktavidhinaa niShevya pratyuuShe svagR^ihamalakShito
jagaama | eva.n tasya taa.n nitya.n sevamaanasya kaalo yaati | atha
kadaacitka~ncukinastasyaaadharoShThapravaalakhaNDana.n dR^iShTvaa
mithaH procuH \- aho pashyataasyaa raajakanyaayaaH puruShopabhuktaayaiva
shariiraavayavaa vibhaavyante | tatkathamaya.n surakShite.apyasmingR^iha
eva.nvidho vyavahaaraH | tadraadnye nivedayaamaH | eva.n nishcitya sarve
sametya raajaana.n procuH \- deva vaya.n na vidmaH | para.n surakShite.api
kanyaantaHpure kashcitpravishati | taddevaH pramaaNamiti |
tacChrutvaa raajaa.atiiva vyaakulitacitto vyacintayat \-

putriiti jaataa mahatiiha cintaa
           kasmai pradeyeti mahaanvitarkaH |
dattvaa sukha.n praapsyati vaa na veti
           kanyaapitR^itva.n khalu naama kaShTam || 222||
nadyashca naaryashca sadR^ikprabhaavaa\-
           stulyaani kuulaani kulaani taasaam |
toyaishca doShaishca nipaatayanti
           nadyo hi kuulaani kulaani naaryaH || 223||
jananiimano harati jaatavatii parivardhate saha shucaa suhR^idaam |
parasaatkR^itaapi kurute malina.n duritakramaa duhitaro vipadaH || 224||

eva.n bahuvidha.n vicintya devii.n rahaHsthaa.n provaaca \- devi dnyaayataa.n
kimete ka~ncukino vadanti | tasya kR^itaantaH kupito yenaitadeva.n kriyate |
devyapi tadaakarNya vyaakuliibhuutaa  satvara.n kanyaantaHpure gatvaa taa.n
khaNDitaadharaa.n nakhavilikhitashariiraavayavaa.n duhitaramapashyat | aaha
ca \- aaH paape  kulakala~NkakaariNi kimeva shiilakhaNDana.n kR^itam |
ko.aya.n kR^itaantaavalokitastvatsakaashamabhyeti | tatkathyataa.n
mamaagre satyam | iti kopaaTopavisa~NkaTa.n vadatyaa.n maatari
raajaputrii bhayalajjaanataanana.n provaaca \- amba saakShaannaaraayaNaH
pratyaha.n garuDaaruuDho nishi samaayaati | cedasatya.n mama vaakya.n
tatsvacakShuShaa vilokayatu niguuDhataraa nishiithe bhagavanta.n
ramaakaantam | tacChrutvaa saapi prahasitavadanaa pulakaa~Nkitasarvaa~Ngii
satvara.n raajaanamuuce \- deva diShTyaa vardhase | nityameva nishiithe
bhagavaannaaraayaNaH kanyakaapaarshve.abhyeti | tena gaandharvavivaahena
saa vivaahitaa | tadadya tvayaa mayaa ca raatrau vaataayanagataabhyaa.n
nishiithe draShTavyaH | yato na sa maanuShaiH sahaalaapa.n karoti |
tacChrutvaa harShitasya raadnyastaddina.n varShashatapraayamiva
katha~ncijjagaama | tatastu raatrau nibhR^ito bhuutvaa raadnyiisahito raajaa
vaataayanastho gaganaasaktadR^iShTiryaavattiShThati taavattasminsamaye
garuDaaruuDha.n ta.n sha~Nkacakragadaapadmahasta.n yathoktacihnaa~Nkita.n
vyomno.avataranta.n naaraayaNamapashyat | tataH sudhaapuuraplaavita\-
mivaatmaana.n manyamaanastaamuvaaca \- priye  naastyanyo dhanyataro
loke mattastvattashca | tatprasuuti.n naaraayaNo bhajate | tatsiddhaaH
sarve.asmaaka.n manorathaaH | adhunaa jaamaatR^iprabhaaveNa sakalaamapi
  vasumatii.n vashyaa.n kariShyaami | eva.n nishcitya sarvaiH siimaadhipaiH
saha maryaadaavyatikramamakarot | te ca ta.n maryaadaavyatikrameNa
vartamaanamaalokya sarve sametya tena saha vigraha.n cakruH | atraantare
sa raajaa deviimukhena taa.n duhitaramuvaaca \- putri tvayi duhitari
vartamaanaayaa.n naaraayaNe bhagavati jaamaatari sthite tatkimeva.n
yujyate yatsarve paarthivaa mayaa saha vigraha.n kurvanti | tatsa.nbodhyo.adya
tvayaa nijabhartaa yathaa mama shatruunvyaapaadayati | tatastayaa sa kauliko
raatrau savinayamabhihitaH \- bhagavan tvayi jaamaatari sthite mama taato
yacChatrubhiH paribhuuyate tanna yuktam | tatprasaada.n kR^itvaa
sarvaa.nstaanshatruunvyaapaadaya| kaulika aaha \- subhage kiyanmaatraastvete
  tava pituH shatravaH | tadvishvastaa bhava | kShaNenaapi sudarshanacakreNa
sarvaa.nstilashaH khaNDayiShyaami | atha gacChataa kaalena sarvadesha.n
shatrubhirudvaasya sa raajaa praakaarasheShaH kR^itaH | tathaapi
vaasudevaruupadhara.n kaulikamajaananraajaa nityameva visheShataH
karpuuraagurukastuurikaadiparimalavisheShaannaanaaprakaaravastrapuShpa\-
bhakShyapeyaa.nshca preShayanduhitR^imukhena tamuuce \- bhagavan
prabhaate nuuna.n sthaanabha~Ngo bhaviShyati | yato yavasendhanakShayaH
sa.njaatastathaa sarvo.api janaH prahaarairjarjaritadehaH sa.nvR^itto
yoddhumakShamaH pracuro mR^itashca | tadeva.n dnyaatvaa.atra kaale
yaducita.n bhavati tadvidheyamiti | tacChrutvaa kauliko.apyacintayat \-
sthaanabha~Nge jaate mamaanayaa saha viyogo bhaviShyati |
tasmaadgaruDamaaruhya saayudhamaatmaanamaakaashe darshayaami |
kadaacinmaa.n vaasudeva.n manyamaanaaste saasha~Nkaa raadnyo
yoddhR^ibhirhanyate | ukta~nca \-

nirviSheNaapi sarpeNa kartavyaa mahatii phaNaa |
viSha.n bhavatu vaa maabhuutphaNaaTopo bhaya~NkaraH || 225||

atha yadi mama sthaanaarthamudyatasya mR^ityurbhaviShyati tadapi
sundarataram | ukta~nca \-

gavaamarthe braahmaNaarthe svaamyarthe sviikR^ite.athavaa |
sthaanaarthe yastyajet praaNaa.nstasya lokaaH sanaatanaaH || 226||
candre maNDalasa.nsthe vigR^ihyate raahuNaa dinaadhiishaH |
sharaNaagatena saardha.n vipadapi tejasvinaa.n shlaaghyaa || 227||

eva.n nishcitya pratyuuShe dantadhaavana.n kR^itvaa taa.n provaaca \-
subhage samastaiH shatrubhirhatairanna.n paana.n caasvaadayiShyaami |
  ki.n bahunaa tvayaapi saha sa~Ngama.n tataH kariShyaami | para.n
vaacyastvayaa.atmapitaa yatprabhaate prabhuutena sainyena saha
nagaraanniShkramya yoddhavyam | aha.n caakaashasthita eva
sarvaa.nstaannistejasaH kariShyaami | pashcaatsukhena bhavataa
hantavyaaH | yadi punaraha.n taansvayameva suudayaami tatteShaa.n
paapaatmanaa.n vaikuNThiiyaa gatiH syaat | tasmaatte tathaa kartavyaa
yathaa palaayanto hanyamaanaaH svarga.n na gacChanti | saapi tadaakarNya
pituH samiipa.n gatvaa sarva.n vR^ittaanta.n nyavedayat | raajaapi tasyaa
vaakya.n shraddadhaanaH pratyuuShe samutthaaya samunnaddhasainyo
yuddhaartha.n nishcakraama | kauliko.api maraNe kR^itanishcayashcaapa\-
paaNirgaganagatirgaruDaaruuDho yuddhaaya prasthitaH | atraantare
bhagavataa naaraayaNenaatiitaanaagatavartamaanavedinaa smR^itamaatro
vainateyaH sa.npraapto vihasya proktaH \- bho garutman jaanaasi tva.n
yanmama ruupeNa kauliko daarumayagaruDe samaaruuDho raajakanyaa.n
kaamayate | so.abraviit \- deva sarva.n dnyaayate tacceShTitam | tat ki.n
  kurmaH saampratam | shriibhagavaanaaha \- adya kauliko maraNe
kR^itanishcayo vihitaniyamo yuddhaarthe vinirgataH sa nuuna.n pradhaana\-
kShatriyairmilitvaa vaasudevo garuDashca nipaatitaH | tataH para.n
loko.ayamaavayoH puujaa.n na kariShyati | tatastva.n drutatara.n tatra
daarumayagaruDe sa~NkramaNa.n kuru | ahamapi kaulikashariire pravesha.n
kariShyaami | yena sa shatruunvyaapaadayati | tatashca
shatruvadhaadaavayormaahaatmyavR^iddhiH syaat | atha garuDe tatheti
pratipanne shriibhagavannaaraayaNastacChariire sa~NkramaNamakarot |
tato bhagavanmaahaatmyena gaganasthaH sa kaulikaH sha~Nkhacakra\-
gadaacaapacihnitaH kShaNaadeva liilayaiva samastaanapi pradhaana\-
kShatriyaannistejasashcakaara | tatastena raadnyaa svasainyaparivR^itena
sa~Ngraame jitaa nihataashca te sarve.api shatravaH | jaatashca lokamadhye
pravaado yathaa.anena viShNujaamaatR^iprabhaaveNa sarve shatravo nihataa
iti | kauliko.api taanhataan dR^iShTvaa pramuditamanaa gaganaadavatiirNaH
san yaavad raajaamaatyapauralokaasta.n nagaravaastavya.n kaulika.n
pashyanti tataH pR^iShTaH kimetaditi | tataH so.api muulaadaarabhya sarva.n
praagvR^ittaanta.n nyavedayat | tatashca kaulikasaahasaanura~njitamanasaa
shatruvadhaadavaaptatejasaa raadnyaa saa raajakanyaa sakalajanapratyakSha.n
vivaahavidhinaa tasmai samarpitaa deshashca pradattaH | kauliko.api tayaa
saardha.n pa~ncaprakaara.n jiivalokasaara.n viShayasukhamanubhavankaala.n
ninaaya | atastuucyate suprayuktasya dambhasyeti | tacChrutvaa karaTaka
aaha \- bhadra astvevam | para.n tathaapi mahanme bhayam | yato
buddhimaansa.njiivako raudrashca si.nhaH | yadyapi te buddhipraagalbhya.n
tathaapi tva.n pi~Ngalakaatta.n viyojayitumasamartha eva | damanaka aaha \-
bhraataH asamartho.api samartha eva | ukta~nca \-

upaayena hi yacChakya.n na tacChakya.n paraakramaiH |
kaakii kanakasuutreNa kR^iShNasarpamaghaatayat || 228||

karaTaka aaha \- kathametat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 6
vaayasadampatikathaa |

asti kasmi.nshcitpradeshe mahaannyagrodhapaadapaH | tatra vaayasa\-
dampatii prativasataH sma | atha tayoH prasavakaale vR^ikShavivaraanni\-
Shkramya kR^iShNasarpaH sadaiva tadapatyaani bhakShayati | tatastau
nirvedaadanyavR^ikShamuulanivaasina.n priyasuhR^ida.n shR^igaala.n
gatvocatuH \- bhadra kimeva.nvidhe sa~njaata aavayoH kartavya.n bhavati |
eva.n taavadduShTaatmaa kR^iShNasarpo vR^ikShavivaraannirgatyaavayo\-
rbaalakaanbhakShayati | tatkathyataa.n tadrakShaartha.n kashcidupaayaH |

yasya kShetra.n nadiitiire bhaaryaa ca parasa~Ngataa |
sasarpe ca gR^ihe vaasaH katha.n syaattasya nirvR^itiH || 229||

anyacca \-

sarpayukte gR^ihe vaaso mR^ityureva na sa.nshayaH |
yadgraamaante vasetsarpastasya syaatpraaNasa.nshayaH || 230||

asmaakamapi tatrasthitaanaa.n pratidina.n praaNasa.nshayaH | sa aaha \-
naatra viShaye svalpo.api viShaadaH kaaryaH | nuuna.n sa lubdho
nopaayamantareNa vadhyaH syaat |

upaayena jayo yaadR^igripostaadR^i~N na hetibhiH |
upaayadnyo.alpakaayo.api na shuuraiH paribhuuyate || 231||

tathaa ca \-

bhakShayitvaa bahuunmatsyaanuttamaadhamamadhyamaan |
atilaulyaadbakaH kashcinmR^itaH karkaTakagrahaat || 232||

taavuucatuH \- kathametat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 7
bakakuliirakakathaa |

asti kasmi.nshcidvanapradeshe naanaajalacarasanaatha.n mahatsaraH | tatra
ca kR^itaashrayo baka eko vR^iddhabhaavamupaagato matsyaanvyaapaada\-
yitumasamarthaH | tatashca kShutkShaamakaNThaH sarastiira upaviShTo
muktaaphalaprakarasadR^ishairashrupravaahairdharaatalamabhiShi~ncan
ruroda | ekaH kuliirako naanaajalacarasametaH sametya tasya duHkhena
duHkhitaH saadaramidamuuce \- maama kimadya tvayaa naahaaravR^itti\-
ranuShThiiyate | kevalamashrupuurNanetraabhyaa.n saniHshvaasena
sthiiyate | sa aaha \- vatsa satyamupalakShita.n bhavataa | mayaa hi
matsyaadana.n prati paramavairaagyatayaa saamprata.n praayopaveshana.n
kR^itam | tenaaha.n samiipaagataanapi matsyaanna bhakShayaami |
kuliirakastacChrutvaa praaha \- maama ki.n tadvairaagyakaaraNam | sa
praaha \- vatsa ahamasminsarasi jaato vR^iddhi.n gatashca |
tanmayaitacChruta.n yaddvaadashavarShikyanaavR^iShTiH sampadyate
  lagnaa | kuliiraka aaha \- kasmaattacChrutam | baka aaha \-
daivadnyamukhaat | eSha shanaishcaro hi rohiNiishakaTa.n bhittvaa bhauma.n
shakra.n ca prayaasyati | ukta~nca varaahamihireNa \-

yadi bhinte suuryasuto rohiNyaaH shakaTamiha loke |
dvaadashavarShaaNi tadaa na hi varShati vaasavo bhuumau || 233||

tathaa ca \-

praajaapatye shakaTe bhinne kR^itvaiva paataka.n vasudhaa |
bhasmaasthishakalaakiirNaa kaapaalikamiva vrata.n dhatte || 234||

tathaa ca \-

rohiNiishakaTamarkanandanashcedbhinnatti rudhiro.athavaa shashii |
ki.n vadaami tadaniShTasaagare sarvalokamupayaati sa~NkShayaH || 235||
rohiNiishakaTamadhyasa.nsthite candramasya sharaNiikR^itaa janaaH |
kvaapi yaanti shishupaacitaashanaaH suuryataptabhiduraambupaayinaH || 236||

tadetatsaraH svalpatoya.n vartate | shiighra.n shoSha.n yaasyati | asmin
shuShke yaiH sahaaha.n vR^iddhi.n gataH sadaiva kriiDitashca te sarve
toyaabhaavaannaasha.n yaasyanti | tatteShaa.n viyoga.n draShTumahama\-
samarthaH | tenaitatpraayopaveshana.n kR^itam | saamprata.n sarveShaa.n
svalpajalaashayaanaa.n jalacaraa gurujalaashayeShu svasvajanairniiyante |
kecicca makarashishumaarajalahastiprabhR^itayaH svayameva gacChanti |
atra punaH sarasi ye jalacaraaste nishcintaaH santi tenaaha.n
visheShaadrodimi yadbiijasheShamaatramapyatra noddhariShyati | tataH
sa tadaakarNyaanyeShaamapi jalacaraaNaa.n tattasya vacana.n
nivedayaamaasa | atha te sarve bhayatrastamanaso matsyakacChapa\-
prabhR^itayastamabhyupetya papracChuH \- maama asti kashcidupaayo
yenaasmaaka.n rakShaa bhavati | baka aaha \- astyasya jalaashayasya
naatiduure prabhuutajalasanaatha.n saraH padminiikhaNDamaNDita.n
yaccaturvi.nshatyapi varShaaNaamavR^iShTyaa na shoShameShyati | tadyadi
  mama pR^iShTha.n kashcidaarohati tadaha.n ta.n tatra nayaami | atha te
tatra vishvaasamaapannaaH taata maatula bhraataH iti bruvaaNaa aha.n
puurvamaha.n puurvamiti samantaatparitasthuH | so.api duShTaashayaH
krameNa taanpR^iShTha aaropya jalaashayasya naatiduure shilaa.n
samaasaadya tasyaamaakShipya  svecChayaa bhakShayitvaa bhuuyo.api
jalaashaya.n samaasaadya jalacaraaNaa.n mithyaavaartaasandeshakai\-
rmanaa.nsi ra~njayannityamevaahaaravR^ittimakarot | anyasmindine ca
kuliirakeNoktaH \- maama mayaa saha te prathamaH snehasambhaaShaH
sa~njaataH | tatki.n maa.n parityajyaanyaannayasi | tasmaadadya me
praaNatraaNa.n kuru | tadaakarNya so.api duShTaashayashcintitavaan \-
nirviNNo.aha.n matsyamaa.nsaadanena tadadyaina.n kuliiraka.n
vya~njanasthaane karomi | iti vicintya ta.n pR^iShThe samaaropya taa.n
vadhyashilaamuddishya prasthitaH | kuliirako.api duuraadevaasthiparvata.n
shilaashrayamavalokya mastyaasthiini paridnyaaya tamapR^icChat \-
maama kiyadduure sa jalaashayaH | madiiyabhaareNaatishraantastvam |
tat kathaya | so.api mandadhiirjalacaro.ayamiti matvaa sthale na prabhavatiiti
sasmitamidamaaha \- kuliiraka kuto.anyo jalaashayaH | mama
praaNayaatreyam | tasmaatsmaryataamaatmano.abhiiShTadevataa |
tvaamapyanyaa.n shilaayaa.n nikShipya bhakShayiShyaami | ityuktavati
tasminsvavadanada.nshadvayena mR^iNaalanaaladhavalaayaa.n
mR^idugriivaayaa.n gR^ihiito mR^itashca | atha sa taa.n bakagriivaa.n
samaadaaya shanaiH shanaistajjalaashayamaasasaada | tataH sarvaireva
jalacaraiH pR^iShTaH \- bhoH kuliiraka ki.n nivR^ittastvam | sa
maatulo.api naayaataH | tat ki.n cirayati| vaya.n sarve sotsukaaH
kR^itakShaNaastiShThaamaH | eva.n tairabhihite kuliirako.api vihasyovaaca \-
muurkhaaH sarve jalacaraastena mithyaavaadinaa va~ncayitvaa naatiduure
shilaatale prakShipya bhakShitaaH | tan mamaayuHsheShatayaa tasya
  vishvaasaghaatakasyaabhipraaya.n dnyaatvaa griiveyam aaniitaa | tad ala.n
sambhrameNa | adhunaa sarvajalacaraaNaa.n kShema.n bhaviShyati |
ato.aha.n braviimi \- bhakShayitvaa bahuunmatsyaaniti | vaayasa aaha \-
bhadra tatkathaya katha.n sa duShTasarpo vadhamupaiShyati | shR^igaala
aaha \- gacChatu bhavaan ka~ncinnagara.n raajaadhiShThaanam | tatra
kasyaapi dhanino raajaamaatyaadeH pramaadinaH kanakasuutra.n haara.n
  vaa gR^ihiitvaa tatkoTare prakShipa yena sarpastadgrahaNena vadhyate |
tatkShaNaatkaakaH kaakii ca tadaakarNyaatmecChayotpatitau | tatashca
kaakii ki~ncitsaraH praapya yaavatpashyati taavattanmadhye kasyacidraadnyo\-
.antaHpura.n jalaasanna.n nyastakanakasuutra.n muktamuktaahaara\-
vastraabharaNa.n jalakriiDaa.n kurute | atha saa vaayasii kanakasuutra\-
mekamaadaaya svagR^ihaabhimukha.n pratasthe | tatashca ka~ncukino
varShavaraashca tanniiyamaanamupalakShya gR^ihiitalaguDaaH
satvaramanuyayuH | kaakyapi sarpakoTare tatkanakasuutra.n prakShipya
suduuramavasthitaa | atha yaavadraajapuruShaasta.n vR^ikShamaaruhya
tatkoTaramavalokayanti taavatkR^iShNasarpaH prasaaritabhogastiShThati |
tatasta.n laguDaprahaareNa hatvaa kanakasuutramaadaaya yathaabhilaShita.n
sthaana.n gataaH | vaayasadampatyapi tataH para.n sukhena vasataH |
ato.aha.n braviimi upaayena hi yatkuryaaditi | tanna ki.ncidiha
buddhimataamasaadhyamasti | ukta~nca \-

yasya buddhirbala.n tasya nirbuddhestu kuto balam |
vane si.nho madonmattaH shashakena nipaatitaH || 237||

karaTaka aaha \- kathametat| sa aaha \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 8
bhaasurakaakhyasi.nhakathaa |

kasmi.nshcidvane bhaasurako naama si.nhaH prativasati sma | athaasau
viiryaatirekaannityamevaanekaanmR^igashashakaadiinvyaapaadaya\-
nnopararaama | athaanyedyustadvanajaaH sarve saara~NgavaraahamahiSha\-
shashakaadayo militvaa tamabhyupetya procuH \- svaaminkimanena
sakalamR^igavadhena nityameva yatastavaikenaapi mR^igeNa tR^iptirbhavati
tatkriyataamasmaabhiH saha samayadharmaH | adyaprabhR^iti
tavaatropaviShTasya jaatikrameNa pratidinameko mR^igo bhakShaNaartha.n
sameShyati | eva.n kR^ite tava taavatpraaNayaatraa klesha.n vinaa.api
bhaviShyati | asmaaka.n ca punaH sarvocChedana.n na syaat | tadeSha
raajadharmo.anuShThiiyataam | ukta~nca \-

shanaiH shanaishca yo raajyamupabhu~Nkte yathaabalam |
rasaayanamiva praadnyaH sa puShTi.n paramaa.n vrajet || 238||
vidhinaa mantrayuktena ruukShaapi mathitaapi ca |
prayacChati phala.n bhuumiraraNiiva hutaashanam || 239||
prajaanaa.n paalana.n shasya.n svargakoshasya vardhanam |
piiDana.n dharmanaashaaya paapaayaayashase sthitam || 240||
gopaalena prajaadhenorvittadugdha.n shanaiH shanaiH |
paalanaatpoShaNaadgraahya.n nyaayyaa.n vR^itti.n samaacaret || 241||
ajaamiva prajaa.n mohaadyo hanyaat pR^ithiviipatiH |
tasyaikaa jaayate tR^iptirna dvitiiyaa katha~ncana || 242||
phalaarthii nR^ipatirlokaanpaalayedyatnamaasthitaH |
daanamaanaaditoyena maalaakaaro.a~Nkuraaniva || 243||
nR^ipadiipo dhanasneha.n prajaabhyaH sa.nharannapi |
aantarasthairguNaiH shubhrairlakShyate naiva kenacit || 244||
yathaa gaurduhyate kaale paalyate ca tathaa prajaa |
sicyate ciiyate caiva lataa puShpaphalapradaa || 245||
yathaa biijaa~NkuraH suukShmaH prayatnenaabhirakShitaH |
phalaprado bhavetkaale tadvallokaH surakShitaH || 246||
hiraNyadhaanyaratnaani yaanaani vividhaani ca |
tathaanyadapi yatki~ncitprajaabhyaH syaanmahiipateH || 247||
lokaanugrahakartaaraH pravardhante nareshvaraaH |
lokaanaa.n sa.nkShayaaccaiva kShaya.n yaanti na sa.nshayaH || 248||

atha teShaa.n tadvacanamaakarNya bhaasuraka aaha \- aho satyamabhihita.n
bhavadbhiH | para.n yadi mamopaviShTasyaatra nityameva naikaH shvaapadaH
samaagamiShyati | tannuuna.n sarvaanapi bhakShayiShyaami | atha te tathaiva
pratidnyaaya nirvR^itibhaajastatraiva vane nirbhayaaH paryaTanti | ekashca
pratidina.n krameNa yaati | vR^iddho vaa vairaagyayukto vaa shokagrasto vaa
putrakalatranaashabhiito vaa teShaa.n madhyaattasya bhojanaartha.n
madhyaahnasamaya upatiShThate | atha kadaacijjaatikramaacChashaka\-
syaavasaraH samaayaataH | sa samastamR^igaiH prerito.anicChannapi
manda.n manda.n gatvaa tasya vadhopaaya.n cintayanvelaatikrama.n
kR^itvaa vyaakulitahR^idayo yaavadgacChati taavanmaarge gacChataa kuupaH
sa.ndR^iShTaH | yaavatkuupopari yaati taavatkuupamadhya aatmanaH
pratibimba.n dadarsha | dR^iShTvaa ca tena hR^idaye cintitam \- yadbhavya
  upaayo.asti| aha.n bhaasuraka.n prakopya svabuddhyaa.asminkuupe
paatayiShyaami | athaasau dinasheShe bhaasurakasamiipa.n praaptaH |
si.nho.api velaatikrameNa kShutkShaamakaNThaH kopaaviShTaH sR^ikkaNii
parilelihanvyacintayat \- aho praataraahaaraaya niHsattva.n vana.n mayaa
kartavyam | eva.n cintayatastasya shashako manda.n manda.n gatvaa
praNamya tasyaagre sthitaH | atha ta.n prajvalitaatmaa bhaasurako
  bhartsayannaaha \- re shashakaadhama ekastaavattva.n laghuH
praapto.aparato velaatikrameNa | tadasmaadaparaadhaattvaa.n nipaatya
praataH sakalaanyapi mR^igakulaanyucChedayiShyaami |atha shashakaH
savinaya.n provaaca \- svaaminnaaparaadho mama | na ca sattvaanaam |
tacChruuyataa.n kaaraNam | si.nha aaha \- satvara.n nivedaya yaavanmama
da.nShTraantargato na bhavaanbhaviShyatiiti | shashaka aaha \-
svaaminsamastamR^igairadya jaatikrameNa mama laghutarasya prastaava.n
vidnyaaya tato.aha.n pa~ncashashakaiH sama.n preShitaH | tatashcaaha\-
maagacChannantaraale mahataa kenacidapareNa si.nhena vivaraannirga\-
tyaabhihitaH \- abhiiShTadevataa.n smarata | tato mayaabhihitam \- vaya.n
svaamino bhaasurakasi.nhasya sakaashamaahaaraartha.n samayadharmeNa
gacChaamaH | tatastenaabhihitam \- yadyeva.n tarhi madiiyametadvanam |
mayaa saha samayadharmeNa samastairapi shvaapadairvartitavyam |
cauraruupii sa bhaasurakaH | atha yadi so.atra raajaa vishvaasasthaane
caturaH shashakaanatra dhR^itvaa tamaahuuya drutataramaagacCha | yena
yaH kashcidaavayormadhyaatparaakrameNa raajaa bhaviShyati sa
sarvaanetaanbhakShayiShyatiiti | tato.aha.n tenaadiShTaH
svaamisakaashamabhyaagataH | etadvelaavyatikramakaaraNam | tadatra
svaamii pramaaNam | tacChrutvaa bhaasuraka aaha \- bhadra yadyeva.n
tatsatvara.n darshaya me ta.n caurasi.nha.n yenaaha.n mR^igakopa.n
tasyopari kShiptvaa svastho bhavaami | ukta~nca \-

bhuumirmitra.n hiraNya.n ca vigrahasya phalatrayam |
naastyekamapi yadyeShaa.n na ta.n kuryaatkatha~ncana || 249||
yatra na syaatphala.n bhuuri yatra ca syaatparaabhavaH |
na tatra matimaanyuddha.n samutpaadya samaacaret || 250||

shashaka aaha \- svaamin satyamidam | svabhuumihetoH paribhavaacca
yudhyante kShatriyaaH | para.n sa durgaashrayaH | durgaanniShkramya
vaya.n tena viShkambhitaaH | tato durgastho duHsadhyo bhavati ripuH |
ukta~nca \-

na gajaanaa.n sahasreNa na ca lakSheNa vaajinaam |
yatkR^itya.n saadhyate raadnyaa.n durgeNaikena vigrahe || 251||
shatameko.api sa.ndhatte praakaarastho dhanurdharaH |
tasmaaddurga.n prasha.nsanti niitishaastravicakShaNaaH || 252||
puraa guroH samaadeshaaddhiraNyakashiporbhayaat |
shakreNa vihita.n durga.n prabhaavaadvishvakarmaNaH || 253||
tenaapi ca varo datto yasya durga.n sa bhuupatiH |
vijayii syaattato bhuumau durgaaNi syuH sahasrashaH || 254||
da.nShTraavirahito naago madahiino yathaa gajaH |
sarveShaa.n jaayate vashyo durgahiinastathaa nR^ipaH || 255||

tacChrutvaa bhaasuraka aaha | bhadra durgasthamapi darshaya ta.n
caurasi.nha.n yena vyaapaadayaami | ukta~nca \-

jaatamaatra.n na yaH shatru.n roga.n ca prashama.n nayet |
mahaabalo.api tenaiva vR^iddhi.n praapya sa hanyate || 256||

tathaa ca \-
uttiShThamaanastu paro nopekShyaH pathyamicChataa |
samau hi shiShTairaamnaatau vartsyantaavaamayaH sa ca || 257||

api ca \-

upekShitaH kShiiNabalo.api shatruH
           pramaadadoShaatpuruShairmadaandhaiH |
saadhyo.api bhuutvaa prathama.n tato.asaa\-
           vasaadhyataa.n vyaadhiriva prayaati || 258||

tathaa ca \-

aatmanaH shaktimudviikShya maanotsaaha~nca yo vrajet |
bahuunhanti sa eko.api kShatriyaanbhaargavo yathaa || 259||

shashaka aaha \- astyetat | tathaapi balavaansa mayaa dR^iShTaH | tanna
yujyate svaaminastasya saamarthyamaviditvaa gantum | ukta~nca \-

aviditvaa.atmanaH shakti.n parasya ca samutsukaH |
gacChannabhimukho vahnau naasha.n yaati pata~Ngavat || 260||
yo balaatpronnata.n yaati nihantu.n sabalo.apyarim |
vimadaH sa nivarteta shiirNadanto gajo yathaa || 261||

bhaasuraka aaha \- bhoH ki.n tavaanena vyaapaareNa | darshaya me ta.n
durgasthamapi | atha shashaka aaha \- yadyeva.n tarhyaagacChatu svaamii |
evamuktvaa.agre vyavasthitaH | tatashca tenaagacChataa yaH kuupo
dR^iShTo.abhuuttameva kuupamaasaadya bhaasurakamaaha \- svaaminkaste
prataapa.n soDhu.n samarthaH | tvaa.n dR^iShTvaa duurato.api caurasi.nhaH
praviShTaH sva.n durgam | tadaagacCha yathaa darshayaamiiti | bhaasuraka
aaha \- darshaya me durgam | tadanu darshitastena kuupaH | tataH so.api
muurkhaH si.nhaH kuupamadhya aatmapratibimba.n jalamadhyagata.n
dR^iShTvaa si.nhanaada.n mumoca | tataH pratishabdena kuupamadhyaa\-
ddviguNataro naadaH samutthitaH | atha tena ta.n shatru.n matvaa.a.atmaana.n
tasyopari prakShipya praaNaaH parityaktaaH | shashako.api hR^iShTamanaaH
sarvamR^igaanaanandya taiH saha prashasyamaano yathaasukha.n tatra vane
nivasati sma | ato.aha.n braviimi \- yasya buddhirbala.n tasyeti | tadyadi
bhavaankathayati tattatraiva gatvaa tayoH svabuddhiprabhaaveNa maitriibheda.n
  karomi | karaTaka aaha \- bhadra yadyeva.n tarhi gacCha | shivaaste
panthaanaH santu | yathaabhipretamanuShThiiyataam | atha damanakaH
sa~njiivakaviyukta.n pi~Ngalakamavalokya tatraantare praNamyaagre
samupaviShTaH | pi~Ngalako.api tamaaha \- bhadra ki.n ciraaddR^iShTaH |
damanaka aaha \- na ki~nciddevapaadaanaamasmaabhiH prayojanam |
tenaaha.n naagacChaami | tathaapi raajaprayojanavinaashamavalokya
sa.ndahyamaanahR^idayo vyaakulatayaa svayamevaabhyaagato vaktum |
ukta~nca \-

priya.n vaa yadi vaa dveShya.n shubha.n vaa yadi vaa.ashubham |
apR^iShTo.api hita.n vakShyedyasya necChetparaabhavam || 262||

atha tasya saabhipraaya.n vacanamaakarNya pi~Ngalaka aaha \- ki.n
vaktumanaa bhavaan | tatkathyataa.n yatkathaniiyamasti | sa praaha \-
deva sa~njiivako yuShmatpaadaanaamupari drohabuddhiriti | vishvaasagatasya
mama vijana idamaaha \- bho damanaka dR^iShTaa mayaasya pi~Ngalakasya
saaraasaarataa | tadahamena.n hatvaa sakalamR^igaadhipatya.n tvatsaacivya\-
padaviisamanvita.n kariShyaami | pi~Ngalako.api 
tadvajrasaaraprahaarasadR^isha.n
daaruNa.n vacaH samaakarNya mohamupagato na ki~ncidapyuktavaan |
damanako.api tasya tamaakaaramaalokya cintitavaan \- aya.n taavatsa~njiivaka\-
nibaddharaagaH | tannuunamanena mantriNaa raajaa vinaashamavaapsyatiiti |
ukta~nca \-

eka.n bhuumipatiH karoti saciva.n raajye pramaaNa.n yadaa |
ta.n mohaacChrayate madaH sa ca madaaddaasyena nirvidyate |
nirviNNasya pada.n karoti hR^idaye tasya svatantraspR^ihaa |
svaatantryaspR^ihayaa tataH sa nR^ipateH praaNaanabhidruhyati || 263||

tatkimatra yuktamiti | pi~Ngalako.api cetanaa.n samaasaadya kathamapi
tamaaha \- sa~njiivakastaavatpraaNasamo bhR^ityaH | sa katha.n mamopari
drohabuddhi.n karoti | damanaka aaha \- deva bhR^ityo.abhR^itya
ityanekaantikametat | ukta~nca \-

na so.asti puruSho raadnyaa.n yo na kaamayate shriyam |
ashaktaa eva sarvatra narendra.n paryupaasate || 264||

pi~Ngalaka aaha \- bhadra tathaapi mama tasyopari cittavR^ittirna vikR^iti.n
yaati | athavaa saadhvidamucyate \-

anekadoShaduShTasya kaayaH kasya na vallabhaH |
kurvannapi vyaliikaani yaH priyaH priya eva saH || 265||

damanaka aaha \- ata evaaya.n doShaH | ukta~nca \-

yasminnevaadhika.n  cakShuraaropayati paarthivaH |
akuliinaH kuliino vaa sa shriyaa bhaajana.n naraH || 266||

apara.n kena guNavisheSheNa svaamii sa~njiivaka.n nirguNakamapi nikaTe
dhaarayati | atha deva yadyeva.n cintayasi mahaakaayo.ayam | anena
ripuunvyaapaadayiShyaami | tadasmaanna sidhyati yato.aya.n shaShpabhojii |
  devapaadaanaa.n punaH shatravo maa.nsaashinaH | tadripusaadhanamasya
saahaayyena na bhavati | tasmaadena.n duuShayitvaa hanyataamiti |
pi~Ngalaka aaha \-

ukto bhavati yaH puurva.n  guNavaan iti sa.nsadi |
tasya doSho na vaktavyaH pratidnyaabha~NgabhiiruNaa || 267||

anyacca | mayaa.asya tava vacanenaabhayapradaana.n dattam | tatkatha.n
svayameva vyaapaadayaami | sarvathaa sa~njiivako.aya.n suhR^idasmaakam |
na ta.n prati kashcinmanyuriti | ukta~nca \-

itaH sa daityaH praaptashriirneta evaarhati kShayam |
viShavR^ikSho.api sa.nvardhya svaya.n Chettumasaampratam || 268||
aadau na vaa praNayinaa.n praNayo vidheyo
           datto.athavaa pratidina.n paripoShaNiiyaH |
utkShipya yatkShipati tatprakaroti lajjaa.n
           bhuumau sthitasya patanaadbhayameva naasti || 269||
upakaariShu yaH saadhuH saadhutve tasya ko guNaH |
apakaariShu yaH saadhuH sa saadhuH sadbhirucyate || 270||

taddrohabuddherapi mayaa.asya na viruddhamaacaraNiiyam | damanaka
aaha \- svaamin | naiSha raajadharmo yaddrohabuddhirapi kShamyate |
ukta~nca \-

tulyaartha.n tulyasaamarthya.n marmadnya.n vyavasaayinam |
ardharaajyahara.n bhR^itya.n yo na hanyaatsa hanyate || 271||

apara.n tvayaasya sakhitvaatsarvo.api raajadharmaH parityaktaH |
raajadharmaabhaavaatsarvo.api parijano virakti.n gataH | yaH sa~njiivakaH
shaShpabhojii | bhavaan maa.nsaadaH | tava prakR^itayashca |
yattavaavadhyavyasaayabaahya.n kutastaasaa.n maa.nsaashanam |
yadrahitaastvaa.n tyaktvaa yaasyanti | tato.api tva.n vinaShTa eva | asya
sa~Ngatyaa punaste na kadaacidaakheTake matirbhaviShyati | ukta~nca \-

yaadR^ishaiH sevyate bhR^ityairyaadR^ishaa.nshcopasevate |
kadaacinnaatra sandehastaadR^igbhavati puuruShaH || 272||

tathaa ca \-

santaptaayasi sa.nsthitasya payaso naamaapi na dnyaayate |
muktakaaratayaa tadeva naliniipatrasthita.n raajate |
svaatau saagarashuktikukShipatita.n tajjaayate mauktikam |
praayeNaadhamamadhyamottamaguNaH sa.nvaasato jaayate || 273||

tathaa ca \-

asataa.n sa~NgadoSheNa satii yaati matirbhramam |
ekaraatripravaasena kaaShTha.n mu~nje pralambitam || 274||

ata eva santo niicasa~Nga.n varjayanti | ukta~nca \-

na hyavidnyaatashiilasya pradaatavyaH pratishrayaH |
matkuNasya ca doSheNa hataa mandavisarpiNii || 275||

pi~Ngalaka aaha \- kathametat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 9
mandavisarpiNiinaamayuukaakathaa |

asti kasyacinmahiipatermanorama.n shayanasthaanam | tatra
shvetatarapaTayugalamadhyasa.nsthitaa mandavisarpiNii yuukaa
prativasati sma | saa ca tasya mahiipate raktamaasvaadayantii
sukhena kaala.n nayamaanaa tiShThati | anyedyushca tatra
shayane kvacidbhraamyannagnimukho naama matkuNaH samaayaataH |
atha ta.n dR^iShTvaa saa viShaNNavadanaa provaaca | bho.agnimukha
kutastvamatraanucitasthaane samaayaataH | tadyaavanna kashcidvetti
taavacChiighra.n  gamyataamiti | sa aaha \- bhagavati
gR^ihaagatasyaasaadhorapi naitadyujyate vaktum | ukta~nca \-

ehyaagacCha samaavishaasanamida.n kasmaacciraaddR^ishyase |
kaa vaarteti sudurbalo.asi kushala.n priito.asmi te darshanaat |
eva.n ye samupaagataanpraNayinaH pratyaalapantyaadaraat |
teShaa.n yuktamasha~Nkitena manasaa harmyaaNi gantu.n sadaa || 276||

apara.n  mayaanekamaanuShaaNaamanekavidhaani rudhiraaNyaasvaa\-
ditaanyaahaaradoShaatkaTutiktakaShaayaamlarasaasvaadaani na ca
kadaacinmadhurarakta.n samaasvaaditam | tadyadi tva.n prasaada.n karoShi
tadasya nR^ipatervividhavya~njanaannapaanacoShyalehyasvaadvaahaara\-
vashaadasya shariire yanmiShTa.n rakta.n sa.n jaata.n
tadaasvaadanena saukhya.n sampaadayaami jihvaayaa iti |
ukta~nca \-

ra~Nkasya nR^ipatervaapi jihvaasaukhya.n sama.n smR^itam |
tanmaatra.n ca smR^ita.n saara.n tadartha.n yatate janaH || 277||
yadyeva na bhavelloke karma jihvaapratuShTidam |
tanna bhR^ityo bhavetkashcitkasyacidvashago.atha vaa || 278||
yadasatya.n vadenmartyo yadvaasevya.n ca sevate |
yadgacChati videsha.n ca tatsarvamudaraarthataH || 279||

tanmayaa gR^ihaagatena bubhukShayaa piiDyamaanenaapi
tvatsakaashaadbhojanamarthaniiyam | tanna tvayaikaakinyaasya
bhuupate raktabhojana.n kartu.n yujyate | tacChrutvaa mandavisarpiNyaaha \-
bho matkuNa | asya nR^ipaternidraavasha.n gatasya raktamaasvaadayaami |
punastvamagnimukhashcapalashca | tadyadi mayaa saha raktapaana.n
karoShi tattiShTha | abhiiShTatararaktamaasvaadaya | so.abraviit \- bhagavati
eva.n kariShyaami | yaavattva.n naasvaadayasi prathama.n nR^iparakta.n
taavanmama devagurukR^itaH shapathaH syaadyadi tadaasvaadayaami |
eva.n tayoH paraspara.n vadatoH sa raajaa tacChayanamaasaadya prasuptaH |
athaasau matkuNo jihvaalaulyotkR^iShTautsukyaajjaagratamapi ta.n
mahiipatimadashat | athavaa saadhvidamucyate |

svabhaavo nopadeshena shakyate kartumanyathaa |
sutaptamapi paaniiya.n punargacChati shiitataam || 280||
yadi syaacChiitalo vahniH shiitaa.nshurdahanaatmakaH |
na svabhaavo.atra martyaanaa.n shakyate kartumanyathaa || 281||

athaasau mahiipatiH suucyagraviddha iva tacChayana.n tyaktvaa
tatkShaNaadevotthitaH | aho dnyaayataamatra pracChaadanapaTe matkuNo
yuukaa vaa nuuna.n tiShThati yenaaha.n daShTa iti | atha ye ka~ncukinastatra
sthitaaste satvara.n pracChaadanapaTa.n gR^ihiitvaa suukShmadR^iShTyaa
viikShaa.ncakruH | atraantare sa matkuNashcaapalyaatkhaTvaanta.n
praviShTaH saa mandavisarpiNyapi vastrasandhyantargataa tairdR^iShTaa
vyaapaaditaa ca | ato.aha.n  braviimi \-  na hyavidnyaatashiilasya iti | eva.n
dnyaatvaa tvayaiSha vadhyaH | no cettvaa.n vyaapaadayiShyatiiti |
ukta~nca \-

tyaktaashcaabhyantaraa yena baahyaashcaabhyantariikR^itaaH |
sa eva mR^ityumaapnoti yathaa raajaa kakuddrumaH || 282||

pi~Ngalaka aaha \-  kathametat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 10
caNDaravanaamashR^igaalakathaa |

asti kasmi.nshcidvanoddeshe caNDaravo naama shR^igaalaH prativasati
sma | sa kadaacitkShudhaaviShTo jihvaalaulyaannagaramadhye praviShTaH |
atha ta.n nagaravaasinaH saarameyaa avalokya sarvataH shabdaayamaanaaH
paridhaavya tiikShNada.nShTraagrairbhakShitumaarabdhaaH | so.api
tairbhakShyamaaNaH praaNabhayaatpratyaasannarajakagR^iha.n  praviShTaH |
tatra niiliirasaparipuurNa.n  mahaabhaaNDa.n sajjiikR^itamaasiit | tatra
saarameyairaakraanto bhaaNDamadhye patitaH | atha yaavanniShkraanta\-
staavanniiliivarNaH sa~njaataH | tatraapare saarameyaasta.n
shR^igaalamajaananto yathaabhiiShTadisha.n jagmuH | caNDaravo.api
duuratara.n pradeshamaasaadya kaananaabhimukha.n pratasthe |
na ca niilavarNena kadaacinnijara~Ngastyajyate | ukta~nca \-

vajralepasya muurkhasya naariiNaa.n karkaTasya ca |
eko grahastu miinaanaa.n niiliimadyapayoryathaa || 283||

atha ta.n haragalagaralatamaalasamaprabhamapuurva.n sattvamavalokya
sarve si.nhavyaaghradviipivR^ikaprabhR^itayo.araNyanivaasino
bhayavyaakulitacittaaH samantaatpalaayanakriyaa.n kurvanti | kathayanti
ca \-  na dnyaayate.asya kiidR^igviceShTita.n pauruSha.n  ca |
tadduuratara.n gacChaamaH | ukta~nca \-

na yasya ceShTita.n vidyaanna kula.n na paraakramam |
na tasya vishvasetpraadnyo yadiicChecChriyamaatmanaH || 284||

caNDaravo.api bhayavyaakulitaanvidnyaayedamaaha \- bho bhoH
shvaapadaaH | ki.n yuuya.n maa.n dR^iShTvaiva sa.ntrastaa vrajatha |
tanna bhetavyam | aha.n brahmaNaadya svayameva sR^iShTvaabhihitaH \-
yacChvaapadaanaa.n kashcidraajaa naasti  | tattva.n mayaadya
sarvashvaapadaprabhutve.abhiShiktaH kakuddrumaabhidhaH | tato gatvaa
  kShititale taansarvaanparipaalayeti | tato.ahamatraagataH | tanmama
ChatracChaayaayaa.n sarvairapi shvaapadairvartitavyam | aha.n kakuddrumo
  naama raajaa trailokye.api sa.njaataH | tacChrutvaa si.nhavyaaghrapuraHsaraaH
shvaapadaaH svaaminprabho samaadisheti vadantasta.n parivavruH | atha tena
si.nhasyaamaatyapadavii pradattaa | vyaaghrasya shayyaapaalakatvam |
dviipinastaambuulaadhikaaraH | vR^ikasya dvaarapaalakatvam | ye caatmiiyaaH
shR^igaalaastaiH sahaalaapamaatramapi na karoti | shR^igaalaaH
sarve.apyadharmacandra.n dattvaa niHsaaritaaH | eva.n tasya raajyakriyayaa.n
vartamaanasya te si.nhaadayo mR^igaanvyaapaadya tatpurataH prakShipanti |
so.api prabhudharmeNa sarveShaa.n taanpravibhajya prayacChati | eva.n
gacChati kaale kadaacittena samaagatena duuradeshe shabdaayamaanasya
shR^igaalavR^indasya kolaahalo.ashraavi | ta.n shabda.n shrutvaa
pulakitatanuraanandaashrupuurNanayana utthaaya taarasvareNa
virotumaarabdhavaan | atha te si.nhaadayasta.n taarasvaramaakarNya
shR^igaalo.ayamiti matvaa lajjayaa.adhomukhaaH kShaNa.n sthitvaa procuH \-
bhoH | vaahitaa vayamanena kShudrashR^igaalena | tadvadhyataamiti | so.api
tadaakarNya palaayitumicCha{\m+}statra sthaana eva si.nhaadibhiH
khaNDashaH kR^ito mR^itashca |ato.aha.n braviimi \-  tyaktaashcaabhyantaraa
yeneti | tadaakarNya pi~Ngalaka aaha \- bho damanaka | kaH pratyayo.atra
viShaye yatsa mamopari duShTabuddhiH |sa aaha \- yadadya mamaagre tena
nishcayaH kR^ito yatprabhaate pi~Ngalaka.n vadhiShyaami | tadatraiva
pratyayaH | prabhaate.avasaravelaayaamaaraktamukhanayanaH
sphuritaadharo disho.avalokayannanucitasthaanopaviShTastvaa.n
kruuradR^iShTyaa vilokayiShyati | eva.n dnyaatvaa yaducita.n tatkartavyam |
iti kathayitvaa sa.njiivakasakaasha.n gatasta.n praNamyopaviShTaH |
sa.njiivako.api sodvegaakaara.n mandagatyaa samaayaanta.n tamudviikShya
saadarataramuvaaca \-  bho mitra | svaagatam | ciraaddR^iShTo.asi | api
shiva.n bhavataH | tatkathaya yenaadeyamapi tubhya.n gR^ihaagataaya
prayacChaami | ukta~nca \-

te dhanyaaste vivekadnyaaste sabhyaa iha bhuutale |
aagacChanti gR^ihe yeShaa.n kaaryaartha.n suhR^ido janaaH || 285||

damanaka aaha \- bhoH | katha.n shiva.n sevakajanasya |

sampattayaH paraayattaaH sadaa cittamanirvR^itam |
svajiivite.apyavishvaasasteShaa.n ye raajasevakaaH || 286||

tathaa ca \-

sevayaa dhanamicChadbhiH sevakaiH pashya yatkR^itam |
svaatantrya.n yacChariirasya muuDhaistadapi haaritam || 287||
taavajjanmaatiduHkhaaya tato durgatataa sadaa |
tatraapi sevayaa vR^ittiraho duHkhaparamparaa || 288||
jiivanto.api mR^itaaH pa~nca shruuyante kila bhaarate |
daridro vyaadhito muurkhaH pravaasii nityasevakaH || 289||
naashnaati svacChayotsukyaadvinidro na prabudhyate |
na niHsha~Nka.n vaco bruute sevako.apyatra jiivati || 290||
sevaa shvavR^ittiraakhyaataa yaistairmithyaa prajalpitam |
svacChanda.n carati shvaa.atra sevakaH parashaasanaat || 291||
bhuushayyaa brahmacarya.n ca kR^ishatva.n laghubhojanam |
sevakasya yateryadvadvisheShaH paapadharmajaH || 292||
shiitaatapaadikaShTaani sahate yaani sevakaH |
dhanaaya taani caalpaani yadi dharmaanna mucyate || 293||
mR^idunaapi suvR^ittena sushliShTenaapi haariNaa |
modakenaapi ki.n tena niShpattiryasya sevayaa || 294||

sa.njiivaka aaha \- atha bhavaanki.n vaktumanaaH | so.abraviit \- mitra
sacivaanaa.n mantrabheda.n kartu.n na yujyate | ukta~nca \-

yo mantra.n svaamino bhidyaatsaacivye sanniyojitaH |
sa hatvaa nR^ipakaarya.n tatsvaya.n ca naraka.n vrajet || 295||
yena yasya kR^ito bhedaH sacivena mahiipateH |
tenaashastravadhastasya kR^ita ityaaha naaradaH || 296||

tathaapi mayaa tava snehapaashabaddhena mantrabhedaH kR^itaH |
yatastva.n mama vacanenaatra raajakule vishvastaH praviShTashca |
ukta~nca \-

vishrambhaadyasya yo mR^ityumavaapnoti katha~ncana |
tasya hatyaa tadutthaa saa praaheda.n vacana.n manuH || 297||

tattavopari pi~Ngalako.aya.n duShTabuddhiH kathita.n caadyaanena
matpuratashcatuShkarNatayaa \-  yatprabhaate sa.njiivaka.n hatvaa
samastamR^igaparivaara.n ciraattR^ipti.n neShyaami | tataH sa mayoktaH \-
svaamin | na yuktamida.n yanmitradroheNa jiivana.n kriyate | ukta~nca \-

api brahmavadha.n kR^itvaa praayashcittena shudhyati |
tadarthena viciirNena na katha~ncitsuhR^iddruhaH || 298||

tatastenaaha.n saamarSheNoktaH \-  bho duShTabuddhe
sa.njiivakastaavacChaShpabhojii vaya.n maa.nsaashinaH | tadasmaaka.n
svaabhaavika.n vairamiti katha.n ripurupekShyate | tasmaatsaamaadibhiru\-
paayairhanyate | na ca hate tasmindoShaH syaat | ukta~nca \-

dattvaapi kanyakaa.n vairii nihantavyo vipashcitaa |
anyopaayairashakyo yo hate doSho na vidyate || 299||
kR^ityaakR^itya.n na manyeta kShatriyo yudhi sa~NgataH |
prasupto droNaputreNa dhR^iShTadyumnaH puraa hataH || 300||

tadaha.n tasya nishcaya.n dnyaatvaa tvatsakaashamihaagataH | saamprata.n
me naasti vishvaasaghaatakadoShaH | mayaa suguptamantrastava niveditaH |
atha yatte pratibhaati tatkuruShva iti | atha sa.njiivakastasya
tadvajrapaatadaaruNa.n vacana.n shrutvaa mohamupagataH | atha
cetanaa.n labdhvaa savairaagyamidamaaha \- bhoH saadhvidamucyate \-

durjanagamyaa naaryaH praayeNaasnehavaanbhavati raajaa |
kR^ipaNaanusaari ca dhana.n megho giridurgavarShii ca || 301||
aha.n hi sa.nmato raadnyo ya eva.n manyate kudhiiH |
baliivardaH sa vidnyeyo viShaaNaparivarjitaH || 302||
vara.n vana.n vara.n bhaikSha.n vara.n bhaaropajiivanam |
vara.n vyaadhirmanuShyaaNaa.n naadhikaareNa sampadaH || 303||

tadayukta.n mayaa kR^ita.n yadanena saha maitrii vihitaa | ukta~nca \-

yayoreva sama.n vitta.n yayoreva sama.n kulam |
tayormaitrii vivaahashca na tu puShTavipuShTayoH || 304||

tathaa ca \-

mR^igaa mR^igaiH sa~Ngamanuvrajanti
           gaavashca gobhisturagaasturagaiH |
muurkhaashca muurkhaiH sudhiyaH sudhiibhiH
           samaanashiilavyasanena sakhyam || 305||

tadyadi gatvaa ta.n prasaadayaami tathaapi na prasaada.n yaasyati |
ukta~nca \-

nimittamuddishya hi yaH prakupyati
           dhruva.n sa tasyaapagame prashaamyati |
akaaraNadveShaparo hi yo bhavet
           katha.n narasta.n paritoShayiShyati || 306||

aho saadhu cedamucyate \-

bhaktaanaamupakaariNaa.n parahitavyaapaarayuktaatmanaam |
sevaasa.nvyavahaaratattvaviduShaa.n drohacyutaanaamapi |
vyaapattiH skhalitaantareShu niyataa siddhirbhavedvaa na vaa |
tasmaadambupaterivaavanipateH sevaa sadaa sha~Nkinii || 307||

tathaa ca \-

bhaavasnigdhairupakR^itamapi dveShyataa.n yaati loke |
saakShaadanyairapakR^itamapi priitaye copayaati |
durgraahyatvaannR^ipatimanasaa.n naikabhaavaashrayaaNaam |
sevaadharmaH paramagahano yoginaamapyagamyaH || 308||

tatparidnyaata.n mayaa matprasaadamasahamaanaiH samiipavartibhireSha
pi~NgalakaH prakopitaH | tenaaya.n mamaadoShasyaapyeva.n vadati |
ukta~nca \-

prabhoH prasaadamanyasya na sahantiiha sevakaaH |
sapatnya iva sa.nkruddhaaH sapatnyaaH sukR^itairapi || 309||

bhavati caiva.n yadguNavatsu samiipavartiShu guNahiinaanaa.n na prasaado
bhavati | ukta~nca \-

guNavattarapaatreNa cChaadyante guNinaa.n guNaaH |
raatrau diipashikhaakaantirna bhaanaavudite sati || 310||

damanaka aaha \- bho mitra | yadyeva.n tannaasti te bhayam | prakopito.api
sa durjanaistava vacanaracanayaa prasaada.n yaasyati | sa aaha \- bhoH |
na yuktamukta.n bhavataa | laghuunaamapi durjanaanaa.n madhye vastu.n
na shakyate | upaayaantara.n vidhaaya te nuuna.n ghnanti | ukta~nca \-

bahavaH paNDitaaH kShudraaH sarve maayopajiivinaH |
kuryuH kR^ityamakR^itya.n vaa uShTre kaakaadayo yathaa || 311||

damanaka aaha \- kathametat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 11
madotkaTasi.nhakathaa |

asti kasmi.nshcidvanoddeshe madotkaTo naama si.nhaH prativasati sma |
tasya caanucaraa anye dviipivaayasagomaayavaH santi | atha
kadaacittairitastato bhramadbhiH saarthaadbhraShTaH krathanako
naamoShTro dR^iShTaH | atha si.nha aaha \- aho apuurvamida.n sattvam |
tajdnyaayataa.n kimetadaaraNyaka.n graamya.n veti | tacChrutvaa vaayasa
aaha \- bhoH svaamin | graamyo.ayamuShTranaamaa jiivavisheShastava
bhojyaH | tadvyaapaadyataam | si.nha aaha \- naaha.n gR^ihamaagata.n
hanmi | ukta~nca \-

gR^iha.n shatrumapi praapta.n vishvastamakutobhayam |
yo hanyaattasya paapa.n syaacChatabraahmaNaghaatajam || 312||

tadabhayapradaana.n dattvaa matsakaashamaaniiyataa.n yenaasyaagama\-
kaaraNa.n pR^icChaami | athaasau sarvairapi vishvaasyaabhayapradaana.n
dattvaa madotkaTasakaashamaaniitaH praNamyopaviShTashca | tatastasya
pR^icChatastenaatmavR^ittaantaH saarthabhra.nshasamudbhavo niveditaH |
tataH si.nhenoktam \-  bhoH krathanaka | maa tva.n graama.n gatvaa
bhuuyo.api bhaarodvahanakaShTabhaagii bhuuyaaH | tadatraivaaraNye
nirvisha~Nko marakatasadR^ishaani shaShpaagraaNi bhakShayanmayaa
saha sadaiva vasa | so.api tathetyuktvaa teShaa.n madhye vicaranna kuto.api
bhayamiti sukhenaaste | tathaanyedyurmadotkaTasya mahaagajenaa\-
raNyacaariNaa saha yuddhamabhavat | tatastasya dantamusalaprahaarairvyathaa
sa~njaataa | vyathitaH kathamapi praaNairna viyuktaH | atha
shariiraasaamarthyaanna kutracitpadamapi calitu.n shaknoti | te sarve
kaakaadayo.apyaprabhutvena kShudhaaviShTaaH para.n duHkha.n bhejuH |
atha taansi.nhaH praaha \- bhoH | anviShyataa.n kutracitki.ncitsattva.n
yenaahametaamapi dashaa.n praaptastaddhatvaa yuShmadbhojana.n
sampaadayaami | atha te catvaaro.api bhramitumaarabdhaa yaavanna
ki.ncitsattva.n pashyanti taavadvaayasashR^igaalau paraspara.n mantrayataH |
shR^igaala aaha \- bho vaayasa | ki.n prabhuutabhraantena | ayamasmaaka.n
prabhoH krathanako vishvastastiShThati | tadena.n hatvaa praaNayaatraa.n
kurmaH | vaayasa aaha \- yuktamukta.n bhavataa | para.n svaaminaa
tasyaabhayapradaana.n dattamaaste na vadhyo.ayamiti | shR^igaala aaha \-
  bho vaayasa | aha.n svaamina.n vidnyaapya tathaa kariShye yathaa svaamii
vadha.n kariShyati | tattiShThantu bhavanto.atraiva yaavadaha.n gR^iha.n
gatvaa prabhoraadnyaa.n gR^ihiitvaa caagacChaami | evamabhidhaaya
satvara.n si.nhamuddishya prasthitaH | atha si.nhamaasaadyedamaaha \-
svaamin | samasta.n vana.n bhraantvaa vayamaagataaH | na
ki.ncitsattvamaasaaditam | tatki.n kurmo vayam | samprati vaya.n
bubhukShayaa padamekamapi pracalitu.n na shaknumaH | devo.api
pathyaashii vartate | tadyadi devaadesho bhavati tatkrathanakapishitenaadya
pathyakriyaa kriyate | atha si.nhastasya taddaaruNa.n vacanamaakarNya
sakopamidamaaha \- dhikpaapaadhama | yadyeva.n bhuuyo.api vadasi
tatastvaa.n tatkShaNameva vadhiShyaami | tato mayaa tasyaabhaya.n
pradattam | tatkatha.n vyaapaadayaami | ukta~nca \-

na gopradaana.n na mahiipradaana.n
           na caannadaana.n hi tathaa pradhaanam |
yathaa vadantiiha budhaaH pradhaana.n
           sarvapradaaneShvabhayapradaanam || 313||

tacChrutvaa shR^igaala aaha \- svaamin yadyabhayapradaana.n dattvaa
vadhaH kriyate tadeSha doSho bhavati | punaryadi devapaadaanaa.n
bhaktyaa sa aatmano jiivitavya.n prayacChati tanna doShaH | tato yadi sa
svayamevaatmaana.n vadhaaya niyojayati tadvadhyo.anyathaasmaaka.n
madhyaadekatamo vadhya iti | yato devapaadaaH pathyaashinaH
kShunnirodhaadantyaa.n dashaa.n yaasyanti | tatkimetaiH praaNairasmaaka.n
ye svaamyarthe na yaasyanti | apara.n pashcaadapyasmaabhirvahnipraveshaH
kaaryo yadi svaamipaadaanaa.n ki.ncidaniShTa.n bhaviShyati | ukta~nca \-

yasminkule yaH puruShaH pradhaanaH
           sa sarvayatnaiH parirakShaNiiyaH |
tasminvinaShTe svakula.n vinaShTa.n
           na naabhibha~Nge hyarakaa vahanti || 314||

tadaakarNya madotkaTa aaha \- yadyeva.n tatkuruShva yadrocate |
tacChrutvaa sa satvara.n gatvaa taanaaha \- bhoH | svaamino mahatyavasthaa
vartate | tatki.n paryaTitena | tena vinaa ko.atraasmaanrakShayiShyati |
tadgatvaa tasya kShudrogaatparaloka.n prasthitasyaatmashariiradaana.n
kurmo yena svaamiprasaadasyaanR^iNataa.n gacChaamaH | ukta~nca \-

aapada.n praapnuyaatsvaamii yasya bhR^ityasya pashyataH |
praaNeShu vidyamaaneShu sa bhR^ityo naraka.n vrajet || 315||

tadanantara.n te sarve baaShpapuuritadR^isho madotkaTa.n
praNamyopaviShTaaH | taandR^iShTvaa madotkaTa aaha \- bhoH | praapta.n
dR^iShTa.n vaa ki~ncitsattvam | atha teShaa.n madhyaatkaakaH provaaca \-
svaamin | vaya.n taavatsarvatra paryaTitaaH para.n na 
ki~ncitsattvamaasaadita.n
dR^iShTa.n vaa | tadadya maa.n bhakShayitvaa praaNaandhaarayatu svaamii
yena devasyaashvaasana.n bhavati mama punaH svargapraaptiriti | ukta~nca \-

svaamyarthe yastyajetpraaNaanbhR^ityo bhaktisamanvitaH |
sa para.n padamaapnoti jaraamaraNavarjitam || 316||

tacChrutvaa shR^igaala aaha \- bhoH svalpakaayo bhavaan | tava
bhakShaNaatsvaaminastaavatpraaNayaatraa na bhavati | aparo doShashca
taavatsamutpadyate | ukta~nca \-

kaakamaa.nsa.n tathocChiShTa.n stoka.n tadapi durbalam |
bhakShitenaapi ki.n tena yena tR^iptirna jaayate || 317||

taddarShitaa svaamibhaktirbhavataa gata.n caa.anR^iNya.n bhartR^ipiNDasya
praaptashcobhayaloke saadhuvaadaH | tadapasaraagrataH | aha.n svaamina.n
vidnyaapayaami | tathaanuShThite shR^igaalaH saadara.n
praNamyopaviShTaH praaha \- svaamin | maa.n bhakShayitvaadya
praaNayaatraa.n vidhaaya mamobhayalokapraapti.n kuru | ukta~nca \-

svaamyaayattaaH sadaa praaNaa bhR^ityaanaamarjitaa dhanaiH |
yatastato na doSho.asti teShaa.n grahaNasambhavaH || 318||

atha tacChrutvaa dviipyaaha \- bhoH saadhuukta.n bhavataa punarbhavaanapi
svalpakaayaH svajaatishca nakhaayudhatvaadabhakShya eva | ukta~nca \-

naabhakShya.n bhakShayetpraadnyaH praaNaiH kaNThagatairapi |
visheShaattadapi stoka.n lokadvayavinaashakam || 319||

taddarshita.n tvayaatmanaH kauliinyam | athavaa saadhu cedamucyate \-

etadartha.n kuliinaanaa.n nR^ipaaH kurvanti sa~Ngraham |
aadimadhyaavasaaneShu na te gacChanti vikriyaam || 320||

tadapasaraagrataH yenaaha.n svaamina.n vidnyaapayaami | tathaanuShThite
dviipii praNamya madotkaTamaaha \- svaamin | kriyataamadya mama
praaNaiH praaNayaatraa | diiyataamakShayo vaasaH svarge | mama
vistaaryataa.n kShititale prabhuuta.n yashaH | tannaatra vismayaH
kaaryaH | ukta~nca \-

mR^itaanaa.n svaaminaH kaarye bhR^ityaanaamanuvartinaam |
bhavetsvarge.akShayo vaasaH kiirtishca dharaNiitale || 321||

tacChrutvaa krathanakashcintayaamaasa \-  etaistaavatsarvairapi
shobhaavaakyaanyuktaani na caiko.api svaaminaa vinaashitaH | tadahamapi
praaptakaala.n vakShyaami yena madvacanamete trayo.api samarthayanti |
  iti nishcitya provaaca \-  bhoH satyamukta.n bhavataa para.n bhavaanapi
nakhaayudhaH | tatkatha.n bhavanta.n svaamii bhakShayati | ukta~nca \-

manasaa.api svajaatyaanaa.n yo.aniShTaani pracintayet |
bhavanti tasya taanyeva iha loke paratra ca || 322||

tadapasaraagrataH yenaaha.n svaamina.n vidnyaapayaami | tathaanuShThite
krathanako.agre sthitvaa praNamyovaaca \-  svaamin | ete.abhakShyaastava
tanmama praaNaiH praaNayaatraa vidhiiyataa.n yena
mamobhayalokapraaptirbhavati | ukta~nca \-

na yajvaano.api gacChanti taa.n gati.n naiva yoginaH |
yaa.n yaanti projjhitapraaNaaH svaamyarthe sevakottamaaH || 323||

evamabhihite taabhyaa.n shR^igaalacitrakaabhyaa.n vidaaritobhayakukShiH
krathanakaH praaNaanatyaakShiit | tatashca taiH kShudrapaNDitaiH
sarvairbhakShitaH | ato.aha.n braviimi \-  bahavaH paNDitaaH kShudraa iti |
tadbhadra kShudraparivaaro.aya.n te raajaa mayaa samyagdnyaataH |
sataamasevyashca | ukta~nca \-

ashuddhaprakR^itau raadnyi janataa naanurajyate |
yathaa gR^idhrasamaasannaH kalaha.nsaH samaacaret || 324||

tathaa ca \-

gR^idhraakaaro.api sevyaH syaaddha.nsaakaaraiH sabhaasadaiH |
ha.nsaakaaro.api santyaajyo gR^idhraakaaraiH sa tairnR^ipaH || 325||

tannuuna.n mamopari kenaciddurjanenaaya.n prakopitaH tenaiva.n vadati |
athavaa bhavatyetat | ukta~nca \-

mR^idunaa salilena khanyamaanaa\-
           nyavaghR^iShyanti girerapi sthalaani |
upajaapavidaa.n ca karNajaapaiH
           kimu cetaa.nsi mR^iduuni maanavaanaam || 326||
karNaviSheNa ca bhagnaH ki.n ki.n na karoti baalisho lokaH |
kShapaNakataamapi dhatte pibati suraa.n narakapaalena || 327||

athavaa saadhvidamucyate \-

paadaahato.api dR^iDhadaNDasamaahato.api
           ya.n da.nShTrayaa spR^ishati ta.n kila hanti sarpaH |
ko.apyeSha eva pishunogramanuShyadharmaH
           karNe para.n spR^ishati hanti para.n samuulam || 328||

tathaa ca \-

aho khalabhuja~Ngasya vipariito vadhakramaH |
karNe lagati caanyasya praaNairanyo viyujyate || 329||

tadeva.n gate.api ki.n kartavyamityaha.n tvaa.n suhR^idbhaavaatpR^icChaami |
damanaka aaha \- taddeshaantaragamana.n yujyate | naiva.nvidhasya
kusvaaminaH sevaa.n vidhaatum | ukta~nca \-

gurorapyavaliptasya kaaryaakaaryamajaanataH |
utpathapratipannasya parityaago vidhiiyate || 330||

sa.njiivaka aaha \- asmaakamupari svaamini kupite gantu.n na
shakyate na caanyatra gataanaamapi nirvR^itirbhavati | ukta~nca \-

mahataa.n yo.aparaadhyeta duurastho.asmiiti naashvaset |
diirghau buddhimato baahuu taabhyaa.n hi.nsati hi.nsakam || 331||

tadyuddha.n muktvaa me naanyadasti shreyaskaram | ukta~nca \-

na taanhi tiirthaistapasaa ca lokaan\-
           svargaiShiNo daanashataiH suvR^ittaiH |
kShaNena yaanyaanti raNeShu dhiiraaH
           praaNaansamujjhanti hi ye sushiilaaH || 332||
mR^itaiH sampraapyate svargo jiivadbhiH kiirtiruttamaa |
tadubhaavapi shuuraaNaa.n guNaavetau sudurlabhau || 333||
lalaaTadeshe rudhira.n sravattu
           shuurasya yasya pravishecca vaktre |
tatsomapaanena sama.n bhavecca
           sa~Ngraamayadnye vidhivatpradiShTam || 334||

tathaa ca \-

homaarthairvidhivatpradaanavidhinaa sadvipravR^indaarcanai \-
ryadnyairbhuurisudakShiNaiH suvihitaiH sampraapyate yatphalam |
sattiirthaashramavaasahomaniyamaishcaandraayaNaadyaiH kR^itaiH
pu.nbhistatphalamaahave vinihitaiH sampraapyate tatkShaNaat || 335||

tadaakarNya damanakashcintayaamaasa \-  yuddhaaya kR^itanishcayo.aya.n
dR^ishyate duraatmaa | tadyadi kadaacittiikShNashR^i~Ngaabhyaa.n
svaamina.n prahariShyati tanmahaananarthaH sampatsyate | tadena.n
bhuuyo.api svabuddhyaa prabodhya tathaa karomi yathaa
deshaantaragamana.n karoti | aaha ca \-  bho mitra | samyagabhihita.n
bhavataa | para.n kaH svaamibhR^ityayoH sa~NgraamaH | ukta~nca \-

balavanta.n ripu.n dR^iShTvaa kilaatmaana.n pragopayet |
balavadbhishca kartavyaa sharaccandraprakaashataa || 336||

anyacca \-

shatrorvikramamadnyaatvaa vairamaarabhate hi yaH |
sa paraabhavamaapnoti samudraShTiTTibhaadyathaa || 337||

sa.njiivaka aaha \- kathametat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 12
TiTTibhadampatiikathaa |

kasmi.nshcitsamudraikadeshe TiTTibhadampatii prativasataH sma | tato
gacChati kaala R^itusamayamaasaadya TiTTibhii garbhamaadhatta |
aasannaprasavaa satii saa TiTTibhamuuce \-  bhoH kaanta | mama
prasavasamayo vartate | tadvicintyataa.n kimapi nirupadrava.n sthaana.n
yena tatraahamaNDakamokShaNa.n karomi |TiTTibhaH praaha \- bhadre
ramyo.aya.n samudrapradeshaH | tadatraiva prasavaH kaaryaH | saa
praaha \- atra puurNimaadine samudravelaa carati | saa mattagajendraanapi
samaakarShati | tadduuramanyatra ki~ncitsthaanamanviShyataam |
tacChrutvaa vihasya TiTTibha aaha \- bhadre na yuktamukta.n bhavatyaa |
kaa maatraa samudrasya yo mama duuShayiShyati prasuutim | ki.n na
shruta.n bhavatyaa \-

baddhvaambaracaramaarga.n vyapagatadhuuma.n sadaa mahadbhayadam |
mandamatiH kaH pravishati hutaashana.n svecChayaa manujaH || 338||
mattebhakumbhavidalanakR^itashrama.n suptamantakapratimam |
yamalokadarshanecChuH si.nha.n bodhayati ko naama || 339||
ko gatvaa yamasadana.n svayamantakamaadishatyajaatabhayaH |
praaNaanapahara matto yadi shaktiH kaacidasti tava || 340||
praaleyaleshamishre maruti praabhaatike ca vaati jaDe |
guNadoShadnyaH puruSho jalena kaH shiitamapanayati || 341||

tasmaadvishrabdhaa.atraiva garbha.n mu~nca | ukta~nca \-

yaH paraabhavasantrastaH svasthaana.n santyajennaraH |
tena cetputriNii maataa tadvandhyaa kena kathyate || 342||

tacChrutvaa samudrashcintayaamaasa \-  aho garvaH pakShikiiTasyaasya |
athavaa saadhvidamucyate \-

utkShipya TiTTibhaH paadaavaaste bha~NgabhayaaddivaH |
svacittakalpito garvaH kasya naatraapi vidyate || 343||

tanmayaasya pramaaNa.n kutuuhalaadapi draShTavyam | ki.n
mamaiSho.aNDaapahaare kR^ite kariShyati | iti cintayitvaa sthitaH |
atha prasavaanantara.n praaNayaatraartha.n gataayaaShTiTTibhyaaH
samudro velaavyaajenaaNDaanyapajahaara | athaayaataa saa TiTTibhii
prasavasthaana.n shuunyamavalokya pralapantii TiTTibhamuuce \-  bho
muurkha | kathitamaasiinmayaa te yatsamudravelayaa.aNDaanaa.n vinaasho
bhaviShyati tadduuratara.n vrajaavaH para.n muuDhatayaa.aha.nkaara\-
maashritya mama vacana.n na karoShi | athavaa saadhvidamucyate |

suhR^idaa.n hitakaamaanaa.n na karotiiha yo vacaH |
sa kuurma iva durbuddhiH kaaShThaadbhraShTo vinashyati || 344||

TiTTibha aaha \- kathametat | saabraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 13
kambugriivaakhyakuurmakathaa |

asti kasmi.nshcijjalaashaye kambugriivo naama kacChapaH | tasya ca
sa~NkaTavikaTanaamnii mitre ha.nsajaatiiye paramasnehakoTimaashrite
nityameva sarastiiramaasaadya tena sahaanekadevarShimaharShiiNaa.n
kathaaH kR^itvaa.astamayavelaayaa.n svaniiDaasa.nshraya.n kurutaH | atha
gacChataa kaalenaavR^iShTivashaat saraH shanaiH shanaiH
shoShamagamat | tatastadduHkhaduHkhitau taavuucatuH \-  bho mitra |
jambaalasheShametatsaraH  sa~njaatam | tatkatha.n bhavaanbhaviShyatiiti
vyaakulatva.n no hR^idi vartate | tacChrutvaa kambugriiva aaha \- bhoH
saamprata.n naastyasmaaka.n jiivitavya.n jalaabhaavaat |
tathaapyupaayashcintyataamiti | ukta~nca \-

tyaajya.n na dhairya.n vidhure.api kaale
           dhairyaatkadaacidgatimaapnuyaatsaH |
yathaa samudre.api ca potabha~Nge
           saa.nyaatriko vaa~nChati tartumeva || 345||

apara~nca \-

mitraarthe baandhavaarthe ca buddhimaanyatate sadaa |
jaataasvaapatsu yatnena jagaadeda.n vaco manuH || 346||

tadaaniiyataa.n kaaciddR^iDharajjurlaghukaaShTha.n vaa | anviShyataa.n
ca prabhuutajalasanaatha.n saraH yena mayaa madhyapradeshe
dantairgR^ihiite sati yuvaa.n koTibhaagayostatkaaShTha.n mayaa sahita.n
sa~NgR^ihya tatsaro nayathaH | taavuucatuH \-  bho mitra | eva.n
kariShyaavaH | para.n bhavataa maunavratena sthaatavyam | no cettava
kaaShThaatpaato bhaviShyati | tathaanuShThite gacChataa
kambugriiveNaadhobhaagavyavasthita.n ki~ncitpuramaalokitam | tatra ye
pauraaste tathaa niiyamaana.n vilokya savismayamidamuucuH \-  aho
cakraakaara.n kimapi pakShibhyaa.n niiyate | pashyata pashyata | atha
teShaa.n kolaahalamaakarNya kambugriiva aaha \- bhoH | kimeSha
kolaahalaH | iti vaktumanaa ardhokte patitaH pauraiH khaNDashaH
kR^itashca | ato.aha.n braviimi \-  suhR^idaa.n hitakaamaanaamiti |
tathaa ca \-

anaagatavidhaataa ca pratyutpannamatistathaa |
dvaavetau sukhamedhete yadbhaviShyo vinashyati || 347||

TiTTibha aaha \- kathametat | saa.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 14
anaagatavidhaataadimatsyatrayakathaa |

kasmi.nshcijjalaashaye.anaagatavidhaataa pratyutpannamati\-
ryadbhaviShyashceti trayo matsyaaH santi | atha kadaacitta.n jalaashaya.n
dR^iShTvaa gacChadbhirmatsyajiivibhirukta.n yadaho bahumatsyo.aya.n
hradaH | kadaacidapi naasmaabhiranveShitaH | tadadya taavadaahaaravR^ittiH
sa~njaataa | sandhyaasamayashca sa.nvR^ittaH | tataH
prabhaate.atraagantavyamiti nishcayaH | atasteShaa.n
tatkulishapaatopama.n vacaH samaakarNyaanaagatavidhaataa
sarvaanmatsyaanaahuuyedamuuce \-  aho shruta.n
bhavadbhiryanmatsyajiivibhirabhihitam | tadraatraavapi gamyataa.n
ki~ncinnikaTa.n saraH | ukta~nca \-

ashaktairbalinaH shatroH kartavya.n prapalaayanam |
sa.nshritavyo.athavaa durgo naanyaa teShaa.n gatirbhavet || 348||

tannuuna.n prabhaatasamaye matsyajiivino.atra samaagamya
matsyasa.nkShaya.n kariShyanti | etanmama manasi vartate |
tanna yukta.n saamprata.n kShaNamapyatraavasthaatum | ukta~nca \-

vidyamaanaa gatiryeShaamanyatraapi sukhaavahaa |
te na pashyanti vidvaa.nso dehabha~Nga.n kulakShayam || 349||

tadaakarNya pratyutpannamatiH praaha \- aho satyamabhihita.n bhavataa |
mamaapyabhiiShTametat | tadanyatra gamyataamiti | ukta~nca \-

paradeshabhayaadbhiitaa bahumaayaa napu.nsakaaH |
svadeshe nidhana.n yaanti kaakaaH kaapuruShaa mR^igaaH || 350||
yasyaasti sarvatra gatiH sa kasmaat
           svadesharaageNa hi yaati naasham |
taatasya kuupo.ayamiti bruvaaNaaH
           kShaara.n jala.n kaapuruShaaH pibanti || 351||

atha tatsamaakarNya proccairvihasya  yadbhaviShyaH provaaca \-  aho na
bhavadbhyaa.n mantrita.n samyagetaditi yataH ki.n vaa~NmaatreNaapi
teShaa.n pitR^ipaitaamahikametatsarastyaktu.n yujyate |
yadyaayuHkShayo.asti tadanyatra gataanaamapi mR^ityurbhaviShyatyeva |
ukta~nca \-

arakShita.n tiShThati daivarakShita.n surakShita.n daivahata.n vinashyati |
jiivatyanaatho.api vane visarjitaH kR^itaprayatno.api gR^ihe na 
jiivati || 352||

tadaha.n na yaasyaami | bhavadbhyaa.n ca yatpratibhaati tatkartavyam |
atha tasya ta.n nishcaya.n dnyaatvaa.anaagatavidhaataa
pratyutpannamatishca niShkraantau saha parijanena | atha prabhaate
tairmatsyajiivibhirjaalaistajjalaashayamaaloDya yadbhaviShyeNa saha tatsaro
nirmatsyataa.n niitam | ato.aha.n braviimi \-  anaagatavidhaataa ceti |
tacChrutvaa TiTTibha aaha \- bhadre ki.n maa.n yadbhaviShyasadR^isha.n
sambhaavayasi | tatpashya me buddhiprabhaava.n yaavadena.n
duShTasamudra.n svaca~ncvaa shoShayaami | TiTTibhyaaha \- aho kaste
samudreNa saha vigrahaH | tanna yuktamasyopari kopa.n kartum |
ukta~nca \-

pu.nsaamasamarthaanaamupadravaayaatmano bhavetkopaH |
piThara.n jvaladatimaatra.n nijapaarshvaaneva dahatitaraam || 353||

tathaa ca \-

aviditvaatmanaH shakti.n parasya na samutsukaH |
gacChannabhimukho vahnau naasha.n yaati pata~Ngavat || 354||

TiTTibha aaha \- priye maa maiva.n vada | yeShaamutsaahashaktirbhavati
te svalpaa api guruunvikramante | ukta~nca \-

visheShaatparipuurNasya yaati shatroramarShaNaH |
aabhimukhya.n shashaa~Nkasya yathaadyaapi vidhuntudaH || 355||

tathaa ca \-

pramaaNaadadhikasyaapi gaNDashyaamamadacyuteH |
pada.n muurdhni samaadhatte kesarii mattadantinaH || 356||

tathaa ca \-

baalasyaapi raveH paadaaH patantyupari bhuubhR^itaam |
tejasaa saha jaataanaa.n vayaH kutropayujyate || 357||
hastii sthuulataraH sa caa~NkushavashaH ki.n hastimaatro.a~NkushoH |
diipe prajvalite praNashyati tamaH ki.n diipamaatra.n tamaH |
vajreNaapi hataaH patanti girayaH ki.n vajramaatro giri \-
stejo yasya viraajate sa balavaansthuuleShu kaH pratyayaH || 358||

tadanayaa ca~ncvaasya sakala.n toya.n shuShkasthalataa.n nayaami |
TiTTibhyaaha \- bhoH kaanta | yatra jaahnavii navanadiishataani gR^ihiitvaa
nityameva pravishati tathaa sindhushca | tatkatha.n tvamaShTaadasha\-
nadiishataiH puuryamaaNa.n ta.n vipruShavaahinyaa ca~ncvaa
shoShayiShyasi | tatkimashraddheyenoktena | TiTTibha aaha \- priye |

anirvedaH shriyo muula.n ca~ncurme lohasa.nnibhaa |
ahoraatraaNi diirghaaNi samudraH ki.n na shuShyati || 359||
duradhigamaH parabhaago yaavatpuruSheNa pauruSha.n na kR^itam |
jayati tulaamadhiruuDho bhaasvaanapi jaladapaTalaani || 360||

TiTTibhyaaha \- yadi tvayaavashya.n samudreNa saha
vigrahaanuShThaana.n kaarya.n tadanyaanapi viha~Ngamaanaahuuya
suhR^ijjanasahita eva.n samaacara | ukta~nca \-

bahuunaamapyasaaraaNaa.n samavaayo hi durjayaH |
tR^iNairaaveShTyate rajjuryena naago.api baddhyate || 361||

tathaa ca \-

caTakaa kaaShThakuuTena makShikaa darduraistathaa |
mahaajanavirodhena ku~njaraH pralaya.n gataH || 362||

TiTTibha aaha \- kathametat | saa praaha \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 15
ku~njaracaTakadampatiikathaa |

kasmi.nshcidvanoddeshe caTakadampatii tamaalatarukR^itanilayau
prativasataH sma | atha tayorgacChataa kaalena santatirabhavat |
anyasminnahani pramatto vanagajaH kashcitta.n tamaalavR^ikSha.n
gharmaartashChaayaarthii samaashritaH | tato madotkarShaattaa.n tasya
shaakhaa.n caTakaashritaa.n puShkaraagreNaakR^iShya babha~nja | tasyaa
bha~Ngena caTakaaNDaani sarvaaNi vishiirNaani | aayuHsheShatayaa ca
caTakau kathamapi praaNairna viyuktau | atha caTakaa svaaNDabha~Ngaa\-
bhibhuutaa pralaapaankurvaaNaa na ki~ncitsukhamaasasaada |
atraantare tasyaastaanpralaapaanshrutvaa kaaShThakuuTo naama pakShii
tasyaaH paramasuhR^ittadduHkhaduHkhito.abhyetya taamuvaaca \-
bhagavati | ki.n vR^ithaa pralaapena | ukta~nca \-

naShTa.n mR^itamatikraanta.n naanushocanti paNDitaaH |
paNDitaanaa.n ca muurkhaaNaa.n visheSho.aya.n yataH smR^itaH || 363||

tathaa ca \-

ashocyaaniiha bhuutaani yo muuDhastaani shocati |
tadduHkhaallabhate duHkha.n dvaavanarthau niShevate || 364||

anyacca \-

shleShmaashru baandhavairmukta.n preto bhu~Nkte yato.avashaH |
tasmaanna roditavya.n hi kriyaaH kaaryaashca shaktitaH || 365||

caTakaa praaha \- astvetat | para.n duShTagajena madaanmama
santaanakShayaH kR^itaH | tadyadi mama tva.n suhR^itsatyastadasya
gajaapasadasya ko.api vadhopaayashcintyataam | yasyaanuShThaanena
me santatinaashaduHkhamapasarati | ukta~nca \-

aapadi yenopakR^ita.n yena ca hasita.n dashaasu viShamaasu |
apakR^itya tayorubhayoH punarapi jaata.n nara.n manye || 366||

kaaShThakuuTa aaha \- bhagavati satyamabhihita.n bhavatyaa |
ukta~nca \-

sa suhR^idvyasane yaH syaadanyajaatyudbhavo.api san |
vR^iddhau sarvo.api mitra.n syaatsarveShaameva dehinaam || 367||
sa suhR^idvyasane yaH syaatsa putro yastu bhaktimaan |
sa bhR^ityo yo vidheyadnyaH saa bhaaryaa yatra nirvR^itiH || 368||

tatpashya me buddhiprabhaavam | para.n mamaapi suhR^idbhuutaa
viiNaaravaa naama makShikaasti | tattaamaahuuyaagacChaami yena sa
duraatmaa duShTagajo vadhyate |athaasau caTakayaa saha
makShikaamaasaadya provaaca \-  bhadre mameShTeya.n caTakaa
kenacidduShTagajena paraabhuutaaNDasphoTanena | tattasya
vadhopaayamanutiShThato me saahaayya.n kartumarhasi |
makShikaapyaaha \- bhadra | kimucyate.atra viShaye | ukta~nca \-

punaH pratyupakaaraaya mitraaNaa.n kriyate priyam |
yatpunarmitramitrasya kaarya.n mitrairna ki.n kR^itam || 369||

satyametat | para.n mamaapi bheko meghanaado naama mitra.n
tiShThati | tamapyaahuuya yathocita.n kurmaH | ukta~nca \-

hitaiH saadhusamaacaaraiH shaastradnyairmatishaalibhiH |
katha~ncinna vikalpante vidvadbhishcintitaa nayaaH || 370||

atha te trayo.api gatvaa meghanaadasyaagre samasta.n vR^ittaanta.n
nivedya tasthuH | atha sa provaaca \-  kiyanmaatro.asau varaako gajo
mahaajanasya kupitasyaagre | tanmadiiyo mantraH kartavyaH | makShike
tva.n gatvaa madhyaahnasamaye tasya madoddhatasya gajasya karNe
viiNaaravasadR^isha.n shabda.n kuru | yena shravaNasukhalaalaso
nimiilitanayano bhavati | tatashca kaaShThakuuTaca~ncvaa
sphoTitanayano.andhiibhuutastR^iShaarto mama gartataTaashritasya
saparikarasya shabda.n shrutvaa jalaashaya.n matvaa samabhyeti | tato
gartamaasaadya patiShyati pa~ncatva.n yaasyati ceti | eva.n samavaayaH
kartavyo yathaa vairasaadhana.n bhavati | atha tathaanuShThite sa mattagajo
makShikaageyasukhaannimiilitanetraH kaaShThakuuTahR^itacakShu\-
rmadhyaahnasamaye bhraamyanmaNDuukashabdaanusaarii
gacChanmahatii.n gartaamaasaadya patito mR^itashca | ato.aha.n braviimi \-
caTakaa kaaShThakuuTeneti | TiTTibha aaha \- bhadre eva.n bhavatu |
suhR^idvargasamudaayena saha samudra.n shoShayiShyaami | iti nishcitya
bakasaarasamayuuraadiinsamaahuuya provaaca \-  bhoH paraabhuuto.aha.n
samudreNaaNDakaapahareNa | taccintyataamasya shoShaNopaayaH | te
sammantrya procuH \-  ashaktaa vaya.n samudrashoShaNe | tatki.n
vR^ithaa prayaasena | ukta~nca \-

abalaH pronnata.n shatru.n yo yaati madamohitaH |
yuddhaartha.n sa nivarteta shiirNadanto yathaa gajaH || 371||

tadasmaaka.n svaamii vainateyo.asti | tasmai sarvametatparibhavasthaana.n
nivedyataa.n yena svajaatiparibhavakupito vairaanR^iNya.n gacChati |
athavaatraavalepa.n kariShyati tathaapi naasti vo duHkham | ukta~nca \-

suhR^idi nirantararacite guNavati bhR^itye.anuvartini kalatre |
svaamini shaktisamete nivedya duHkha.n sukhii bhavati || 372||

tadyaamo vainateyasakaasha.n yato.asaavasmaaka.n svaamii |
tathaanuShThite sarve te pakShiNo viShaNNavadanaa baaShpapuuritadR^isho
vainateyasakaashamaasaadya karuNasvareNa phuutkartumaarabdhaaH \-
aho |  abrahmaNyamabrahmaNyam | adhunaa sadaacaarasya TiTTibhasya
bhavati naathe sati samudreNaaNDaanyapahR^itaani tatpranaShTamadhunaa
pakShikulam | anye.api svecChayaa samudreNa vyaapaadiShyante |
ukta~nca \-

kva kasya karma sa.nviikShya karotyanyo.api garhitam |
gataanugatiko loko na lokaH paaramaarthikaH || 373||
caaTutaskaradurvR^ittaistathaa saahasikaadibhiH |
piiDyamaanaaH prajaa rakShyaaH kuuTacChadmaadibhistathaa || 374||
prajaanaa.n dharmaShaDbhaago raadnyo bhavati rakShituH |
adharmaadapi ShaDbhaago jaayate yo na rakShati || 375||
prajaapiiDanasantaapaatsamudbhuuto hutaashanaH |
raadnyaH shriya.n kula.n praaNaannaadagdhvaa vinivartate || 376||
raajaa bandhurabandhuunaa.n raajaa cakShuracakShuShaam |
raajaa pitaa ca maataa ca sarveShaa.n nyaayavartinaam || 377||
phalaarthii paarthivo lokaanpaalayedyatnamaasthitaH |
daanamaanaaditoyena maalaakaaro.a~Nkuraaniva || 378||
yathaa biijaa~NkuraH suukShmaH prayatnenaabhirakShitaH |
phalaprado bhavetkaale tadvallokaH surakShitaH || 379||
hiraNyadhaanyaratnaani yaanaani vividhaani ca |
tathaanyadapi yatki~ncitprajaabhyaH syaannR^ipasya tat || 380||

athaiva.n garuDaH samaakarNya tadduHkhaduHkhitaH kopaaviShTashca
vyacintayat \-  aho | satyamuktametaiH pakShibhiH | tadadya gatvaa ta.n
samudra.n shoShayaamaH | eva.n cintayatastasya viShNuduutaH
samaagatyaaha \- bho garutman | bhagavataa naaraayaNenaaha.n tava
paarshve preShitaH | devakaaryaaya bhagavaanamaraavatyaa.n yaasyatiiti |
tatsatvaramaagamyataam| tacChrutvaa garuDaH saabhimaana.n praaha \-
bho duuta | ki.n mayaa kubhR^ityena bhagavaankariShyati | tadgatvaa
ta.n vada yadanyo bhR^ityo vaahanaayaasmatsthaane kriyataam |
madiiyo namaskaaro vaacyo bhagavataH | ukta~nca \-

yo na vetti guNaanyasya na ta.n seveta paNDitaH |
na hi tasmaatphala.n ki~ncitsukR^iShTaaduuSharaadiva || 381||

duuta aaha \- bho vainateya | kadaacidapi bhagavanta.n prati tvayaa
naitadabhihitamiidR^ik| tatkathaya ki.n te bhagavataapamaanasthaana.n
kR^itam | garuDa aaha \- bhagavadaashrayabhuutena
samudreNaasmaTTiTTibhaaNDaanyapahR^itaani | tadyadi nigraha.n na
karoti tadaha.n bhagavato na bhR^itya ityeSha nishcayastvayaa vaacyaH |
taddrutatara.n gatvaa bhavataa bhagavataH samiipe vaktavyam |atha
duutamukhena praNayakupita.n vainateya.n vidnyaaya
bhagavaa.nshcintayaamaasa aho sthaane kopo vainateyasya |
tatsvayameva gatvaa sammaanapuraHsara.n tamaanayaami|
ukta~nca \-

bhakta.n shakta.n kuliina.n ca na bhR^ityamavamaanayet |
putrava laalayennitya.n ya icChecChriyamaatmanaH || 382||

anyacca \-

raajaa tuShTo.api bhR^ityaanaamarthamaatra.n prayacChati |
te tu sammaanitaastasya praaNairapyupakurvate || 383||

ityeva.n sampradhaarya rukmapure vainateyasakaasha.n satvaramagamat |
vainateyo.api gR^ihaagata.n bhagavantamavalokya trapaadhomukhaH
praNamyovaaca \-  bhagavan | tvadaashrayonmattena samudreNa mama
bhR^ityaasyaaNDaanyapahR^itya mamaapamaano vihitaH | para.n
bhagavallajjayaa mayaa vilambitam | no cedenamaha.n sthalaantaramadyaiva
nayaami | yataH svaamibhayaacChuNo.api prahaaro na diiyate | ukta~nca \-

yena syaallaghutaa vaatha piiDaa citte prabhoH kvacit |
praaNatyaage.api tatkarma na kuryaatkulasevakaH || 384||

tacChrutvaa bhagavaanaaha \- bho vainateya | satyamabhihita.n bhavataa |
ukta~nca \-

bhR^ityaaparaadhajo daNDaH svaamino jaayate yataH |
tena lajjaapi tasyotthaa na bhR^ityasya tathaa punaH || 385||

tadaagacCha yenaaNDaani samudraadaadaaya TiTTibha.n
sambhaavayaavaH | amaraavatii.n ca gacChaavaH | tathaanuShThite
samudro bhagavataa nirbhartsyaagneya.n shara.n sandhyaayaabhihitaH \-
bho duraatman | diiyantaa.n TiTTibhaaNDaani | no cetsthalataa.n tvaa.n
nayaami | tataH samudreNa sabhayena TiTTibhaaNDaani taani pradattaani |
TiTTibhenaapi bhaaryaayai samarpitaani | ato.aha.n braviimi \-
shatrorbalamavidnyaaya iti | tasmaatpuruSheNodyamo na tyaajyaH |
tadaakarNya sa.njiivakastameva bhuuyo.api papracCha \-  bho mitra |
katha.n dnyeyo mayaa.asau duShTabuddhiriti | iyanta.n kaala.n
yaavaduttarottarasnehena prasaadena caaha.n dR^iShTaH | na
kadaacittadvikR^itirdR^iShTaa | tatkathyataa.n yenaahamaatmarakShaartha.n
tadvadhaayodyama.n karomi | damanaka aaha \- bhadra kimatra dnyeyam |
eSha te pratyayaH | yadi raktanetrastrishikhaa.n bhruukuTi.n dadhaanaH
sR^ikkiNii.n parilelihantvaa.n dR^iShTvaa bhavati tadduShTabuddhiH |
anyathaa suprasaadashceti | tadaadnyaapaya maam | svaashraya.n prati
gacChaami | tvayaa ca yathaaya.n mantrabhedo na bhavati tathaa kaaryam |
yadi nishaamukha.n praapya gantu.n shaknoShi taddeshatyaagaH
kaaryaH | yataH \-

tyajedeka.n kulasyaarthe graamasyaarthe kula.n tyajet |
graama.n janapadasyaarthe svaatmaarthe pR^ithivii.n tyajet || 386||
aapadarthe dhana.n rakSheddaaraanrakSheddhanairapi |
aatmaana.n satata.n rakSheddaarairapi dhanairapi || 387||

balavataabhibhuutasya videshagamana.n tadanupravesho vaa niitiH |
taddeshatyaagaH kaaryaH| athavaatmaa saamaadibhirupaayai\-
rabhirakShaNiiyaH | ukta~nca \-

api putrakalatrairvaa praaNaanrakSheta paNDitaH |
vidyamaanairyatastaiH syaatsarva.n bhuuyo.api dehinaam || 388||

tathaa ca \-

yena kenaapyupaayena shubhenaapyashubhena vaa |
uddhareddiinamaatmaana.n samartho dharmamaacaret || 389||
yo maayaa.n kurute muuDhaH praaNatyaage dhanaadiShu |
tasya praaNaaH praNashyanti tairnaShTairnaShTameva tat || 390||

evamabhidhaaya damanakaH karaTakasakaashamagamat | karaTako.api
tamaayaanta.n dR^iShTvaa provaaca \-  bhadra | ki.n kR^ita.n tatrabhavataa |
damanaka aaha \- mayaa taavanniitibiijanirvaapaNa.n kR^itam | parato
daivavihitaayattam | ukta~nca \-

paraa~Nmukhe.api daive.atra kR^itya.n kaarya.n vipashcitaa |
aatmadoShavinaashaaya svacittastambhanaaya ca || 391||

tathaa ca \-

udyogina.n puruShasi.nhamupaiti lakShmii \-
rdaiva.n hi daivamiti kaapuruShaa vadanti |
daiva.n nihatya kuru pauruShamaatmashaktyaa |
yatne kR^ite yadi na sidhyati ko.atra doShaH || 392||

karaTaka aaha \- tatkathaya kiidR^iktvayaa niitibiija.n nirvaapitam |
so.abraviit \-
mayaa.anyonya.n taabhyaa.n mithyaaprajalpena bhedastathaa vihito yathaa
bhuuyo.api mantrayantaavekasthaanasthitau na drakShyasi | karaTaka aaha \-
aho na yukta.n bhavataa vihita.n yatparaspara.n tau snehaardrahR^idayau
sukhaashrayau kopasaagare prakShiptau | ukta~nca \-

aviruddha.n sukhastha.n yo duHkhamaarge niyojayet |
janmajanmaantara.n duHkhii sa naraH syaadasa.nshayam || 393||

apara.n tva.n yadbhedamaatreNaapi tuShTastadapyayukta.n yataH
sarvato.api jano viruupakaraNe samartho bhavati nopakartum |
ukta~nca \-

ghaatayitumeva niicaH parakaarya.n vetti na prasaadayitum |
paatayitumasti shaktirvaayorvR^ikSha.n na connamitum || 394||

damanaka aaha \- anabhidnyo bhavaanniitishaastrasya tenaitadbraviiti |
ukta~nca yataH \-

jaatamaatra.n na yaH shatru.n vyaadhi.n ca prashama.n nayet |
mahaabalo.api tenaiva vR^iddhi.n praapya sa hanyate || 395||

tacChatrubhuuto.ayamasmaaka.n mantripadaaharaNaat | ukta~nca \-

pitR^ipaitaamaha.n sthaana.n yo yasyaatra jigiiShate |
sa tasya sahajaH shatrurucChedyo.api priye sthitaH || 396||

tanmayaa sa udaasiinatayaa samaaniito.abhayapradaanena
yaavattaavadahamapi tena saacivyaatpracyaavitaH |
athavaa saadhvidamucyate \-

dadyaatsaadhuryadi nijapade durjanaaya pravesham
tannaashaaya prabhavati tato vaa~nChamaanaH svaya.n saH |
tasmaaddeyo vipulamatibhirnaavakaasho.adhamaanaam |
jaaraapi syaadgR^ihapatiriti shruuyate vaakyato.atra || 397||

tena mayaa tasyopari vadhopaaya eva viracyate | deshatyaagaaya vaa
bhaviShyati | tacca tvaa.n muktvaa.anyo na dnyaasyati | taduktametatte
svaarthaayaanuShThitam | ukta~nca \-

nistri.nsha.n hR^idaya.n kR^itvaa vaaNii.n kShurasamopamaam |
vikalpo.atra na kartavyo hanyaattatraapakaariNam || 398||

apara.n mR^ito.apyasmaaka.n bhojyo bhaviShyati | tadeka.n
taavadvarasaadhanam | apara.n saacivya.n ca bhaviShyati tR^iptishceti |
tadguNatraye.asminnupasthite kasmaanmaa.n duuShayasi tva.n
jaaDyabhaavaat | ukta~nca \-

parasya piiDana.n kurvansvaarthasiddhi.n ca paNDitaH |
muuDhabuddhirna bhakSheta vane caturako yathaa || 399||

karaTaka aaha \- kathametat | sa aaha \-

