kathaa 16
vajrada.nShTranaamasi.nhakathaa |

asti kasmi.nshcidvanoddeshe vajrada.nShTro naama si.nhaH | tasya
caturakakravyamukhanaamaanau shR^igaalavR^ikau bhR^ityabhuutau
sadaivaanugatau tatraiva vane prativasataH | athaanyadine si.nhena
kadaacidaasannaprasavaa prasavavedanayaa svayuuthaadbhraShToShTryupaviShTaa
kasmi.nshcidvanagahane samaasaaditaa | atha taa.n vyaapaadya yaavadudara.n
sphoTayati taavajjiivallaghudaaserakashishurniShkraantaH | si.nho.api
daaserakyaaH pishitena saparivaaraH paraa.n tR^iptimupaagataH | para.n
snehaadbaaladaaseraka.n tyakta.n gR^ihamaaniiyedamuvaaca \-  bhadra
na te.asti mR^ityorbhaya.n matto naanyasmaadapi | tataH svecChayaa.atra
vane bhraamyataamiti | yataste sha~NkusadR^ishau karNau tataH
sha~NkukarNo naama bhaviShyati | evamanuShThite catvaaro.api ta
ekasthaane vihaariNaH parasparamanekaprakaaragoShThiisukha\-
manubhavantastiShThanti | sha~NkukarNo.api yauvanapadaviimaaruuDhaH
kShaNamapi na ta.n si.nha.n mu~ncati | atha kadaacidvajrada.nShTrasya
kenacidvanyena mattagajena saha yuddhamabhavat | tena madaviiryaatsa
dantaprahaaraistathaa kShatashariiro vihito yathaa pracalitu.n na shaknoti |
tadaa kShutkShaamakaNThastaanprovaaca \-  bhoH | anviShyataa.n
ki~ncitsattva.n yenaahameva.nsthito.api ta.n vyaapaadyaa.atmano
yuShmaaka.n ca kShutpraNaasha.n karomi | tacChrutvaa te trayo.api vane
sandhyaakaala.n yaavadbhraantaaH para.n na ki~ncitsattvamaasaaditam|
atha caturakashcintayaamaasa \-  yadi sha~NkukarNo.aya.n vyaapaadyeta
tataH sarveShaa.n katiciddinaani tR^iptirbhavati | para.n naina.n svaamii
mitratvaadaashrayasamaashritatvaacca vinaashayiShyati | athavaa
buddhiprabhaaveNa svaamina.n pratibodhya tathaa kariShye yathaa
vyaapaadayiShyati | ukta~nca \-

avadhya.n caathavaagamyamakR^itya.n naasti ki~ncana |
loke buddhimataa.n  buddhestasmaattaa.n viniyojayet|| 400||
eva.n vicintya sha~NkukarNamidamaaha \- bhoH sha~NkukarNa | svaamii
taavatpathya.n vinaa kShudhayaa paripiiDyate | svaamyabhaavaadasmaaka\-
mapi dhruva.n vinaasha eva | tato vaakya.n ki~ncitsvaamyarthe vadiShyaami |
tacChruuyataam | sha~NkukarNa aaha \- bhoH shiighra.n nivedyataa.n  yena
te vacana.n shiighra.n nirvikalpa.n karomi | apara.n svaamino hite kR^ite
mayaa sukR^itashata.n kR^ita.n bhaviShyati | atha caturaka aaha \- bho
bhadra | aatmashariira.n dviguNalaabhena svaamine prayacCha yena te
dviguNa.n shariira.n bhavati | svaaminaH punaH praaNayaatraa bhavati |
tadaakarNya sha~NkukarNaH praaha \- bhadra | yadyeva.n tanmadiiya\-
prayojanametaducyataa.n svaamyarthaH kriyataamiti | paramatra dharmaH
pratibhuuriti | te vicintya sarve si.nhasakaashamaajagmuH | tatashcaturaka
aaha \- deva | na ki~ncitsattva.n praaptam | 
bhagavaanaadityo.apyasta.n gataH |
tadyadi svaamii dviguNa.n shariira.n prayacChati tataH sha~NkukarNo.aya.n
dviguNavR^iddhyaa svashariira.n prayacChati dharmapratibhuvaa | si.nha
aaha \- bhoH yadyeva.n tatsundarataram | vyavahaarasyaasya dharmaH
pratibhuuH kriyataamiti |atha si.nhavacanaanantara.n vR^ikashR^igaa\-
laabhyaa.n vidaaritobhayakukShiH sha~NkukarNaH pa~ncatvamupaagataH |
atha vajrada.nShTrashcaturakamaaha \- bhoshcaturaka | yaavadaha.n nadii.n
gatvaa snaana.n devataarcanavidhi.n kR^itvaa.a.agacChaami taavattvayaa
.atraapramattena bhaavyamityuktvaa nadyaa.n gataH | atha tasmingate
caturakashcintayaamaasa \-  katha.n mamaikaakino bhojyo.ayamuShTro
bhaviShyati iti vicintya kravyamukhamaaha \- bhoH kravyamukha |
kShudhaalurbhavaan | tadyaavadasau svaamii naagacChati taavattvamasyo\-
ShTrasya maa.nsa.n bhakShaya | aha.n tvaa.n svaamino nirdoSha.n
pratipaadayiShyaami | so.api tacChrutvaa yaavatki~ncinmaa.nsamaasvaa\-
dayati taavaccaturakeNoktam \-  bhoH kravyamukha | samaagacChati
svaamii | tattyaktvaina.n duure tiShTha yenaasya bhakShaNa.n na
vikalpayati | tathaanuShThite si.nhaH samaayaato yaavaduShTra.n pashyati
taavadriktiikR^itahR^idayo daaserakaH | tato bhR^ikuTi.n kR^itvaa
paruShataramaaha \- aho kenaiSha uShTra ucChiShTataa.n niito yena
tamapi vyaapaadayaami | evamabhihite kravyamukhashcaturakamukha\-
mavalokayati | atha caturako vihasyovaaca \-  bhoH | maamanaadR^itya
pishita.n bhakShayitvaa.adhunaa manmukhamavalokayasi |
tadaasvaadayaasya durNayataroH phalamiti | tadaakarNya kravyamukho
jiivanaashabhayaadduuradesha.n gataH | etasminnantare tena maargeNa
daaserakasaartho bhaaraakraantaH samaayaataH | tasyaagresaroShTrasya
kaNThe mahatii ghaNTaa baddhaa | tasyaaH shabda.n duurato.apyaakarNya
si.nho jambukamaaha \- bhadra dnyaayataa.n kimeSha raudraH shabdaH
shruuyate.ashrutapuurvaH |  tacChrutvaa caturakaH ki~ncidvanaantara.n
gatvaa satvaramabhyupetya provaaca \-  svaamin | gamyataa.n gamyataa.n
yadi shaknoShi gantum | so.abraviit \- bhadra kimeva.n maa.n vyaakulayasi |
tatkathaya kimetaditi | caturaka aaha \- svaamin eSha dharmaraajastavopari
kupitao yadanenaakaale daaserako.aya.n madiiyo vyaapaaditaH |
tatsahasraguNamuShTramasya sakaashaadgrahiiShyaami | iti nishcitya
bR^ihanmaanamaadaayaagresarasyoShTrasya griivaayaa.n ghaNTaa.n
baddhvaa badhyadaaserakasaktaanapi pitR^ipitaamahaanaadaaya
vairaniryaatanaarthamaayaata eva | si.nho.api tacChrutvaa sarvato
duuraadevaavalokya mR^itamuShTra.n parityajya praaNabhayaatpraNaShTaH |
caturako.api shanaiH shanaistasyoShTrasya maa.nsa.n bhakShayaamaasa |
ato.aha.n braviimi \-  parasya piiDana.n kurvanniti | atha damanake gate
sa.njiivakashcintayaamaasa \-  aho kimetanmayaa kR^itam |
yacChaShpaado.api maa.nsaashitastasyaanugaH sa.nvR^ittaH |
athavaa saadhvidamucyate \-

agamyaanyaH pumaanyaati yo.asevyaa.nshca niShevate |
sa mR^ityumupagRihNaati garbhamashvatarii yathaa || 401||

tatki.n karomi | kva gacChaami | katha.n me shaantirbhaviShyati |
athavaa tameva pi~Ngalaka.n gacChaami | kadaacinmaa.n sharaNaagata.n
rakShati | praaNairna viyojayati | yata ukta~nca \-

dharmaartha.nyatataamapiiha vipado devaadyadi syuH kvacit |
tattaasaamupashaantaye sumatibhiH kaaryo visheShaannayaH |
loke khyaatimupaagataa.atra sakale lokoktireShaa yataH |
dagdhaanaa.n kila vahninaa hitakaraH seko.api tasyodbhavaH || 402||

tathaa ca \-

loke.athavaa tanubhR^itaa.n nijakarmapaaka.n
nitya.n samaashritavataa.n suhitakriyaaNaam |
bhaavaarjita.n shubhamathaapyashubha.n nikaama.n
yadbhaavi tadbhavati naatra vicaarahetuH || 403||

apara.n caanyatra gatasyaapi me kasyacidduShTasattvasya maa.nsaashinaH
sakaashaanmR^ityurbhaviShyati | tadvara.n si.nhaat | ukta~nca \-

mahadbhiH spardhamaanasya vipadeva gariiyasii |
dantabha~Ngo.api naagaanaa.n shlaaghyo girividaaraNe || 404||

tathaa ca \-

mahato.api kShaya.n labdhvaa shlaaghya.n niico.api gacChati |
daanaarthii madhupo yadvadgajakarNasamaahataH || 405||

eva.n nishcitya sa sthalitagatirmanda.n gatvaa si.nhaashraya.n
pashyannapaThat \-  aho saadhvidamucyate \-

antarliinabhuja~Ngama.n gR^ihamivaantaHsthograsi.nha.n vanam |
graahaakiirNamivaabhiraamakamalacChaayaasanaatha.n saraH |
kaalenaaryajanaapavaadapishunaiH kShudrairanaaryaiH shritam |
duHkhena pravigaahyate sacakita.n raadnyaa.n manaH saamayam || 406||

eva.n paThandamanakoktaakaara.n pi~Ngalaka.n dR^iShTvaa pracakitaH
sa.nvR^itashariiro duuratara.n praNaamakR^iti.n vinaapyupaviShTaH |
pi~Ngalako.api tathaavidha.n ta.n vilokya damanakavaakya.n
shraddadhaanaH kopaattasyopari papaata | atha sa.njiivakaH
kharanakhavikartitapR^iShThaH shR^i~Ngaabhyaa.n tadudaramullikhya
kathamapi tasmaadapetaH shR^i~Ngaabhyaa.n hantumicChanyuddhaa\-
yaavasthitaH | atha dvaavapi tau puShpitapalaashapratimau parasparavadha\-
kaa~NkShiNau dR^iShTvaa karaTako damanakamaaha \- bho muuDhamate |
anayorvirodha.n vitanvataa tvayaa saadhu na kR^itam | na ca tva.n 
niititattva.n
vetsi | niitividbhirukta~nca \-

kaaryaaNyuttamadaNDasaahasaphalaanyaayaasasaadhyaani ye |
priityaa sa.nshamayanti niitikushalaaH saamnaiva te mantriNaH |
niHsaaraalpaphalaani ye tvavidhinaa vaa~nChanti daNDodyamaiH |
teShaa.n durNayaceShTitairnarapateraaropyate shriistulaam || 407||

tadyadi svaamyabhighaato bhaviShyati tatki.n tvadiiyamantrabuddhyaa
kriyate | atha sa.njiivako na badhyate tathaapyabhavyam | yataH
praaNasa.ndehaattasya ca vadhaH | tanmuuDha | katha.n tva.n
mantripadamabhilaShasi | saamasiddhi.n na vetsi | tadvR^ithaa
manoratho.aya.n te daNDaruceH | ukta~nca \-

saamaadidaNDaparyanto nayaH proktaH svayambhuvaa |
teShaa.n daNDastu paapiiyaa.nsta.n pashcaadviniyojayet || 408||

tathaa ca \-

saamnaiva yatra siddhirna tatra daNDo budhena viniyojyaH |
pitta.n yadi sharkarayaa shaamyati ko.arthaH paTolena || 409||

tathaa ca \-

aadau saama prayoktavya.n puruSheNa vijaanataa |
saamasaadhyaani kaaryaaNi vikriyaa.n yaanti na kvacit || 410||
na candreNa na cauShadhyaa na suuryeNa na vahninaa |
saamnaiva vilaya.nyaati vidveShaprabhava.n tamaH || 411||

tathaa yattva.n mantritvamabhilaShasi tadapyayuktam | yatastva.n
mantrigati.n na vetsi | yataH pa~ncavidho mantraH | sa ca
karmaNaamaarambhopaayaH puruShadravyasampaddeshakaalavibhaago
vinipaatapratiikaaraH kaaryasiddhishceti | so.aya.n svaamyamaatyayo\-
rekatamasya ki.n vaa dvayorapi vinipaataH samutpadyate lagnaH | tadyadi
kaacicChaktirasti tadvicintyataa.n vinipaatapratiikaaraH | bhinnasandhaane hi
mantriNaa.n buddhipariikShaa | tanmuurkha | tatkartumasamarthastva.n
yato vipariitabuddhirasi | ukta~nca \-

mantriNaa.n bhinnasandhaane bhiShajaa.n saa.nnipaatike |
karmaNi vyajyate pradnyaa susthe ko vaa na paNDitaH || 412||

anyacca \-

ghaatayitumeva niicaH parakaarya.n vetti na prasaadhayitum |
paatayitumeva shaktirnaakhoruddhartumannapiTam || 413||

athavaa na te doSho.ayam | svaamino doShaH yaste vaakya.n
shraddadhaati | ukta~nca \-

naraadhipaa niicajanaanuvartino budhopadiShTena pathaa na yaanti ye |
vishantyato durgamamaarganirgama.n samastasambaadhamanarthapa~njaram || 414||

tadyadi tvamasya mantrii bhaviShyasi tadaanyo.api kashcinnaasya samiipe
saadhujanaH sameShyati | ukta~nca \-

guNaalayo.apyasanmantrii nR^ipatirnaadhigamyate |
prasannasvaadusalilo duShTagraahyo yathaa hradaH || 415||

tathaa ca shiShTajanarahitasya svaamino.api naasho bhaviShyati |
ukta~nca \-

citraasvaadakathairbhR^ityairanaayaasitakaarmukaiH |
ye ramante nR^ipaasteShaa.n ramante ripavaH shriyaa || 416||

tatki.n muurkhopadeshena | kevala.n doSho na guNaH | ukta~nca \-

naanaamya.n namate daaru naashmani syaatkShurakriyaa |
suuciimukha.n vijaaniihi naashiShyaayopashyate || 417||

damanaka aaha kathametat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 17
vaanarayuuthakathaa |

asti kasmi.nshcitparvataikadeshe vaanarayuutham | tacca kadaaciddhemanta\-
samaye.atikaThoravaatasa.nsparshavepamaanakalevara.n tuShaaravarSho\-
ddhatapravarShaghanadhaaraanipaatasamaahata.n na katha~ncicChaanti\-
magamat | atha kecidvaanaraa vahnikaNasadR^ishaani gu~njaaphalaa\-
nyavacitya vahnivaa~nChayaa phuutkurvantaH samantaattasthuH | atha
suuciimukho naama pakShii teShaa.n ta.n vR^ithaayaasamavalokya
provaaca \-  bhoH sarve muurkhaa yuuyam | naite vahnikaNaaH
gu~njaaphalaani etaani | tatki.n vR^ithaa shrameNa | naitasmaacChiitarakShaa
bhaviShyati | tadanviShyataa.n kashcinnirvaato vanapradesho guhaa
girikandara.n vaa | adyaapi saTopaa medhaa dR^ishyante | atha
teShaamekatamo vR^iddhavaanarastamuvaaca \-  bho muurkha | ki.n
taavadanena vyaapaareNa | tadgamyataam | ukta~nca \-

muhurvighnitakarmaaNa.n dyuutakaara.n paraajitam |
naalaapayedvivekadnyo yadiicChetsiddhimaatmanaH || 418||

tathaa ca \-

aakheTaka.n vR^ithaaklesha.n muurkha.n vyasanasa.nsthitam |
samaalaapena yo yu~Nkte sa gacChati paraabhavam || 419||

so.api tamanaadR^itya bhuuyo.api vaanaraananavaratamaaha \- bhoH | ki.n
vR^ithaa kleshena | atha yaavadasau na katha~ncitpralapanviramati
taavadekena vaanareNa vyarthashramatvaatkupitena pakShaabhyaa.n
gR^ihiitvaa shilaayaamaasphaalita uparatashca | ato.aha.n braviimi \-
naanamya.n namate daaru ityaadi | tathaa ca \-

upadesho hi muurkhaaNaa.n prakopaaya na shaantaye |
payaHpaana.n bhuja~Ngaanaa.n kevala.n viShavardhanam || 420||

anyacca \-
upadesho na daatavyo yaadR^ishe taadR^ishe nare |
pashya vaanaramuurkheNa sugR^ihii nirgR^ihiikR^itaa || 421||

damanaka aaha \- kathametat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 18

kasmi.nshcidvanoddeshe shamiivR^ikShaH | tasya lambamaanashaakhaayaa.n
kR^itaavaasaavaraNyacaTakadampatii prativasataH sma | atha kadaacittayoH
sukhasa.nsthayorhemantamegho manda.n manda.n varShitumaarabdhaH |
atraantare kashcicChaakhaamR^igo vaataasaarasamaahataH proddhuuShita\-
shariiro dantaviiNaa.n vaadayanvepamaanastasyaaH shamyaa
muulamaasaadyopaviShTaH | atha ta.n taadR^iShamavalokya caTakaa
praaha \- bho bhadra |

hastapaadasamopeto dR^ishyase puruShaakR^itiH |
shiitena bhidyase muuDha katha.n na kuruShe gR^iham || 422||

etacChrutvaa taa.n vaanaraH sakopamaaha \- adhame kasmaanna tva.n
maunavrataa bhavasi | aho dhaarShTyamasyaaH | adya maamupahasati \-

suuciimukhii duraacaaraa raNDaa paNDitavaadinii |
naasha~Nkate prajalpantii tatkimenaa.n na hanmyaham || 423||

eva.n pralapya taamaaha \- mugdhe | ki.n mama cintayaa tava prayojanam |
ukta~nca \-

vaacya.n shraddhaasametasya pR^icChatashca visheShataH |
prokta.n shraddhaavihiinasya araNyaruditopamam || 424||

tatki.n bahunaa taavat | kulaayasthitayaa tayaa punarapyabhihitaH |
sa taavattaa.n shamiimaaruhya tasyaaH kulaaya.n shatadhaa
khaNDasho.akarot | ato.aha.n braviimi \-  upadesho na daatavya iti |
tanmuurkha | shikShaapito.api na shikShitastvam | athavaa na te
doSho.asti yataH saadhoH shikShaa guNaaya sampadyate
naasaadhoH | ukta~nca \-

ki.n karotyeva paaNDityamasthaane viniyojitam |
andhakaarapraticChanne ghaTe diipa ivaahitaH || 425||

tadvyarthapaaNDityamaashritya mama vacanamashR^iNvannaatmanaH
shaantimapi vetsi tannuunamapajaatastvam | ukta~nca \-

jaataH putro.anujaatashca atijaatastathaiva ca |
apajaatashca loke.asminmantavyaaH shaastravedibhiH || 426||
maatR^itulyaguNo jaatastvanujaataH pituH samaH |
atijaato.adhikastasmaadapajaato.adhamaadhamaH || 427||
apyaatmano vinaasha.n gaNayati na khalaH paravyasanahR^iShTaH |
praayo mastakanaashe samaramukhe nR^ityati kabandhaH || 428||

aho saadhvidamucyate \-

dharmabuddhiH kubuddhishca dvaavetau viditau mama |
putreNa vyarthapaaNDityaatpitaa dhuumena ghaatitaH || 429||

damanaka aaha kathametat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 20

kasmi.nshciddeshe dharmabuddhiH paapabuddhishca dve mitre prativasataH |
atha kadaacitpaapabuddhinaa cintita.n yadaha.n taavanmuurkho
daaridryopetashca | tadena.n dharmabuddhimaadaaya deshaantara.n
gatvaa.asyaashrayeNaarthopaarjanaa.n kR^itvainamapi va~ncayitvaa
sukhiibhavaami | athaanyasminnahani paapabuddhirdharmabuddhi.n praaha \-
bho mitra | vaardhakabhaave ki.n tvaatmaviceShTita.n smarasi |
deshaantaramadR^iShTvaa kaa.n shiShTajanasya vaarttaa.n
kathayiShyasi | ukta~nca \-

deshaantareShu bahuvidhabhaaShaaveShaadi yena na dnyaatam |
bhramataa dharaNiipiiThe tasya phala.n janmano vyartham || 430||

tathaa ca \-

vidyaa.n vitta.n shilpa.n taavannaapnoti maanavaH samyak |
yaavadvrajati na bhuumau deshaaddeshaantara.n hR^iShTaH || 431||

atha tasya tadvacanamaakarNya prahR^iShTamanaastenaiva saha
gurujanaanudnyaataH shubhe.ahani deshaantara.n prasthitaH | tatra
ca dharmabuddhiprabhaaveNa bhramataa paapabuddhinaa prabhuutatara.n
vittamaasaaditam | tatashca tau dvaavapi prabhuutopaarjitadravyau
prahR^iShTau svagR^iha.n pratyautsukyena prasthitau | ukta~nca \-

praaptavidyaarthashilpaanaa.n deshaantaranivaasinaam |
kroshamaatro.api bhuubhaagaH shatayojanavadbhavet || 432||

atha svasthaanasamiipavartinaa paapabuddhinaa dharmabuddhirabhihitaH \-
bhadra | na sarvametaddhana.n gR^iha.n prati netu.n yujyate | yataH
kuTumbino baandhavaashca praarthayiShyante | tadatraiva vanagahane
kvaapi bhuumau nikShipya ki~ncinmaatramaadaaya gR^iha.n pravishaavaH |
bhuuyo.api prayojane sa~njaate tanmaatra.n sametyaasmaat\-
sthaanaanneShyaavaH | ukta~nca \-

na vitta.n darshayetpraadnyaH kasyacitsvalpamapyaho |
munerapi yatastasya darshanaaccalate manaH || 433||

tathaa ca \-

yathaamiSha.n jale matsyairbhakShyate shvaapadairbhuvi |
aakaashe pakShibhishcaiva tathaa sarvatra vittavaan || 434||

tadaakarNya dharmabuddhiraaha \- bhadra eva.n kriyataam | tathaanuShThite
dvaavapi tau svagR^iha.n gatvaa sukhena sa.n sthitavantau |
athaanyasminnahani paapabuddhirnishiithe.aTavyaa.n gatvaa tatsarva.n vitta.n
samaadaaya garta.n puurayitvaa svabhavana.n jagaama | athaanyedyu\-
rdharmabuddhi.n sametya provaaca \-  sakhe bahukuTumbaa vaya.n
vittaabhaavaatsiidaamaH | tadgatvaa tatra sthaane ki~ncinmaatra.n
dhanamaanayaavaH | so.abraviit \- bhadra eva.n kriyataam | atha dvaavapi
gatvaa tatsthaana.n yaavatkhanatastaavadrikta.n bhaaNDa.n dR^iShTavantau |
atraantare paapabuddhiH shirastaaDayanprovaaca \-  bho dharmabuddhe |
tvayaa hR^itametaddhana.n  naanyena | yato bhuuyo.api gartaapuuraNa.n
kR^itam | tatprayacCha me tasyaardham | anyathaa.aha.n raajakule
nivedayiShyaami | sa aaha \- bho duraatman | maa maiva.n vada |
dharmabuddhiH khalvaham | naitaccaurakarma karomi | ukta~nca \-

maatR^ivatparadaaraaNi paradravyaaNi loShTavat |
aatmavatsarvabhuutaani viikShante dharmabuddhayaH || 435||

eva.n dvaavapi vivadamaanau dharmaadhikaariNa.n gatau | procatushca
paraspara.n duuShayantau | atha dharmaadhikaraNaadhiShThitapuruShai\-
rdivyaarthe yaavanniyojitau taavatpaapabuddhiraaha \- aho na
samyagdR^iShTo nyaayaH | ukta~nca \-

vivaade.anviShyate patra.n tadabhaave.api saakShiNaH |
saakShyabhaavaattato divya.n pravadanti maniiShiNaH || 436||

tadatra viShaye mama vR^ikShadevataaH saakShiibhuutaastiShThanti |
taa apyaavayorekatara.n caura.n saadhu.n vaa kariShyanti | atha taiH
sarvairabhihitam \-  bho yuktamukta.n bhavataa | ukta~nca \-

antyajo.api yadaa saakShii vivaade samprajaayate |
na tatra yujyate divya.n ki.n punarvanadevataaH || 437||

tadasmaakamapyatra viShaye mahatkautuuhala.n vartate | pratyuuShasamaye
yuvaabhyaamapyasmaabhiH saha tatra vanoddeshe gantavyamiti |
etasminnantare paapabuddhiH svagR^iha.n gatvaa svajanakamuvaaca \-
taata prabhuuto.aya.n mayaartho dharmabuddheshcoritaH | sa ca tava
vacanena pariNati.n gacChati | anyathaa.asmaaka.n praaNaiH saha yaasyati |
sa aaha \- vatsa druta.n vada yena procya taddravya.n sthirataa.n nayaami |
paapabuddhiraaha \- taata asti tatpradeshe mahaashamii | tasyaa.n
mahatkoTaramasti | tatra tva.n saa.npratameva pravisha | tataH prabhaate
yadaaha.n satyashraavaNa.n karomi tadaa tvayaa vaacya.n
yaddharmabuddhishcaura iti | tathaanuShThite pratyuuShe snaatvaa
paapabuddhiH dharmabuddhipuraHsaro dharmaadhikaraNakaiH saha taa.n
shamiimabhyetya taarasvareNa provaaca |

aadityacandraavanilo.analashca
           dyaurbhuumiraapo hR^idaya.n yamashca |
ahashca raatrishca ubhe ca sandhye
           dharmo hi jaanaati narasya vR^ittam || 438||

bhagavati vanadevate | aavayormadhye yashcaurasta.n kathaya | atha
paapabuddhipitaa shamiikoTarasthaH provaaca \-  bho dharmabuddhinaa
hR^itametaddhanam| tadaakarNya sarve te raajapuruShaa
vismayotphullalocanaa yaavaddharmabuddhervittaharaNocita.n nigraha.n
shaastradR^iShTyaavalokayanti taavaddharmabuddhinaa tacChamiikoTara.n
vahnibhojyadravyaiH pariveShTya vahninaa sandiipitam | atha jvalati
tasminshamiikoTare.ardhadagdhashariiraH sphuTitekShaNaH karuNa.n
paridevayanpaapabuddhipitaa nishcakraama | tatashca taiH sarvaiH pR^iShTaH \-
bhoH kimidam | ityukta ida.n sarva.n kukR^itya.n paapabuddheH
kaaraNaajjaatamityuktvaa mR^itaH | tataste raajapuruShaaH paapabuddhi.n
shamiishaakhaayaa.n pratilambya dharmabuddhi.n prashasyedamuucuH \-
aho saadhvidamucyate \-

upaaya.n cintayetpraadnyastathaapaaya.n ca cintayet |
pashyato bakamuurkhasya nakulairbhakShitaaH sutaaH || 439||

dharmabuddhiH praaha \- kathametat | te procuH \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 21
kR^iShNasarpakathaa |

asti kasmi.nshcidvanoddeshe bahubakasanaatho vaTapaadapaH | tasya
koTare kR^iShNasarpaH prativasati sma | sa ca bakabaalakaanajaata\-
pakShaanapi sadaiva bhakShayankaala.n nayati | athaiko bakastena
bhakShitaanyapatyaani dR^iShTvaa shishuvairaagyaatsarastiiramaasaadya
baaShpapuurapuuritanayano.adhomukhastiShThati | ta.n ca taadR^ikceShTita\-
mavalokya kuliirakaH provaaca \-  maama kimeva.n rudyate bhavataa.adya |
sa aaha \- bhadra ki.n karomi | mama mandabhaagyasya baalakaaH
koTaranivaasinaa sarpeNa bhakShitaaH | tadduHkhaduHkhito.aha.n
rodimi | tatkathaya me yadyasti kashcidupaayastadvinaashaaya |
tadaakarNya kuliirakashcintayaamaasa \-  aya.n taavadasmatsahajavairii |
tathopadesha.n prayacChaami satyaanR^ita.n yathaanye.api bakaaH
sarve sa~NkShayamaayaanti | ukta~nca \-

navaniitasamaa.n vaaNii.n kR^itvaa citta.n tu nirdayam |
tathaa prabodhyate shatruH saanvayo mriyate yathaa || 440||

aaha ca \-  maama yadyeva.n tanmatsyamaa.nsakhaNDaani nakulasya
biladvaaraatsarpakoTara.n yaavatprakShipa yathaa nakulastanmaargeNa
gatvaa ta.n duShTasarpa.n vinaashayati | atha tathaanuShThite
matsyamaa.nsaanusaariNaa nakulena ta.n kR^iShNasarpa.n nihatya te.api
tadvR^ikShaashrayaaH sarve bakaashca shanaiH shanairbhakShitaaH | ato
vaya.n bruumaH \-  upaaya.n cintayediti |  eva.n muuDha | tvayaapyupaaya\-
shcintito naapaayaH paapabuddhivat | tanna bhavasi tva.n sajjanaH| kevala.n
paapabuddhirasi | dnyaato mayaa svaaminaH praaNasa.ndehaanayanaat |
prakaTiikR^ita.n tvayaa svayamevaatmano duShTatva.n kauTilya.n ca |
athavaa saadhvidamucyate \-

yatnaadapi kaH pashyecChikhinaamaahaaraniHsaraNamaargam |
yadi jaladadhvanimuditaasta eva muuDhaa na nR^ityeyuH || 441||

yadi tva.n svaaminamenaa.n dashaa.n nayasi tadasmadvidhasya kaa
gaNanaa | tasmaanmamaasannena bhavataa na bhaavyam | ukta~nca \-

tulaa.n lohasahasrasya yatra khaadanti muuShakaaH |
raaja.nstatra harecChyeno baalaka.n naatra sa.nshayaH || 442||

damanaka aaha kathametat |so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 22
jiirNadhananaamavaNikputrakathaa |

asti kasmi.nshcidadhiShThaane jiirNadhano naama vaNikputraH | sa ca
dravyakShayaaddeshaantaragamanamanaa vyacintayat \-

yatra deshe.athavaa sthaane bhogaanbhuktvaa svaviiryataH |
tasminvibhavahiino yo vasetsa puruShaadhamaH || 443||

tathaa ca \-

yenaaha.nkaarayuktena cira.n vilasita.n puraa |
diina.n vadati tatraiva yaH pareShaa.n sa ninditaH || 444||

tasya ca gR^ihe sahasralohabhaaraghaTitaa puurvapuruShopaarjitaa
tulaa.asiit | taa.n ca kasyacicChreShTino gR^ihe nikShepabhuutaa.n
kR^itvaa deshaantara.n prasthitaH | tataH sucira.n kaala.n deshaantara.n
yathecChayaa bhraantvaa punaH svapuramaagatya ta.n shreShThinamuvaaca \-
bhoH shreShThin | diiyataa.n me saa nikShepatulaa | sa aaha \- bho | naasti
saa tvadiiyaa tulaa | muuShikairbhakShitaa | jiirNadhana aaha \- bhoH
shreShThin | naasti doShaste yadi muuShikairbhakShiteti | iidR^igevaaya.n
sa.nsaaraH | na ki~ncidatra shaashvatamasti | paramaha.n nadyaa.n
snaanaartha.n gamiShyaami | tattvamaatmiiya.n shishumena.n
dhanadevanaamaana.n mayaa saha snaanopakaraNahasta.n preShayeti |
so.api cauryabhayaattasya sha~NkitaH svaputramuvaaca \-  vatsa
pitR^ivyo.aya.n tava snaanaartha.n nadyaa.n yaasyati | tadgamyataamanena
saardha.n snaanopakaraNamaadaayeti | aho saadhvidamucyate \-

na bhaktyaa kasyacitko.api priya.n prakurute naraH |
muktvaa bhaya.n pralobha.n vaa kaaryakaaraNameva vaa || 445||

tathaa ca \-

atyaadaro bhavedyatra kaaryakaaraNavarjitaH |
tatra sha~Nkaa prakartavyaa pariNaame.asukhaavahaa || 446||

athaasau vaNikshishuH snaanopakaraNamaadaaya prahR^iShTamanaa\-
stenaabhyaagatena saha prasthitaH | tathaanuShThite vaNiksnaatvaa
ta.n shishu.n nadiiguhaayaa.n prakShipya taddvaara.n
bR^ihacChilayaacChaadya satvara.n gR^ihamaagataH | pR^iShTashca
tena vaNijaa \-  bho abhyaagata tatkathyataa.n kutra me shishuryastvayaa
saha nadii.n gataH iti | sa aaha \- nadiitaTaatsa shyenena hR^ita iti |
shreShThyaaha \- mithyaavaadin | ki.n kvacicChyeno baala.n hartu.n
shaknoti | tatsamarpaya me sutamanyathaa raajakule nivedayiShyaamiiti |
sa aaha \- bhoH satyavaadin | yathaa shyeno baala.n na nayati tathaa
muuShikaa api lohabhaaraghaTitaa.n tulaa.n na bhakShayanti | tadarpaya
me tulaa.n yadi daarakeNa prayojanam | eva.n vivadamaanau dvaavapi
raajakula.n gatau | tatra shreShThii taarasvareNa provaaca \-  bho
abrahmaNyamabrahmaNyam | mama shishuranena caureNaapahR^itaH |
atha dharmaadhikaariNastamuucuH \-  bhoH samarpyataa.n shreShThisutaH |
sa aaha \- ki.n karomi | pashyato me nadiitaTaacChyenenaapahR^itaH
shishuH | tacChrutvaa te procuH \-  bho na satyamabhihita.n bhavataa |
ki.n shyenaH shishu.n hartu.n samartho bhavati | sa aaha \- bho bhoH
shruuyataa.n madvacaH |

tulaa.n lohasahasrasya yatra khaadanti muuShikaaH |
raaja.nstatra harecChyeno baalaka.n naatra sa.n shayaH || 447||

te procuH \-  kathametat | tataH shreShThii sabhyaanaamagre sarva.n
vR^ittaanta.n nivedayaamaasa | tatastairvihasya dvaavapi tau paraspara.n
sambodhya tulaashishupradaanena santoShitau | ato.aha.n braviimi \-
tulaa.n lohasahasrasya iti | tanmuurkha | sa.njiivakaprasaadamasahamaanena
tvayaitatkR^itam | aho saadhvidamucyate \-

praayeNaatra kulaanvita.n kukulajaaH shriivallabha.n durbhagaa
daataara.n kR^ipaNaa R^ijuunanR^ijavo vitte sthita.n nirdhanaaH |
vairuupyopahataashca kaantavapuSha.n dharmaashraya.n paapino
naanaashaastravicakShaNa.n ca puruSha.n nindanti muurkhaaH sadaa || 448||

tathaa ca \-

muurkhaaNaa.n paNDitaa dveShyaa nirdhanaanaa.n mahaadhanaaH |
vratinaH paapashiilaanaamasatiinaa.n kulastriyaH || 449||

tanmuurkha tvayaa hitamapyahita.n kR^itam | ukta~nca \-

paNDito.api vara.n shatrurna muurkho hitakaarakaH |
vaanareNa hato raajaa vipraashcaureNa rakShitaaH || 450||

damanaka aaha kathametat | so.abraviit \-

\medskip\hrule\medskip
kathaa 23

kasyacidraadnyo nitya.n vaanaro.atibhaktiparo.a~Ngasevako.antaHpure\-
.apyapratiShiddhaprasaro.ativishvaasasthaanamabhuut | ekadaa raadnyo
nidraa.n gatasya vaanare vyajana.n niitvaa vaayu.n vidadhati raadnyo
vakShaHsthalopari makShikopaviShTaa | vyajanena muhurmuhurniShidhya\-
maanaapi punaH punastatra evopavishati | tatastena svabhaavacapalena
muurkheNa vaanareNa kruddhena sataa tiikShNa.n khaDgamaadaaya
tasyaa upari prahaaro vihitaH | tato makShikoDDiiya gataa para.n tena
shitadhaareNaasinaa raadnyo vakSho dvidhaa jaata.n raajaa mR^itashca |
tasmaacciraayuricChataa nR^ipeNa muurkho.anucaro na rakShaNiiyaH |
aparamekasminnagare ko.api vipro mahaavidvaanpara.n puurvajanmayogena
cauro vartate | tasminpure.anyadeshaadaagataa.nshcaturo vipraanbahuuni
vastuuni vikriiNato dR^iShTvaa cintitavaan \-  aho kenopaayenaiShaa.n
dhana.n labhe | iti vicintya teShaa.n puro.anekaani shaastroktaani
subhaaShitaani caatipriyaaNi madhuraaNi vacanaani jalpataa teShaa.n
manasi vishvaasamutpaadya sevaa kartumaarabdhaa | athavaa
saadhvidamucyate \-

asatii bhavati salajjaa kShaara.n niira.n ca shiitala.n bhavati |
dambhii bhavati vivekii priyavaktaa bhavati dhuurtajanaH || 451||

atha tasminsevaa.n kurvati tairvipraiH sarvavastuuni vikriiya bahumuulyaani
ratnaani kriitaani | tatastaani ja~Nghaamadhye tatsamakSha.n prakShipya
svadesha.n prati gantumudyamo vihitaH | tataH sa dhuurtaviprastaanvipraan
gantumudyataanprekShya cintaavyaakulitamanaaH sa.njaataH \-  aho
dhanametanna ki~ncinmama caTitam | athaibhiH saha yaami | pathi kvaapi
viSha.n dattvaitaannihatya sarvaratnaani gR^ihNaami | iti vicintya
teShaamagre sakaruNa.n vilapyedamaaha \- bho mitraaNi | yuuya.n
maamekaakina.n muktvaa gantumudyataaH | tanme mano bhavadbhiH saha
snehapaashena baddha.n bhavadvirahanaamnaivaakula.n sa~njaata.n yathaa
dhR^iti.n kvaapi na dhatte | yuuyamanugraha.n vidhaaya sahaayabhuuta.n
maamapi sahaiva nayata | tadvacaH shrutvaa te karuNaardracittaastena
samameva svadesha.n prati prasthitaaH | athaadhvani teShaa.n
pa~ncaanaamapi palliipuramadhye vrajataa.n dhvaa~NkShaaH
kathayitumaarabdhaaH \-  re re kiraataaH | dhaavata dhaavata |
sapaadalakShadhanino yaanti | etaannihatya dhana.n nayata | tataH
kiraatairdhvaa~NkShavacanamaakarNya satvara.n gatvaa te vipraa
laguDaprahaarairjarjariikR^itya vastraaNi mocayitvaa vilokitaaH para.n
dhana.n ki~ncinna labdham | tadaa taiH kiraatairabhihitam \-  bhoH
paanthaaH | puraa kadaapi dhvaa~NkShavacanamanR^ita.n naasiit |
tato bhavataa.n sa.nnidhau kvaapi dhana.n vidyate tadarpayata | anyathaa
sarveShaamapi vadha.n vidhaaya carma vidaarya pratya~Nga.n prekShya
dhana.n neShyaamaH | tadaa teShaamiidR^isha.n vacanamaakarNya
cauravipreNa manasi cintitam \-  yadaiShaa.n vipraaNaa.n vadha.n
vidhaayaa~Nga.n vilokya ratnaani neShyanti tadaapi maa.n vadhiShyanti
tato.aha.n puurvamevaatmaanamaratna.n samarpyaitaanmu~ncaami |
ukta~nca \-

mR^ityorbibheShi ki.n baala na sa bhiita.n vimu~ncati |
adya vaa.abdashataante vaa mR^ityurvai praaNinaa.n dhruvaH || 452||

tathaa ca \-

gavaarthe braahmaNaarthe ca praaNatyaaga.n karoti yaH |
suuryasya maNDala.n bhittvaa sa yaati paramaa.n gatim || 453||

iti nishcityaabhihitam \-  bhoH kiraataaH | yadyeva.n tato maa.n puurva.n
nihatya vilokayata | tatastaistathaanuShThite ta.n dhanarahitamavalokyaapare
catvaaro.api muktaaH |ato.aha.n braviimi \-  paNDito.api vara.n shatruriti |
athaiva.n sa.nvadatostayoH sa.njiivakaH kShaNameka.n pi~Ngalakena
saha yuddha.n kR^itvaa tasya kharanakharaprahaaraabhihito
gataasurvasundharaapiiThe nipapaata | atha ta.n gataasumavalokya
pi~NgalakastadguNasmaraNaardrahR^idayaH provaaca \-  bho ayukta.n
mayaa paapena kR^ita.n sa.njiivaka.n vyaapaadayataa | yato
vishvaasaghaataadanyannaasti paapatara.n karma | ukta~nca \-

mitradrohii kR^itaghnashca yashca vishvaasaghaatakaH |
te naraa naraka.n yaanti yaavaccandradivaakarau || 454||
bhuumikShaye raajavinaasha eva
           bhR^ityasya vaa buddhimato vinaashe |
no yuktamukta.n hyanayoH samatva.n
           naShTaapi bhuumiH sulabhaa na bhR^ityaaH || 455||

tathaa mayaa sabhaamadhye sa sadaiva prasha.nsitaH | tatki.n
kathayiShyaami teShaamagrataH | ukta~nca \-

ukto bhavati yaH puurva.n guNavaan iti sa.nsadi |
na tasya doSho vaktavyaH pratidnyaabha~NgabhiiruNaa || 456||

eva.nvidha.n pralapanta.n damanakaH sametya saharShamidamaaha \-
deva kaataratamastavaiSha nyaayo yaddrohakaariNa.n shaShpabhuja.n
hatvettha.n shocasi | tannaitadupapanna.n bhuubhujaam | ukta~nca \-

pitaa vaa yadi vaa bhraataa putro bhaaryaa.athavaa suhR^it |
praaNadroha.n yadaa gacCheddhantavyo naasti paatakam || 457||

tathaa ca \-

raajaa ghR^iNii braahmaNaH sarvabhakShii
           strii caatrapaa duShTamatiH sahaayaH |
preShyaH pratiipo.adhikR^itaH pramaadii
           tyaajyaa amii yashca kR^ita.n na vetti || 458||

api ca \-

satyaanR^itaa ca paruShaa priyavaadinii ca
           hi.nsraa dayaalurapi caarthaparaa vadaanyaa |
bhuurivyathaa pracuravittasamaagamaa ca
           veshyaa~Nganeva nR^ipaniitiranekaruupaa || 459||

api ca \-

akR^itopadravaH kashcinmahaanapi na puujyate |
puujayanti naraa naagaanna taarkShya.n naagaghaatinam || 460||

tathaa ca \-

ashocyaananvashocastva.n pradnyaavaadaa.nshca bhaaShase |
gataasuunagataasuu.nshca naanushocanti paNDitaaH || 461||

eva.n tena sambodhitaH pi~NgalakaH sa.njiivakashoka.n tyaktvaa
damanakasaacivyena raajyamakarot |

iti shriiviShNusharmaviracite pa~ncatantre mitrabhedo naama
prathama.n tantram |
